NG0204:43: 'jigs byed kyi rgyal po ya man+ta ka he ru

NG0204:58: snying rje chen po'i ting nge 'dzin dang */

NG0204:62: thugs rjes zhe sdang sgrol ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang */
NG0204:63: shes rab kyis 'dod chags sgrol ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang */

NG0204:66: 'bad pa med pa'i cho 'phrul gyis phrag dog 'joms pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang */
NG0204:67: thub pas bdud rnams 'joms pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang */
NG0204:68: de rnams la snyoms par zhugs so //
NG0204:69: de yi 'dzin rtog dbang gi ni //
NG0204:70: 'jig rten gsum po rim gyis chags //
NG0204:71: 'gro drug sems can ma lus la //
NG0204:72: dregs pas rim par dbang bsgyur ba //
NG0204:73: bsam pa log pa'i bar chad bdud //
NG0204:74: nga rgyal khengs pa'i gshin rje dang *//
NG0204:75: zhe sdang myos pa'i srin po dang *//
NG0204:76: dug gsum rgyas pa'i rgyal po dang *//
NG0204:77: phrag dog 'dod chags ma mo sogs //
NG0204:78: khams gsum ma lus rim gyis bsdus //
NG0204:79: nga rgyal dregs pa'i gzugs 'chang ba //
NG0204:80: gzugs phung che la rdos pa rags //
NG0204:81: nga ro che zhing gti mug can //
NG0204:82: lag na mtshon cha sna tshogs thogs //
NG0204:83: byams dang snying rje'i lam dang bral //
NG0204:84: che btsan rtag par 'dzin pa'i mthus //
NG0204:85: log pa'i lam dang gol ba'i sar //
NG0204:86: phyin ci log la yid ches pas //
NG0204:87: las su mtshan ma'i chos la spyod //
NG0204:88: srid pa'i sa bon rtsub mos 'phangs //
NG0204:89: dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal nyams su myong *//
NG0204:90: bskal pa bcu ru myong ba'o //
NG0204:91: gal te de las thar nas kyang *//
NG0204:92: yi dwags mo dang mkha' 'gro la //
NG0204:93: bskal pa drug tu gnas pa'o //
NG0204:94: gal te de las thar nas kyang *//
NG0204:95: slar yang srin po'i lus blangs nas //
NG0204:96: gong ma bzhin du 'khor bar gyur //
NG0204:97: de yi 'khor yang srin mo dang *//
NG0204:98: ma mo dang ni mkha' 'gro dang *//
NG0204:99: shin tu gtum pa'i 'khor dang bcas //
NG0204:100: gsod pa 'ba' zhig grims pa dang *//
NG0204:101: sha dang khrag dang srog la spyod //
NG0204:102: nges pa'i lung dang ma ldan pas //
NG0204:103: kun kyang log pa'i lam du gyur //
NG0204:104: sprul sku la sogs sangs rgyas kyis //
NG0204:105: 'dul ba'i las su ma gyur te //
NG0204:106: slar yang khengs pas ldog par byed //
NG0204:107: de nas 'khor gyi dngos po rnams kyis /
NG0204:108: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs pa thams
NG0204:109: cad kyi bdag nyid dgyes pa chen po rngams pa
NG0204:112: phyogs bcu dus gsum rdzogs pa yi //
NG0204:113: ye shes 'dus pa'i phrin las mchog / ye shes phrin las rmad po che //
NG0204:114: spros la mngon par 'chel ba yis //
NG0204:115: nga rgyal dregs pa'i gdug pa can //
NG0204:116: gdul bya smin par mdzad du gsol //
NG0204:118: de nas 'jigs byed chen pos bka' stsal pa /
NG0204:119: bdud dang srin po gshin rje sogs //
NG0204:120: nga rgyal dregs pas bcings nas ni //
NG0204:121: shin tu gdug cing gtum byed pas //
NG0204:122: de la zhi bas phan mi 'gyur //
NG0204:123: shes rab thabs dang ldan byas nas /
NG0204:124: khro bar de bzhin gshegs pas mdzad //
NG0204:127: khams gsum ma lus thams cad kun //
NG0204:128: skad cig yud la brlag 'gyur na //
NG0204:129: 'jig rten gsum po smos ci dgos //
NG0204:130: de nas 'jigs byed chen po des /
NG0204:131: las ngan pa'i srin po la sogs pa kun /
NG0204:132: nyon mongs pa'i bag chags sbyang ba dang */
NG0204:133: khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad bde ba la gzhag pa'i phyir /
NG0204:134: thugs rje chen po'i ye shes skyes nas /
NG0204:135: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bdag po rngam
NG0204:136: pa chen po ye shes kyis rgyal po de nyid
NG0204:138: rol pa chen po'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te /

NG0204:140: kyi gsang ba'i bdag mo khros pa'i rgyal mo ro

NG0204:154: rje me dpung chen po klong du 'khyil ba'i dbus
NG0204:155: na / phyogs bzhi ngos bzhi thod pa skam rlon rgya gram du brtsigs pa /

NG0204:369: bdud kyi rgyal po nag po 'dzum med @#//
NG0204:372: bdud kyi rgyal po be'u log nag po dang */
NG0204:373: bdud kyi rgyal po nag po spyi ring gnas /
NG0204:374: gshin rje tel pa'i 'khor dag na /
NG0204:375: bdud kyi rgyal po gling bzhi phung byed dang */
NG0204:376: gshin rje phya sangs 'khor dag na /
NG0204:377: bdud kyi rgyal po phya bdud dkar po dang */
NG0204:378: bdud kyi rgyal po phya bdud dmar po dang */
NG0204:379: bdud kyi rgyal po phya bdud ljang nag dang */
NG0204:380: bdud kyi rgyal po phya bdud sngon po dang */
NG0204:381: bdud kyi rgyal po phung byed 'ug pa'i mgo can dang */
NG0204:383: bdud mi lag sprel mgo dang */
NG0204:384: bdud rngam chen dung gi rna ba can dang */
NG0204:385: ral pa tshar dgu'i 'khor dag na //
NG0204:386: bse'i skye bu gdug pa can //
NG0204:387: stag mgo can gyi 'khor dag na //
NG0204:388: klu bdud sbrul gyi rgyu ma can //
NG0204:389: gri thogs ging gi pho nya bcu la sogs //
NG0204:390: ma lus 'dus pa thams cad kyis //
NG0204:391: bdag cag rnams kyi mchis brang dang *//
NG0204:392: ma dang sring mo bu mo rnams //
NG0204:394: dkyil 'khor chen por bzhes su gsol //
NG0204:395: 'jigs byed chen pos bzhes su gsol //
NG0204:396: bdag cag 'khor tshogs thams cad kyis //
NG0204:398: ming tsam 'dzin par sus bgyid pa //
NG0204:399: nor bu rin chen 'bar ba ltar //
NG0204:400: de yi dgos pa rdzogs par bgyi'o //
NG0204:402: de'i mchis brang thams cad yud tsam gyis 'ongs nas /
NG0204:403: las kyi dngos grub stsol ba las /
NG0204:404: de nas 'jigs byed kyi rgyal pos gsang ba'i ming btags lag tu rdo rje byin nas /
NG0204:405: bran dang pho nyar dbang bskur ro //
NG0204:406: de'i tshe mthu stobs kyi bdag po ya ma lag na rdo rje yang */
NG0204:407: mdun gyis bltas te bka' nod pa'i tshul du bzhugs so //
NG0204:408: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:409: gleng gzhi'i le'u ste dang po'o // // de nas
NG0204:410: 'jigs byed kyi rgyal po khrag 'thung ya man+ta ka
NG0204:411: des / thugs rje 'byung ba zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs so //
NG0204:412: de nas khro mo chen mo ro langs pe ta nag mos /
NG0204:414: rang gi pad+ma las khrag gi rgya mtsho bskyil te /
NG0204:415: 'jigs byed khrag 'thung gi rgyal po nyid la mchod cing */
NG0204:418: phyogs bcu dus gsum rdzogs pa yi //
NG0204:419: 'jig byed chen po rol pa'i sku //
NG0204:420: ye shes 'dus pa'i phrin las mchog / ye shes phrin las rmad po che //
NG0204:422: de nas 'jigs byed kyi rgyal po ya man+ta ka des bka' stsal pa /
NG0204:423: ye nas ma skyes gshin rje nag po'i tshogs //
NG0204:424: gnyis med ye shes 'dus pa'i gshin rje'i gshed //
NG0204:425: kun gyi ye shes dam pa 'dus pa yin //
NG0204:426: thugs rje chen pos 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NG0204:427: 'khor ba'i nyes skyon thams cad tshar gcod pa //
NG0204:428: dus gsum 'dul ba'i dpal ldan gar gyi bdag / 'dus pa'i tshogs 'di sems lnga ldan par gyis //
NG0204:431: de nas yang gsang ba'i bdag po ya ma lag na rdo rjes 'di skad ces gsol to //
NG0204:432: e ma'o 'jigs byed chen po lags //
NG0204:433: rnal 'byor can la gnas phyir dang *//
NG0204:434: 'dul byed gnyis kyi don gyi phyir //
NG0204:435: sna tshogs brgya phrag brgyad kyi don //
NG0204:436: dman pa rnams la bshad du gsol //
NG0204:438: de nas 'jigs byed chen po gshin rje khrag 'thung gi rgyal pos 'di skad ces bka' stsal to //
NG0204:439: rang byung ye shes bde chen las /
NG0204:440: khyad par ye shes bzhi ru shar //
NG0204:441: chu zla'i tshul du las rnams 'char //
NG0204:442: bde ba chen po gsal bar gyis shig / ces bka' stsal to //
NG0204:444: e ma'o 'jigs byed chen po lags //
NG0204:445: rang byung ye shes bde chen po //
NG0204:446: chos rnams kun gyi ngo bo de //
NG0204:447: shes bya'i yul du ji ltar 'gyur //
NG0204:448: de las thabs sbyor las rnams ji ltar byung *//
NG0204:449: byung nas grub pa ji ltar 'gyur //
NG0204:451: 'jigs byed chen pos bka' stsal pa //
NG0204:452: snang srid ye nas mya ngan 'das /
NG0204:453: spros bral mi 'gyur gdod nas dag / dag pa nyid na thams cad gsal //
NG0204:454: shes bya shes byed ngang gis stong *//
NG0204:455: chu zla'i dkyil 'khor bzhin du gsal //
NG0204:456: 'di ni yid bzhin rin po che //
NG0204:457: thams cad re ba rdzogs byed pa'o //
NG0204:458: e ma'o rtogs par rab dka' ba //
NG0204:459: sangs rgyas kyis kyang mi mkhyen na //
NG0204:460: gdod nas rnam dag chos kyi dbyings //
NG0204:461: 'gro kun yongs la a cang ches //
NG0204:462: de nas gsang ba'i bdag po ngo mtshar du gyur nas /
NG0204:465: ma rig gnyis kyis bsgribs par gyur //
NG0204:466: rnam par phye ste don rgyas par //
NG0204:467: dpa' bo chen pos bshad du gsol //
NG0204:468: ye shes gsal bar bshad du gsol //
NG0204:469: bcom ldan 'das 'jigs byed chen pos bka' stsal pa /
NG0204:472: thun mong ma yin par rig par bya'o //
NG0204:473: skal ldan rnams la rgyas par bshad kyis nyon cig / 'di lta ste /
NG0204:474: chos thams cad spros pa'i mtshan ma thams cad dang bral ba 'di ni /
NG0204:476: ye nas zug rngu med pa'i 'jam pa'i ngang dang */
NG0204:477: ye nas yin pa'i rang bzhin dang */
NG0204:478: gnyis su med pa'i bdag nyid chen po'o //
NG0204:479: de lta bu'i don de ni rnam pa cir yang gsal ba'o //
NG0204:480: mtshan nyid thams cad dang bral ba'o //
NG0204:481: rang bzhin kun gyi dngos gzhi ste /
NG0204:482: yid bzhin gyi nor bu ltar snang ba'o //
NG0204:483: 'di ni bde ba chen po zhes bya ste /
NG0204:484: rtog pa'i yul dang bral ba'o //
NG0204:485: 'di ni rgyu rkyen dang bral ba ste /
NG0204:487: thams cad sems su mnyam pa ste /
NG0204:488: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes so //
NG0204:489: thams cad me long gi gzugs brnyan ltar gsal ba ste /
NG0204:490: me long lta bu'i ye shes so //
NG0204:491: 'di ni mtshan nyid kyis ma 'dres par gsal te /
NG0204:493: sor rtog pa'i ye shes so //
NG0204:494: de lta bas na gang yang blang dor med pa'o //
NG0204:495: yengs pa med pa'i don du gsal bar bya'o //
NG0204:497: de lta bu'i don de las thams cad 'byung bar smra te /
NG0204:498: de ni nor bu rin chen lta bu'o //
NG0204:499: sa gzhi chen po lta bu'o //
NG0204:507: dbang phyug chen po lta bu'o //
NG0204:509: mya ngan las 'das pa thams cad kyi byed pa por rgyal ba nyid kyis gsungs so //
NG0204:511: blta ba 'di la gang gnas pa'i skyes bu'am /
NG0204:512: rnal 'byor de ni skal pa bzang ba yin to //
NG0204:513: 'di ni las kyi rim pa brgya phrag brgyad //
NG0204:514: rtsa ba gnyis su 'dus pa'i don //
NG0204:515: sbyor ba nyis brgya stong bcu drug / dka' ba med par len par gsungs //
NG0204:516: the tshom med par sems kyis su //
NG0204:517: de bas 'di la nan tan bya //
NG0204:519: 'khor 'dus pa thams cad the tshom dang bral nas /
NG0204:520: yid blos thag chod de chos nyid blos sems so //
NG0204:524: rgyu med 'bras bu dag pa'i don //
NG0204:525: srid pa mya ngan gnyis 'das pa //
NG0204:526: bdag cag grol bar der gyur to //
NG0204:527: zhes gsol nas dad pas 'dun to //
NG0204:528: rgyud kyi rgyal po dpal zla gsang nag po me lce phreng ba'i rgyud las /
NG0204:530: gsal byed lta ba bstan pa'i le'u ste gnyis pa'o
NG0204:531: // // de nas yang 'jigs byed kyi rgyal po
NG0204:532: gshin rje'i gshed kyis phrin las sna tshogs rol pa
NG0204:533: zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs
NG0204:534: so // de'i tshe de'i dus na mthu stobs kyi
NG0204:535: bdag po ya ma lag na rdo rje la sogs
NG0204:536: so // te / gdug pa can gyi 'khor tshogs
NG0204:537: rnams kyis mos pa'i dbang gis mgrin gcig tu thal
NG0204:538: so // te / mo sbyar nas / bcom ldan
NG0204:539: 'das gshin rje'i gshed la 'di skad ces gsol to
NG0204:540: so // te / mo sbyar nas / // e ma'o 'jigs byed chen po lags //
NG0204:541: bdag cag 'khor tshogs ma lus kun //
NG0204:543: stong gsum mun par gtong dang 'jig rten mes bsreg dang *//
NG0204:545: gnam lcags lce yang 'bebs par byed //
NG0204:546: smyo 'bog yams nad gtong dang srog gcod gang yang byed //
NG0204:547: mdze rims me bzad gtong ba'i nad bdag sna tshogs
NG0204:548: mang po dag / dpa' bo chen po'i 'khor du
NG0204:549: 'dus pa kun // ye shes chen po khyod kyis bsal bar mdzad //
NG0204:550: ye shes chen po'i sgron mas gsal bar mdzad par byos //
NG0204:551: bdag cag 'khor tshogs thams cad kyis //
NG0204:552: bstan pa rgya mtsho bsrung bar dam bcas pas //
NG0204:553: bdag cag 'khor tshogs thams cad kyi //
NG0204:554: srog tig rtsa ba'i dam pa 'di //
NG0204:555: 'jigs byed chen po bzhes su gsol //
NG0204:559: de nas sde brgyad so so rang rang gi srog gi snying po phul te /
NG0204:560: 'jigs byed chen pos bdag nyid kyi dkyil 'khor chen po bskyed de /
NG0204:561: rngams pa'i mdangs kyis seng ge'i lta stangs kyis bzhugs so //
NG0204:562: de la dang por las kyi gshed bzhis /
NG0204:563: rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i sngags phul te /
NG0204:564: ya ya ya ya sa ma s+t+wam /
NG0204:566: ma ma rag mo trag sha mu tra kha mun tra /
NG0204:567: snying kha rag ma rag mo rag mo //
NG0204:568: sarba rag mo ti kum dza dza kha la ma ti ma b+h+yo b+h+yo sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NG0204:569: ya ma ra tsa dz+wa la ram /
NG0204:570: nr-i kro d+ha+e shwa ri dz+wa la ram /
NG0204:571: ya tra tra ga rak+sha dz+wa la ram hum /
NG0204:572: ra rag mo kro d+hi sha ri dz+wa la ni hum /
NG0204:573: om raka sha dz+wa la ram pa ya hum /
NG0204:574: sha tra mo kro d+hi shwa ri dz+wa la ram pa hum /
NG0204:575: om tri nag po dz+wa la ram ba hum /
NG0204:576: tsit+ta ro la dz+wa la ram pa hum /
NG0204:577: om rak+sha yak+sha ma snying rtsa dz+wa la ram pa hum /
NG0204:578: a+om ni tsi ra tsu ru kro d+hi shwa ri dz+wa la ni hum /
NG0204:579: om rak+sha ni dz+wa la ram pa ya hum /
NG0204:580: om tra mo rag sha kro d+hi shwa ri hum /
NG0204:581: om many+dzu shri nag po tra trag po tra rak+sha ni ya hum /
NG0204:582: om nag mo rag sha kro d+hi shwa ri ni hum /
NG0204:583: om many+dzu shri badzra ma ro tra rag+sha dz+wa la ram ba ya hum /
NG0204:584: na ga sha tri shr-i ri dz+wa la ram ba ya hum /
NG0204:585: phyogs skyong gshin rje rnams kyis phul lo //
NG0204:586: du tra sa tra mu khrag ba ra khrag tsa de phor ba dun ha ba swa ha /
NG0204:587: sa ma ya a bi shu ra tsa ga sha tshal pa ya ni tri /
NG0204:588: ma ra ya ang+ku sha dza dza /
NG0204:589: om bi sha la du ru ma ni shi ga dza la ya ta swa ha /
NG0204:590: om hri sha ga du ru rag ram na ge tsit+ta tram ma ma yam za 'gram hri /
NG0204:591: hi yo gi sha la dza dza /
NG0204:592: ma ma snying kha rag / snying kha rag / ma ma rak+sha /
NG0204:594: rag mo thun thun snying la thun dza dza /
NG0204:598: ra tsa sa ma ya dzahhum dza ra li bri ma ni hum phat /
NG0204:600: tri tri ra tsa tsa pa la a shug me swa ha /
NG0204:601: ba hu yak+sha bu ro tsa tor ra hu la
NG0204:602: ma trig pa tshil ma khug yak+sha thang thang ma
NG0204:603: ya swa ha / na ga ra tsa ma ha
NG0204:604: ka la to ba tsa sa kha pa kha sha
NG0204:605: ru hum ya hum dza dza /
NG0204:606: na ga ra tsa dza dza /
NG0204:607: om ma ha sa ma ya dza dza /
NG0204:608: om da rak+sha ma snying kha rag dza dza /
NG0204:609: om raka mo raka mo rak+sha snying kha rag dza dza /
NG0204:610: om rag mo rak+sha dza dza //
NG0204:612: 'jig rten gyi khams na dbang bsgyur sde brgyad dang */
NG0204:613: lha dang klu dang gnod sbyin dang *//
NG0204:614: dri za lha min nam mkha' lding *//
NG0204:615: mi'am ci dang lto 'phye chen po dang *//
NG0204:616: sha za 'byung po grul bum dang *//
NG0204:617: srul po dang ni lus srul po //
NG0204:618: skem byed dang ni brjed byed dang *//
NG0204:619: smyo byed dang ni grib gnon dang *//
NG0204:620: gnon po dang ni nam gru dang *//
NG0204:621: de dag la sogs te srog gcod bdud dang */
NG0204:626: gzer thabs btsan gyi tshogs dang */
NG0204:627: srog gcod ging gi tshogs bsam gyis mi khyab pas bka' nyan zer zhing srog snying phul lo //
NG0204:628: de nas yang 'jigs byed chen po gshed po des /
NG0204:630: tshul gyis ye shes rol pa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs so //
NG0204:631: de nas gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rjes
NG0204:632: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pas mchod de 'di skad
NG0204:633: ces gsol to / khrag 'thung chen po 'jigs pa'i sku //
NG0204:634: dam pa rnams la phan bya'i phyir //
NG0204:635: zhing bcu sreg pa'i nyi ma'i tshul //
NG0204:637: 'jigs byed chen pos bshad du gsol //
NG0204:639: 'jigs byed chen pos bka' stsal pa //
NG0204:640: nyon cig zung zhig rdo rje 'dzin pa 'dus pa'i tshogs //
NG0204:642: stong pa'i ye shes dbus nyid dngos //
NG0204:643: gsal ba'i ye shes bzhi ldan te /
NG0204:644: khams gsum sreg pa'i nyi ma yin //
NG0204:646: de nyid don du rjes 'grub pas //
NG0204:648: sprul pa rang byung dngos shar ba //
NG0204:649: dus gsum rgyal ba'i bka' brgyud pa'i //
NG0204:651: brgyad spangs bcu thub gsum rig cing *//
NG0204:652: snying po ldan pas mngon min pa //
NG0204:653: ngang gis 'jam la rgya che zhing */
NG0204:654: khams gsum rmi lam ltar shes pa //
NG0204:655: bstan pa spyi yi blo sred can //
NG0204:656: bla med bdud rtsi rjes bsgrub pa'i //
NG0204:657: dkon mchog rgyal mtshan lta byed pa //
NG0204:658: de 'dre'i bu la ma gtogs pa /
NG0204:659: kha blo ming tsam brjod pa med //
NG0204:661: de nas 'jigs byed chen pos bka' stsal pa /
NG0204:662: nag po gshed kyi gnas rnams ni //
NG0204:663: zur brgyad mu khyud chun 'khor can //
NG0204:664: ngam ri'i brag dang srin brag rdo rje 'dra //
NG0204:665: dgu 'dus rtse dang chu mdo gling *//
NG0204:666: shin tu dben pa'i dur khrod dam //
NG0204:667: de sogs bde ba'i gnas btsal te //
NG0204:668: gzhung dang mthun pa'i gnas dag tu //
NG0204:669: gnas dang 'khor lo brtsam par bya //
NG0204:670: sa chog mtshams bcad bsdig sbyangs la //
NG0204:671: chag chag thig gdab 'og ma yi //
NG0204:672: dkyil 'khor mthing nag gru gsum la //
NG0204:673: zla gam gsum dang ldan par bri //
NG0204:674: thod phreng dang ni me ri 'bar //
NG0204:676: yang na cha mnyam thig bzhi rgya gram gdab //
NG0204:677: le'u tse dgu ldan mu khyud 'khor lo bskor //
NG0204:678: mu khyud 'gram bzhi ldan pa la //
NG0204:679: 'khor lo rtsibs ni bcu drug ldan //
NG0204:680: phyi rim bar khyams sgo khyud bcas //
NG0204:681: bar khyams dur khrod bzhi dang ldan //
NG0204:682: phyi rim yi dwags gzugs brnyan dgod //
NG0204:683: gzhan gyi 'dod pas de yang bstan //
NG0204:685: gcod pa sngags kyi 'khor lo ni //
NG0204:686: dbus na gru gsum rtsibs bzhi la //
NG0204:687: 'khrul sngags drag po lnga dang ldan //
NG0204:688: phyi rim bcu gnyis 'khor lo la //
NG0204:689: 'khrul mig drag po bcu gnyis pa //
NG0204:690: de dag rjes su dgod par bya //
NG0204:691: phyi rim bcu drug 'khor lo la //
NG0204:692: sku gsung thugs kyi snying po ste //
NG0204:693: dgod pa gnam thus lto sbyar dgod //
NG0204:694: yang logs 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi la //
NG0204:695: gcod cing mnan pa'i drag sngags @#//
NG0204:697: 'khor lo rtsibs chen sum cu drug / sngags ni me dbal 'khor lo mtshon //
NG0204:698: 'khor lo me dbal mtshon chen gyis //
NG0204:699: zhing bcu ma lus gtan nas bsreg / ces bka' stsal to //
NG0204:700: de nas der lha dgod pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NG0204:701: 'jigs byed chen pos bka' stsal pa /
NG0204:702: 'jigs byed rgyal po gshin rje'i gshed //
NG0204:703: sku yi gzugs brnyan bzhugs su gsol //
NG0204:704: g.yas su sgeg mo ral gcig ma //
NG0204:705: g.yon du za byed be ta li //
NG0204:706: g.yas g.yon gnyis kyi zla gam la //
NG0204:707: sku yi gzugs brnyan bzhugs su gsol //
NG0204:708: yang na snying po bri bar bya //
NG0204:709: byang gi phyogs kyi zla gam steng *//
NG0204:710: snying po 'jigs byed ya ma ra tsa yi //
NG0204:711: skur bsgom mchog phur sor gsum gzug / ces bka' stsal to //
NG0204:712: yang gsang ba mos pa'i dbang gis dgod pa ni /
NG0204:713: mthar mdzad yab yum dbus su dgod //
NG0204:714: srog gi gshed po yab yum bzhi //
NG0204:715: mu khyud dang por dgod par bya //
NG0204:716: gnyis la phyogs bcu'i yab yum ste //
NG0204:717: bar chod gshed kyi bdud rnams kyang *//
NG0204:718: gong nas 'dus pa'i tshul du bya //
NG0204:719: sgo yi 'khor lor bstan ma yang stam ma dgod //
NG0204:720: de ni gnas kyi 'khor lo las //
NG0204:721: brten pa'i lha yi 'khor lo bstan //
NG0204:722: ye shes byin brlab stobs ldan bya //
NG0204:723: rjes su mthun pa'i cho gar ldan //
NG0204:724: skad cig sngags dang 'od la gsal //
NG0204:727: de la skyen gyi yan lag bzhi //
NG0204:728: gzhung dang mthun pa'i bde gnas su //
NG0204:729: rten rdzas gnyis dang mthun rdzas dang */
NG0204:730: mchod rdzas ling+ga'i rdzas la sogs //
NG0204:731: brnag pa thun gyi rdzas rnams bsog / ces gsungs so //
NG0204:732: de nas yang 'khor gyi dang pos 'di skad ces zhus so //
NG0204:734: rgyu dang rkyen gyi tshon dang ni //
NG0204:735: srad bu rab gnas gang lags pa //
NG0204:736: dpa' bo chen pos bshad du gsol //
NG0204:737: 'jigs byed chen pos bka' stsal pa //
NG0204:738: nyon cig zung zhig rdo rje 'dzin //
NG0204:739: dur khrod gnas su dpa' bo yis //
NG0204:740: ka li ka pa ma gtogs pa //
NG0204:741: gos su bcad pa'i rgyu blangs la //
NG0204:742: thod pas snying po bcud sdud bya //
NG0204:743: de la gcod pa'i 'khor lo bri //
NG0204:744: dur khrod gos la bam chen gyi //
NG0204:745: sme ba lnga yis thang pa bya //
NG0204:746: ni rang su yi thal ba yis //
NG0204:747: tha mar rkyang thang rgya bcad de //
NG0204:748: mchog phran rkang gis phar byas la //
NG0204:749: bam chen don gyi khrag rnams kyis //
NG0204:750: rjes su mthun pa'i 'khor lo bri //
NG0204:752: bam chen sha sha ro du ha //
NG0204:753: thag pas srad bu legs byas te //
NG0204:754: snyoms pas tshad ldan thig gdab bya //
NG0204:755: ni rang su dang mang sar sbyar //
NG0204:756: tshon gsum kha dog byed par 'gyur //
NG0204:757: rus pa du bas bsdus pa ni //
NG0204:758: 'gyur ba med pa'i tshon du bya //
NG0204:760: ye shes byin rlabs ldan pa'i phyir //
NG0204:761: nges par dang du blang bar bya //
NG0204:767: 'jigs byed ya ma'i zhing khams nas //

NG0204:1484: brtul zhugs mthar thug sbyin par bya //
NG0204:1485: rnam grangs rim pa lnga yis rdzogs par bshad //
NG0204:1486: de la rdo rje slob dpon dbang dang 'bar ba ging *//
NG0204:1487: rgyan chas rtags dang byang chub sems //
NG0204:1488: de nas 'di skad ces bka' stsal to //
NG0204:1489: sngon du bya ba'i las zin nas //
NG0204:1490: rim pa rdzogs par bskur bar bya //
NG0204:1492: de nas rdo rje slob dpon du dbang bskur ba ni /
NG0204:1493: hum dus gsum bde gshegs ma lus mkha' la 'dren //
NG0204:1494: shes pa mthong rdzogs yon tan lhun gyis grub //
NG0204:1495: sdug bsngal skyob mdzad ma rig 'dren byed cing *//
NG0204:1498: bud+d+ha'i gdung 'tshob rdo rje slob dpon mchog / gang zhig mngon du lhun gyis grub pa'i dbang *//
NG0204:1499: dbang mchog ma lus khyod kyis thob par shog /
NG0204:1500: om sarba ta tha ga ta ma hum gu ru
NG0204:1501: gu h+ye shwa ra badzra swa b+ha ba at+ma ko\u0f85ham
NG0204:1502: / de nas phyag rgya chen po'i dbang bskur ba //
NG0204:1503: hum thugs rje'i thabs mkhas rang byung he ru ka
NG0204:1504: / khams gsum dbang bsgyur rang byung bcom ldan 'das
NG0204:1505: / khams gsum gdug pa bsreg mdzad 'bar ba'i lha //
NG0204:1506: che ba'i che mchog dbang phyug chen po'i sku //
NG0204:1507: rtog pa thugs rje 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor la //
NG0204:1508: ye shes me 'bar gsal ba'i 'od 'bar te /
NG0204:1509: khro tshogs 'bar ba'i dbang mchog rab 'bar ba //
NG0204:1510: ye shes me 'bar 'bar ba chen po'i dbang *//
NG0204:1511: gdug pa zil gnon ma rig bsreg mdzad cing *//
NG0204:1512: sdug bsngal rgya mtsho bskal pa'i mes bsreg pa //
NG0204:1513: kun la ya ma me 'bar chen po'i dbang *//
NG0204:1514: rigs kyi bu mchog dbang mchog thob par shog /
NG0204:1515: om sarba ta tha ga ta dz+wa la man+da la
NG0204:1516: ma he shwa ra badzra at+ma ko\u0f85ham /
NG0204:1517: de nas khams gsum sgrol ba'i ging gi dbang bskur te /
NG0204:1518: ye shes dregs pas thams cad sgrol ba'i ging *//
NG0204:1519: che ba'i rgyal po kun gyi bdag / thams cad kun tu 'bar ba'i mtshan //
NG0204:1520: ye shes gshed bzhi khams gsum sgrol ba'i ging *//
NG0204:1521: zhing bcu sreg pa'i nyi ma ste //
NG0204:1522: dbang mchog 'di yis dbang bskur bas /
NG0204:1523: khams gsum ma lus thal bar rlog / de 'dra'i
NG0204:1524: dbang mchog thob par shog / om ya ma b+ha
NG0204:1527: de nas rgyan chas rtags kyi dbang bskur te /
NG0204:1528: dang po thod rlon phreng ba thogs la 'di skad do //
NG0204:1529: hum dung chen khong seng dbang po lnga dang ldan //
NG0204:1530: sku gsum tshul 'chang skam rlon ra ri'i tshul //
NG0204:1531: 'khor ba gnas sdud thabs kyi phreng bas brgyan //
NG0204:1532: khams gsum dbang phyug thod phreng dbang bskur bas //
NG0204:1533: sku gsung thugs kyi dbang mchog thob par shog / om pad+ma b+han+d+ha ka pa la ha ha hum /
NG0204:1535: de nas sbrul gyi chun pos dbang bskur ba 'di skad do //
NG0204:1536: thod sbrul mnyen lcug 'jigs byed rgyan du che //
NG0204:1537: sbrul nag stong gis brgyan pa'i rngom brjid ni //
NG0204:1538: sku mchog phyir yang sku yi gnas lngar 'khril //
NG0204:1539: dug lnga ma spangs dbang gi rtags su bstan //
NG0204:1540: mnyen lcug 'khril ldem zhe sdang drag po 'joms //
NG0204:1541: rdzu 'phrul shugs kyis klu rgyal dbang du sdud //
NG0204:1542: gti mug dbang 'dul dbang phyug yin pa'i phyir //
NG0204:1543: sbrul nag stong gi chun pos dbang bskur bas //
NG0204:1544: zhe sdang drag po 'bar ba'i gnas dag nas //
NG0204:1545: thabs mkhas rgyal ba mnyes pa'i dbang thob shog / om badzra na ga ra dza hum /
NG0204:1548: de nas zhing gi g.yang gzhis dbang bskur ba /
NG0204:1549: hum zhing lpags rtag tu gsol zhing dur khrod bdag
NG0204:1550: / g.yang gzhi tshe bdug skud pa sked la bcings
NG0204:1553: dur khrod tshogs kyi bdag po yin pa'i phyir //
NG0204:1554: zhing chen g.yang gzhis khyod la dbang bskur bas //
NG0204:1555: zhing chen rlon pas thabs la mkhas pa yis //
NG0204:1556: 'khor ba'i gnas las yongs su rgyal bar shog / pam smig ta kha hi a b+hi shiny+tsa hum /
NG0204:1557: de nas stag lpags kyis dbang bskur ba /
NG0204:1558: hum zhe sdang drag po stag gi sham thabs can //
NG0204:1559: stag lpags sham thabs dpa' dang ldan pa yi //
NG0204:1560: gdug chom mdoms su bsnol bas phyi nang gsang bar
NG0204:1561: gcig / phrag dog gnas 'joms stag lpags dbang bskur
NG0204:1562: bas // zhe sdang gnas 'joms phrag dog kun rgyal ba'i //
NG0204:1563: dbang mchog dam pa gnas 'dir thob par shog /
NG0204:1564: om badzra bya g+h+ri ma su ta hum a b+hi
NG0204:1565: shiny+tsa hum / de nas glang po che'i ko rlon gyis dbang bskur ba /
NG0204:1566: hum glang chen ko rlon brjid du che ba ni //
NG0204:1567: gti mug ma spangs gnas su dag pa'i rgyan //
NG0204:1568: na bza' rgyan gyi sku la mnga' gsol zhing *//
NG0204:1569: thabs kyi ko rlon rgyan gyi dam pa yis //
NG0204:1570: gang la dmigs pa'i gnas mchog 'dir bskur bas //
NG0204:1571: stobs kyi rgyal po'i dbang mchog thob par shog / om mu ha da ra pra sha d+ha hum /
NG0204:1573: de nas bskal pa'i me ris dbang bskur ba /
NG0204:1574: hum 'bar ba 'phro ba'i ye shes thugs rje ldan //
NG0204:1575: gdug pa'i tshogs 'joms nyon mongs dug bsregs pa //
NG0204:1576: ye shes gsal bas phyogs bcu'i mun nag sel //
NG0204:1577: bskal pa'i me dpung 'bar bas dbang bskur bas //
NG0204:1578: bar chod bgegs kyis rtogs pas mi tshugs shing *//
NG0204:1579: mtshan ma 'joms pa'i dbang mchog thob par shog / om badzra dz+wa la ram hum /
NG0204:1581: de nas 'khor lo sogs phyag mtshan gyi dbang bskur ba ni /
NG0204:1582: hum bdud dpung g.yul las rgyal ba'i rtags kyi phyag mtshan te //
NG0204:1583: gdug pa 'dul phyir mtshon cha sna tshogs bsnams //
NG0204:1584: 'khor lo ral gri tho ba dang *//
NG0204:1585: thod pa sdigs mdzub phur pa sogs //
NG0204:1586: gdug pa'i mtshon cha sna tshogs kyis //
NG0204:1587: dpa' bo bdud las kun tu rgyal ba dang *//
NG0204:1588: tsham rngams rtags kyis drag shul 'dul ba dang *//
NG0204:1589: nyon mongs tshar gcod gdug pa kun 'dul ba'i /
NG0204:1590: khams gsum dregs pa kun las rgyal ba yi //
NG0204:1591: dbang mchog dam pa nges pa thob par shog / om badzra tsakra khad+ga /
NG0204:1593: dze ru ki la ya hum /
NG0204:1595: zhag gi tshom bus dbang bskur ba //
NG0204:1596: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang *//
NG0204:1597: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NG0204:1598: zhing chen gsar rnying ti rar bcas //
NG0204:1599: dmar gyi ar+g+ham rgya mtshor bskyil //
NG0204:1600: zhag gi tshom bus mtshon pa yis //
NG0204:1601: 'di yang sngon gyi dam tshig la //
NG0204:1602: 'di yang rtags kyi phyag rgya ste //
NG0204:1603: chos nyid zhag gis brgyan pa yi //
NG0204:1604: zhag gi tshom bus dbang bskur bas //
NG0204:1605: chos kyi dbyings su rgyal ba dang *//
NG0204:1606: gdug pa thams cad 'dul ba dang *//
NG0204:1607: che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa yi //
NG0204:1608: chos nyid zhag gi dbang ni thob par shog / om ma @#//
NG0204:1611: de nas khrag gi thig les dbang bskur ba /
NG0204:1612: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang *//
NG0204:1613: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NG0204:1614: dpal chen 'khor bcas spyan drangs te //
NG0204:1615: zhing chen gsar rnying ti rar bcas //
NG0204:1616: dmar gyi ar+g+ham rgya mtshor bskyil /
NG0204:1617: khrag gi thig le mtshan ma 'di //
NG0204:1618: 'di yang sngon gyi dam tshig ste //
NG0204:1619: 'di yang rtags kyi phyag rgya ste //
NG0204:1620: 'dod chags gnas su dag pa yi /
NG0204:1621: khrag gi thig les dbang bskur bas //
NG0204:1622: gtum khro drag po 'joms pa dang *//
NG0204:1623: nga rgyal dregs sems 'dul ba dang *//
NG0204:1624: dbang mchog dam pa thob par shog / om rak+ta ti la ka hum /
NG0204:1625: de nas thal chen gyi mtshan mas dbang bskur te /
NG0204:1626: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang *//
NG0204:1627: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NG0204:1628: dpal chen 'khor bcas spyan drangs te //
NG0204:1629: zhing chen gsar rnying ti rar bcas //
NG0204:1630: dmar gyi ar+g+ham mtsho ltar bskyil //
NG0204:1631: thal ba'i mtshan mas brgyan pa ni //
NG0204:1632: 'di yang sngon gyi dam tshig la //
NG0204:1633: 'di yang rtags kyi phyag rgya ste //
NG0204:1634: gdug pa ma lus rab 'dul ba //
NG0204:1635: snang ba nyid las thig le'i ngang la 'dus //
NG0204:1636: lhun rdzogs mthar phyin yon tan rgyas pa'i dbang thob
NG0204:1637: shog / om dz+nya na badzra swa b+ha ba at+ma
NG0204:1638: ko\u0f85ham / dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:1639: 'bras bu mngon du gyur pa'i dbang gi le'u ste drug pa'o ///
NG0204:1640: / de nas yang gshin rje gshed kyi rgyal po gshed pos /
NG0204:1641: gdul bya'i ched du spyan drang pa 'di gsungs so //
NG0204:1642: dbus kyi khro bo chen po ni //
NG0204:1643: rgyal ba rigs lngas dbu brgyan cing *//
NG0204:1644: ye shes sems dang sku gsung thugs //
NG0204:1645: dkyil 'khor lha tshogs kun gyis byin gyis rlobs //
NG0204:1646: chos sku'i thugs rje chen pos kun khyab kyang *//
NG0204:1647: ma rtogs thugs rjes bsgral ba'i phyir //
NG0204:1648: mnyam pa'i ngang las sku bzhengs gshegs su gsol //
NG0204:1649: om shri many+dzu sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NG0204:1650: hum gti mug mun ltar gtibs pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NG0204:1651: bcom ldan gshin rje'i gshed po spyan 'dren na //
NG0204:1652: 'khor gyi gshin rje ma lus 'dul ba dang *//
NG0204:1653: 'gro drug gti mug ma lus gzhom phyir gnas 'dir spyon //
NG0204:1654: 'dod chags chu ltar 'khrugs pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NG0204:1655: ro langs thal mdog 'khor bcas spyan 'dren na //
NG0204:1656: 'khor gyi dur khrod ma mo 'dul ba dang *//
NG0204:1657: 'gro ba'i 'dod chags gzhom phyir gnas 'dir spyon //
NG0204:1658: zhe sdang me ltar 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NG0204:1659: khro mo e ka tsa ti spyan 'dren na //
NG0204:1660: 'khor gyi srid gsum ma mo 'dul ba dang *//
NG0204:1661: 'gro ba'i zhe sdang gzhom phyir gnas 'dir spyon //
NG0204:1662: nga rgyal ri ltar bsnyil ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NG0204:1663: sras mchog ya ma ra dza spyan 'dren na //
NG0204:1664: 'khor gyi ging bdud mang po 'dul ba dang *//
NG0204:1665: 'gro ba'i nga rgyal 'dul phyir gnas 'dir spyon //
NG0204:1666: phrag mdog rlung ltar 'tshubs pa'i dkyil 'khor nas /
NG0204:1667: khro bo mthar byed gshed chen gshin rje'i @#//
NG0204:1669: ging bdud ma mo mkha' 'gro pho nya'i tshogs //
NG0204:1670: gdug pa'i dgra bo ma lus 'dul ba dang *//
NG0204:1671: 'gro ba'i phrag dog gzhom phyir gnas 'dir spyon //
NG0204:1672: om e h+ye hi b+ha ga wan /
NG0204:1673: a kro te ya man+ta ka a' gats+tsha ya dzahhum bam ho /
NG0204:1674: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las yab yum spyan drangs pa'i le'u ste bdun pa'o ///
NG0204:1675: / de nas yang 'jigs byed chen pos gdul bya'i
NG0204:1676: don du mchod cing bstod pa 'di ched du gsungs
NG0204:1677: so // om na mah sarba ta tha ga ta
NG0204:1678: shri ya man+ta ka de ba man+da la sarba ma
NG0204:1679: so // de / sarba pu dza me g+ha kha hi /
NG0204:1680: om sar+b+ba ta tha ga ta shri ya man+ta ka de wa man+da la sarba ma de /
NG0204:1681: badzra push+pe sarba pu dza me g+ha kha hi /
NG0204:1682: badzra d+hu pe sarba pu dza me g+ha kha hi /
NG0204:1683: badzra ni wid+ya sarba pu dza me g+ha kha hi /
NG0204:1684: badzra girti sarba pu dza me g+ha kha hi /
NG0204:1685: badzra gan+d+ha ga da sarba pu dza me g+ha kha hi /
NG0204:1686: gti mug tshul gyis gti mug 'joms mdzad pa //
NG0204:1687: gti mug chen po gshin rje'i gshed po'i sku //
NG0204:1688: bde gshegs rgyal ba'i sku rnams 'dus pa'i bdag / 'gro ba'i lus kyi bag chags rgyud sbyangs shing *//
NG0204:1689: mi rtog chos dbyings ye shes skur snang ba //
NG0204:1690: 'jigs byed gshin rje'i gshed la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0204:1691: 'dod chags tshul gyis 'dod chags 'joms mdzad pa //
NG0204:1692: 'dod chags chen mo ro langs nag mo'i sku //
NG0204:1693: bde gshegs rgyal ba'i gsung rnams 'dus pa'i bdag / yid kyi rnam shes bag chags rgyud sbyangs nas //
NG0204:1694: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes skur snang ba //
NG0204:1695: ro langs khro mo'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0204:1696: zhe sdang tshul gyis zhe sdang 'joms mdzad cing *//
NG0204:1697: zhe sdang chen mo e ka dza ti'i sku //
NG0204:1698: bde gshegs rgyal ba'i thugs rnams 'dus pa'i bdag / 'gro ba'i kun gzhi'i bag chags rgyud sbyangs shing *//
NG0204:1699: me long lta bu'i ye shes skur snang ba //
NG0204:1700: e ka dza ti'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0204:1701: nga rgyal tshul gyis nga rgyal 'joms mdzad cing *//
NG0204:1702: nga rgyal chen po ya ma ra dza'i sku //
NG0204:1703: bde gshegs rgyal ba'i yon tan kun 'dus bdag / nyon mongs yid kyi bag chags rgyud sbyangs shing *//
NG0204:1704: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes skur snang ba //
NG0204:1705: thugs kyi sras mchog sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0204:1706: phrag dog tshul gyis phrag dog 'joms mdzad pa //
NG0204:1707: phrag dog chen po dam can rgya mtsho'i tshogs //
NG0204:1708: bde gshegs rgyal ba'i phrin las rdzogs mdzad cing *//
NG0204:1709: sgo lnga'i rnam shes bag chags rgyud sbyangs shing *//
NG0204:1710: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes skur snang ba //
NG0204:1711: mthar byed khro bo gshin rje'i tshogs rnams dang *//
NG0204:1712: ging bdud ma mo gshin rje'i pho nya la //
NG0204:1713: phrin las bcol zhing dam tshig bskul phyir bstod //
NG0204:1714: e h+ye hi b+ha ga wan a la la ho //
NG0204:1715: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:1716: mchod bstod kyi le'u ste brgyad pa'o // // de
NG0204:1717: nas 'jigs byed kyi rgyal po khrag 'thung chen po
NG0204:1718: des / brtan par bzhugs shing phyag btsal ba 'di dgos ched @#//
NG0204:1720: hum gshin rje'i gshed po yab yum sras dang 'khor du bcas //
NG0204:1721: thugs rje ye shes gshegs bzhugs mi mnga' yang *//
NG0204:1722: log rtog sems can srid pa sgrol ba dang *//
NG0204:1723: rnal 'byor bsgrub pa'i 'bras bu mthar dbyung phyir //
NG0204:1724: gzugs brnyan bskyed pa'i dkyil 'khor dam pa 'dir //
NG0204:1725: 'khor bcas mi g.yo brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NG0204:1726: shri ya man+ta ka ma ha man+da la sar+b+ba de wa man+dal tish+tha badzra /
NG0204:1727: hum chos nyid mnyam pa'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang *//
NG0204:1728: gdug pa 'dul phyir khro rgyal skur sprul pa //
NG0204:1729: 'jigs byed gshin rje'i gshed la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0204:1730: 'jigs byed sku la mnyes mchod dbul lags na //
NG0204:1731: ro langs khro mo thams cad bskyed pa'i yum //
NG0204:1733: gdug pa'i dgra bgegs ma lus 'dul mdzad ma //
NG0204:1734: sgeg mo ral gcig gu+u h+ya gsang ba'i yum //
NG0204:1735: 'gro ba'i zhe sdang 'joms la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0204:1736: yab yum gnyis med thugs las sprul pa'i sras //
NG0204:1737: ya ma ra dza ging bdud kun gyi gtso //
NG0204:1738: 'gro ba'i nga rgyal 'joms la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0204:1739: bcom ldan gshin rje'i gshed po'i spyan lam du //
NG0204:1740: bdud 'dul bstan pa bsrung bar zhal bzhes pa //
NG0204:1741: ging bdud gshin rje ma mo mkha' 'gro la //
NG0204:1742: rnal 'byor bdag cag re ba'i sems kyis 'dud //
NG0204:1743: a ti pu ho pra tits+tsha ho /
NG0204:1744: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:1745: brtan par bzhugs shing phyag 'tshal ba'i le'u ste dgu pa'o ///
NG0204:1746: / de nas 'jigs byed kyi rgyal po khrag 'thung chen po des /
NG0204:1747: rnal 'byor dam pa rnams kyi ched du /
NG0204:1748: tshogs kyi mchod pa 'di gsungs so //
NG0204:1749: sngon du bya ba'i las byas nas //
NG0204:1750: tshogs gnyis rgyun du bsag pa dang *//
NG0204:1751: dngos grub blang dang las 'chol phyir //
NG0204:1752: tshogs kyi mchod pa dus bzhir dbul //
NG0204:1754: byin rlabs hum phat ldan byas nas //
NG0204:1755: rnal 'byor brtan pas tshogs gnyis bsag / zhes kyang gsungs so //
NG0204:1756: hum mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen po 'di //
NG0204:1757: sems kyis yid bzhin sprin tshogs kyis //
NG0204:1758: phyogs bcu thams cad sangs rgyas zhing *//
NG0204:1759: mnyam sbyor dgyes pa'i mchod pas thim /
NG0204:1760: hum nam mkha'i mtha' klas 'jig rten na //
NG0204:1761: gzugs su snang ba ji snyed kun //
NG0204:1762: sku mchog phyag rgya chen po ste //
NG0204:1763: gshin rje'i gshed po 'khor bcas la //
NG0204:1764: mtshon byed gzugs kyi mchod pa 'bul //
NG0204:1765: sku mchog phyag rgyas mnyes gyur cig / hum nam mkha'i mtha' klas 'jig rten na //
NG0204:1766: sgra ru snang ba ji snyed kun //
NG0204:1767: gsung mchog phyag rgya chen po ste //
NG0204:1768: ro langs khro mo 'khor bcas la //
NG0204:1769: sngags tshig sgra yi mchod pa 'bul //
NG0204:1770: gsung mchog dam pa mnyes gyur cig / hum nam mkha'i mtha' klas 'jig rten na //
NG0204:1771: sems can kun gyi rnam rtog kun //
NG0204:1775: rtse gcig thugs kyi mchod pa 'bul //
NG0204:1776: thugs mchog dam pa mnyes gyur cig / hum nam mkha'i mtha' klas 'jig rten na //
NG0204:1778: de bzhin gshegs pa'i byin brlabs te //
NG0204:1779: ya ma ra dza 'khor bcas la //
NG0204:1781: yon tan mchod pas mnyes gyur cig / hum nam mkha'i mtha' klas 'jig rten na //
NG0204:1782: dge dang mi dge'i las rnams kun //
NG0204:1783: de bzhin gshegs pa'i mdzad spyod de //
NG0204:1784: sprul pa'i dam can 'khor bcas la //
NG0204:1785: skyon bral tshogs kyi mchod pa 'bul //
NG0204:1786: tshogs kyi mchod pas mnyes gyur cig / gzhan yang hum phat sbyor ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NG0204:1787: 'dod pa'i yon tan lngas kyang mchod par bya'o //
NG0204:1788: gzhan yang gdul bya bkug bstim la //
NG0204:1789: rdzogs nas phung po dug gsum mchod par 'bul //
NG0204:1790: sgrol sbyor mchod pa kun kyang thim //
NG0204:1791: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /

NG0204:2116: rgyas par bya ba'i sems kyis su //
NG0204:2117: dkyil 'khor gru bzhi pa yi tshul //
NG0204:2118: ldong ros chag chag btab byas te //
NG0204:2119: rnal 'byor dam pa blo ldan pas //
NG0204:2120: thig ni gdab par rab tu brtsam //
NG0204:2121: gser las grub pa'i thig skud la //
NG0204:2122: dpal dang gzi mdangs bsod nams tshogs //
NG0204:2123: 'phel zhing rgyas pa'i sems dang chas //
NG0204:2124: slob ma dam pa las grub par //
NG0204:2125: bsams la thig ni gdab par bya //
NG0204:2126: pho brang gser la rtse mo g.yu //
NG0204:2127: rdo rje'i brtsigs pa gser las grub //
NG0204:2128: gru chad sgo snams lcags las grub //
NG0204:2129: rnal 'byor sngags pa blo ldan pas //
NG0204:2130: thig bzhir re cha brgyad du 'gyur //
NG0204:2131: mtha' nas thig gdab man ngag can //
NG0204:2132: de la sogs pa bsam par bya //
NG0204:2133: rin chen skyil krung 'dug byas la //
NG0204:2134: rin chen rigs kyi ngos su blta //
NG0204:2135: dbus su gsang sngags bdag po ste //
NG0204:2137: phyogs sgo ba dam pa rnams //
NG0204:2138: snga ma bzhin du bsgoms nas kyang *//
NG0204:2139: rang sngags skyes bus de bskyed do //

NG0204:2141: om a kro te ka push+tim ti ba ta na s+t+wam /
NG0204:2142: zhes pas bdag po yab yum la //
NG0204:2144: rang rang bskyed pa dam pa ste //
NG0204:2145: sngags dang ldan par ting 'dzin bsam //
NG0204:2146: gzhug dang brtan dang mchod pa dang *//
NG0204:2147: phyag byed pa la sogs pa yi //
NG0204:2148: las kyi bya ba ma lus pa //
NG0204:2149: thams cad ma lus tshang bar bya //
NG0204:2150: bskyed dang grub pa'i 'bras bu ni //
NG0204:2151: rgyas par bsnyen te thag mi ring *//
NG0204:2152: rang grub 'bras bu de lags so //
NG0204:2153: phyogs dus kun nas gshegs pa yis //
NG0204:2154: dngos grub dam pa rab ste shes //
NG0204:2155: 'dren pa dpa' bos yang dag bshad //
NG0204:2156: de nas gzhan yang rab bshad pa //
NG0204:2157: dkyil 'khor snga ma bzhin byas la //
NG0204:2158: sa zhag gser las grub pa las //
NG0204:2159: gzugs ni dam pa rab tu bya //
NG0204:2160: phyir rgan gan rkyal gnan byas nas //
NG0204:2161: hum push+tim a yu she swa ha /
NG0204:2162: snying gar bris nas brjod bya ba //
NG0204:2163: snying po sngags kyi dam pa ste //
NG0204:2164: bla med dam pas rab tu bshad //
NG0204:2165: om badzra push+tim a yuhpha la ba sham shri push+tim swa ha /
NG0204:2166: brjod na thams cad rgyas par 'gyur ro //
NG0204:2167: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:2168: thams cad rgyas par bya ba'i skabs te le'u bco lnga pa'o ///
NG0204:2169: / de nas yang phyogs skyong gi gshin rje rnams kyis /
NG0204:2170: phrin las dbang gi sgrub thabs 'di /
NG0204:2171: 'jigs byed gshin rje'i gshed po la phul lo //
NG0204:2172: rab tu dmar zhing zangs las grub //
NG0204:2173: zangs las 'brel ba'i yul dag la //
NG0204:2174: rang dbang med par dbang bsdus nas //
NG0204:2175: 'du ba'i sems dang ldan byas te //
NG0204:2176: dbang gi dkyil 'khor bshad par mdzod //
NG0204:2177: ces pa gshin rje gshed la phul /
NG0204:2178: gshin rje gshed pos bka' stsal pa //
NG0204:2179: nyon cig zung zhig rdo rje 'dzin //
NG0204:2180: thams cad dbang du bsdu phyir du //
NG0204:2181: zangs sam dmar po'i sa dag la //
NG0204:2183: legs par khod snyoms zin pa dang *//
NG0204:2184: thig ni rab tu gdab par bya //
NG0204:2185: lte ba can la rtsibs brgyad la //

NG0204:2192: gzhan yang rab tu bshad bya ba //
NG0204:2193: sems kyi dkyil 'khor dam pa de //
NG0204:2194: bla med yang dag nges pa'i lam //
NG0204:2195: sangs rgyas byang chub la sogs rnams //
NG0204:2196: gzhung las 'byung ba'i tshig don rnams //
NG0204:2197: ma nor gsungs pa'i bka' bzhin du //

NG0204:2200: phal pa gzhan lta smos ci dgos //
NG0204:2201: sdud dang 'dren pa byang chub lam //
NG0204:2203: nyung dkar rkang rjes sa'am gzhan /

NG0204:2206: ga bu [\[]'u [\]]gnyis ni kha sbyar la //

NG0204:2211: bzlas pa'i snying po brjod bya zhing *//
NG0204:2212: lan grangs khri tshar du ma ru //

NG0204:2217: la b+h+rum / lan grangs mang du brjod byas na //

NG0204:2219: rgya shug bkrus pa'i khu ba dang *//

NG0204:2237: gdug pa'i sems dang ldan byas te //
NG0204:2238: drag po'i dkyil 'khor bshad par mdzod //
NG0204:2239: ces pa gshin rje gshed la phul //
NG0204:2240: gshin rje gshed pos bka' stsal pa //

NG0204:2242: phyogs skyong gshin rje ma lus kun /

NG0204:2246: dkyil 'khor snga ma bzhin byas te //

NG0204:2256: gru chad rgyan ldan dur khrod rgyan //

NG0204:2265: @#// zhes brjod pa tsam gyis 'jig rten gyi khams 'di dag g.yos so //

NG0204:2302: sngags dang phyag rgya rdzas rnams dang *//

NG0204:2311: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las //

NG0204:2317: dgon pa lta bur song nas ni //
NG0204:2318: thog mar bsod nams tshogs kyang bsag / phyi bshags 'bum la @#//
NG0204:2320: tsha tsha nye 'don la sogs bya //
NG0204:2321: ye shes sems dpa' bsgom par bya //
NG0204:2323: 'jam dpal mtshan ni yang dag pa //
NG0204:2324: rtag tu gdon par dam yang bca' //
NG0204:2325: grub pa'i nyi ma gang yin la //
NG0204:2326: bsod nams tshogs ni ci nus bsag / de nas drag po byed 'dod na //
NG0204:2327: tha chung bzhi yi mar ngo la //
NG0204:2328: man+dal gtsang ma dris byugs la //
NG0204:2329: dka' thub drag po'i sdom pa byas //
NG0204:2330: ku sha'i stan la 'dug nas ni //
NG0204:2331: mgo bo rma bya bzhin du dgug / ru rak+sha yi phreng ba bgrang *//
NG0204:2332: mgon po nyid la gus byas te //
NG0204:2333: sngon du 'gro ba'i bsnyen pa ni //
NG0204:2334: yi ge bcu bdun nus thang gis //
NG0204:2335: drug 'bum dag tu bzlas pa bya //
NG0204:2336: de ni bsnyen pa dang po yin //
NG0204:2337: phyis ni ri rab rtse mo la //
NG0204:2338: gsum 'bum dag tu bzlas pa bya //
NG0204:2339: de ni bsnyen pa gnyis pa yin //
NG0204:2340: de nas dkyil 'khor gtsang ma'i steng */
NG0204:2343: bzhugs pa'i spyan sngar gnyis 'bum bzlas //
NG0204:2344: de ni bsnyen pa gsum pa ste //
NG0204:2345: bye ba gcig 'bum thon pa dang *//
NG0204:2347: me tog la sogs mchod pa bya //
NG0204:2348: phyi dang nang gi mchod pas mchod //
NG0204:2349: bstod pa la sogs ci rigs bya //
NG0204:2350: bsnyen pa rdzogs nas rtags rnam 'byung *//
NG0204:2352: rtags ni bzang po 'byung ba ni //
NG0204:2353: dngos grub la sogs blang bar bya //

NG0204:2355: mi skra ro tshil rab blangs te /
NG0204:2356: khrag chen dag tu spang bar bya /
NG0204:2357: khrag sna tshogs kyi khu bas bkru //
NG0204:2358: brtsir la thal chen sa dkar gyis //
NG0204:2359: mdog bsgyur phur bzhis brgyang la bskam //
NG0204:2360: zla ba nag po'i tshes drug nas //
NG0204:2361: brtsams te phyir gtor la sogs gtang *//
NG0204:2362: mtho gzug dpang gzug gser skyems gtang *//
NG0204:2363: srid pa'i lha 'dre sde brgyad la //
NG0204:2364: bden bdar rgyab brten ma byed bsgo //
NG0204:2365: khram dmar btab la khrag nag la //
NG0204:2366: gshin rje'i drag sngags dag dang bsgrag / shwa rde'u dkar nag brdeg par bya'o //
NG0204:2368: zla ba nag po'i tshes drug ni //
NG0204:2369: nyi shu gcig la dbu btsug nas //
NG0204:2370: nyi shu drug ni tshun chod du //
NG0204:2371: nus thang du ni bzlas pa bya //
NG0204:2372: om hrihsh+t+r-ihbi kr-i ta na na hum hum phat phat /
NG0204:2373: che ge mo ma ra ya hum phat /
NG0204:2374: nyin phyed tshun chod bzlas pa bya //
NG0204:2375: mchod dang bstod pa la sogs bya //
NG0204:2376: brgyangs pa'i ras chen blang nas su //
NG0204:2377: gzhan med sol ba thal ba gnyis //
NG0204:2378: ka na ka yi khu ba dang *//
NG0204:2379: sbrang rtsi sogs dang dug sna tshogs //
NG0204:2380: til dang nyung dkar mar khu dang *//
NG0204:2381: rang gi srin lag khrag sna ni //
NG0204:2382: rnyed na phyi sa ra khrag dang *//
NG0204:2383: ske tshe sa dkar tsan+dan dang *//
NG0204:2384: rgya skyegs ldong ros yung bas bris //
NG0204:2385: ma ra gshin rje'i lto bar bcug / dbang ni chung ma'i snying gar bya //
NG0204:2386: zhi ba tsan+d+ra'i dbus su bya //
NG0204:2391: lkugs pa lug gi khog par bya //
NG0204:2392: gnan pa ri rab 'og tu bya //
NG0204:2393: so so'i rdzas dang las rnams ni //

NG0204:2399: 'khor lo bca' ba'i rim pa ni //
NG0204:2400: brgyangs pa'i ras la dug byugs la //
NG0204:2401: ma da tsha man+dal sdum bu thang phrom dang */
NG0204:2402: kha shog dug sna tshogs rnams la //
NG0204:2403: rang gi srin las khrag dang sbyar //
NG0204:2404: snag tsha byas la bri bar bya //
NG0204:2406: mi grir shi ba'i skra la yang *//
NG0204:2407: pir la sogs pa bya bar gsungs //
NG0204:2408: sgro rtsa skud pa sngo dmar bcing *//
NG0204:2409: 'khor lo bri ba'i rim pa yang *//
NG0204:2410: gsang ba'i las su shes par bya //
NG0204:2411: 'khor lo bris nas smon lam gdab //
NG0204:2412: rang gi a mr-i ta la sogs //
NG0204:2413: mchod cing bstod pa la sogs bya //
NG0204:2414: bdag nyid ya man+ta kar bsgom //
NG0204:2415: sku mdog stang zil nag po'am //
NG0204:2416: chu rlabs nag po'i sprin dang 'dra /
NG0204:2417: kham nag ral pa gyen du brdzes //

NG0204:2420: ljags 'dril tshems gtsigs sus khyim che //

NG0204:2422: ro nye kha nas 'dzag kyang 'dzab kyang zlos //
NG0204:2423: gdug pa'i mtshon cha sna tshogs 'dzin //

NG0204:2425: mkhas pas rang gi rig pas dpyad //
