NG0204:2428: sngon dmar brgyangs la yas man dgab //
NG0204:2429: nyi shu bdun gyi snga dro la //
NG0204:2430: nyi ma ri rab rtser shar nas //
NG0204:2431: stag lpags bgo zhing bgrod dkar 'gro //
NG0204:2432: ru rak+sha yi phreng ba bgrang *//
NG0204:2433: dbyug to thogs la sdigs mdzub bsgreng *//
NG0204:2434: phyag kyang mi 'tshal lam mi bzur //
NG0204:2435: phrad na gang yin brlag par byed //
NG0204:2436: smra bcad byas te khri khri bzlas //
NG0204:2437: rnal 'byor nang la gtam zer na //
NG0204:2438: lag gi brda yi gdab par bya //
NG0204:2439: skom dang zas ni 'dod pa'i phyir //
NG0204:2440: lag gi brda yis blang bar bya //
NG0204:2441: smras na rnal 'byor rang don zad //
NG0204:2442: de yi phyir na lag brda bya //
NG0204:2443: de yi tshe na 'di yang gdon //
NG0204:2444: ya ma ra dza sa do me ya che ge mo'i pra ma ya hum phat /
NG0204:2445: de nas dmar thag chad bar du /
NG0204:2446: khri khri bzlas pa bya ba yin //
NG0204:2447: dmar thag chad nas sngags gzhug gcad //
NG0204:2448: phur bu gdab dang nyung dkar brdeg / pho nya bcol bskul drag tu bya //
NG0204:2449: ma nyes dpang btsug cho nges gdab //
NG0204:2450: nyin gnyis pa la 'di yang gdon //
NG0204:2451: ya me do ru na yo da ya che ge mo rak+ta tsa ra hum phat /
NG0204:2452: dmar thag chad nas sngags gzhug gcad //
NG0204:2453: las kyi rim pa gong dang 'dra //
NG0204:2454: nyin gsum po la 'di yang gdon //
NG0204:2455: ya da yo ni ra ya k+she ya che ge mo mur tsa ya hum phat /
NG0204:2456: dmar thag chad nas sngags gzhug @#//
NG0204:2458: las kyi rim pa gong dang 'dra //
NG0204:2459: nyin bzhi pa la 'di yang gdon //
NG0204:2460: ya k+she yats+tsha ni ra ma ya che ge mo zhig ma ra ya hum phat /
NG0204:2462: gdab yig nyi shu rtsa lnga ni //
NG0204:2463: mnan pa'i 'khor lo gzhug par bya //
NG0204:2464: mnan pa'i gzugs ni ri rab bri //
NG0204:2465: thod par rabs chad nag po'am //
NG0204:2466: ngag dig glen pa bkra mi shis //
NG0204:2467: nang du bcug la re bar 'gril //
NG0204:2468: lha khang them pa'i 'og dag gam //
NG0204:2469: ro khang dur khrod dag tu gnan //
NG0204:2470: gtad pa gshin rje nyid la ste //
NG0204:2471: dong ni ral pa tshar dgu'o //
NG0204:2472: rgya mtsho chen po'i 'og tu gnan //
NG0204:2473: gnan pa'i lha ni ral pa tshar dgu ste //
NG0204:2474: chu nag 'dra ba'i gzugs chen la //
NG0204:2475: ma he nag po dag la bskyon //
NG0204:2476: gshin rje'i dbyug pa nag po thogs //
NG0204:2477: de lta bu yi dngos po la //
NG0204:2478: bdag gis ral gri'i phyag rgya bcas //
NG0204:2479: sa gzhi chen po gshags nas ni //
NG0204:2480: gshin rje yi ni lag tu gtad //
NG0204:2481: ri rab chen po nyid kyis mnan //
NG0204:2482: don yod grub pa'i pho brang gdab //
NG0204:2483: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:2484: drag po bca' gzhi'i skabs te le'u bcu dgu pa'o
NG0204:2485: // // de nas yang bcom ldan 'das 'jigs byed
NG0204:2486: chen pos 'di skad ces bka' stsal to //
NG0204:2487: drag po'i las dag byed 'dod pas //
NG0204:2488: yid 'ong mthun pa'i gnas lam du //
NG0204:2489: rnal 'byor mos dang dad pa yis //
NG0204:2490: bla ma mnyes byas dbang dag mnos //
NG0204:2491: lung dang man ngag thob nas kyang *//
NG0204:2492: brtson 'grus chen pos myur du bsgrub //
NG0204:2493: gnas dang gzungs ma dag dang ni //
NG0204:2494: lta spyod ldan pa dag gis kyang *//
NG0204:2495: 'khor lo'i rgyu dang snag tsha'i rgyu //
NG0204:2496: smyu gu'i rgyu dang dus phyogs dang *//
NG0204:2497: mkhas pas zla gsang rgyud nas bshad //
NG0204:2498: drag po sa yi man+dal yang *//
NG0204:2499: bskrad dang bzung dang bslang ba sogs //
NG0204:2500: mkhas pas zla gsang rgyud las so //
NG0204:2501: drag po'i dkyil 'khor bri ba yang *//
NG0204:2502: thig g.yog mtshan ldan gzungs ma la //
NG0204:2503: ba su ta yi thig dang thal chen tshon rgyu dang *//
NG0204:2504: rgyud dang man ngag shes pas bya //
NG0204:2505: shar nub lho dang phyogs dang mtshams //
NG0204:2506: phyogs cha rig pas blta bar bya //
NG0204:2507: stegs bu 'dom gang gru bzhi la //
NG0204:2508: chag chag gsum dang skyang nul yang *//
NG0204:2509: zla gsang rgyud las shes par bya //
NG0204:2510: byin rlobs gnam sa thig btab pa //
NG0204:2511: zla gsang las las shes par bya //
NG0204:2512: thig ni brgyad kyi cha ru bya //
NG0204:2513: thig skor bzhi dang ldan pa la //
NG0204:2514: thig skor gsum la thig gsum gdab //
NG0204:2515: le'u tshe dag ni dgu ru 'gyur //
NG0204:2516: phyi rol thig skor rdo rje'i rwa //
NG0204:2517: thig skor gnyis pa dag la ni //
NG0204:2518: bcu gnyis rtsibs dang ldan par bya //
NG0204:2519: ya ma me da k+she zhes bya //
NG0204:2520: phyogs bzhi dbus kyi le'u tshe //
NG0204:2521: drag po sngags kyi yi ge dgod //
NG0204:2522: bcu gnyis rtsibs dang ldan pa la //
NG0204:2523: ra dza sa do bzhi dag dgod //
NG0204:2524: ru na yo ni dag dang yang *//
NG0204:2525: ra ya tsa ni zhes pa ni //
NG0204:2526: 'khor lo'i rtsibs la dgod par bya //
NG0204:2529: bcu drug rtsibs dang ldan pa la //
NG0204:2530: hrihsh+t+r-ih'i sngags kyi yi ge dag / bsgrub bya'i ming dang spel la dgod //
NG0204:2531: rdo rje rwa ba'i phyi rol du //
NG0204:2532: sgo dang sgo khyud ldan pa bya //
NG0204:2533: dbus ni drag po gru gsum gnag / ling tse bzhi ni phyogs dang sbyar //
NG0204:2534: sa stong mdzes pa'i tshon du gtang *//
NG0204:2535: bcu gnyis drag po bcu drug rgyas //
NG0204:2536: rdo rje lcags la gru chad ljang *//
NG0204:2537: mtha' ma lcags ri sgo ni phyogs dang sbyar //
NG0204:2538: gshin rje lha ni lho shar byang *//
NG0204:2539: bu don lho yi phyogs su dgram //
NG0204:2540: sha khrag rdzas dang me tog sngo //
NG0204:2541: lho yi phyogs nas dbul bar bya //
NG0204:2542: drag po rdzas kyi ga bu [\[]'u [\]]de //
NG0204:2543: mnga' gsol dbang bskur byas nas kyang *//
NG0204:2544: dkyil 'khor steng du bzhugs su gsol //
NG0204:2545: 'khor lo bcu gnyis rtse la yang *//
NG0204:2546: phur pa bcu gnyis rim gyis so //
NG0204:2547: 'khor lo bcu drug rtse mo la //
NG0204:2548: ke sing bcu drug phur pa dgod //
NG0204:2549: sgo bzhi sre mo'i phur pa bzhi //
NG0204:2550: nyi shu rtsa brgyad rtsang la yang *//
NG0204:2551: dbang phyug mnga' gsol bar khyams la'o //
NG0204:2552: bsgrub bya'i dam rdzas gtor ma yang *//
NG0204:2553: bsgrub bya'i lha ste dpal la gcig / bsnyen pa'i
NG0204:2554: lha ste ya man+ta kar gcig / las su gnyer
NG0204:2555: ba'i lha ste nyi ma bzhi pa la gcig /
NG0204:2556: phrin las gnyer ba'i lha ste gri thogs ging dang
NG0204:2557: khram thogs bdud la gcig / ma mo'i tshogs la
NG0204:2558: gcig kyang dbul // zhi khro'i lha la las gzhung bsrang *//
NG0204:2559: de nas 'chi bdag las gzhung bsrang *//
NG0204:2560: zhes pa gshin rje gshen pos bshad //
NG0204:2561: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:2562: dkyil 'khor gyi bca' gzhi'i le'u ste nyi shu pa'o ///
NG0204:2563: / de nas mthu stobs kyi bdag po dpal phyag na rdo rje la 'di skad ces zhus so //
NG0204:2564: he he dpa' bo 'jam pa'i mgon //
NG0204:2565: phyogs skyong 'dul ba'i gshed po ste //
NG0204:2567: tshul bzhin bsgrub pa'i don bshad kyang *//
NG0204:2568: phrin las gzhung bsrang ji ltar bsrang *//
NG0204:2569: ting 'dzin rnam gsum ji ltar bskyed //
NG0204:2570: spyan drang bzhugs mchod ji ltar bgyi //
NG0204:2572: dpa' bo chen pos bka' stsol cig / de nas
NG0204:2573: bcom ldan 'das 'jigs byed chen pos phrin las kyi
NG0204:2575: dmar nag brag gam sog po khros pa 'dra //
NG0204:2576: mi ro mang po yod cing rkang gcig shing gi rtsar //
NG0204:2577: gcan gzan mang po 'grul zhing 'dab chags mang po 'du //
NG0204:2578: lha 'dre mang po tshogs par drag po'i gnas btsal te //
NG0204:2579: mchod pa bshams la dkon mchog gsum po spyan drangs la //
NG0204:2580: mnyes par bya phyir mchod pa rnam lnga 'bul //
NG0204:2581: sa bdag sa srin mang po spyan drangs la //
NG0204:2582: gtor ma chang phud mchod rdzas byin brlabs te //
NG0204:2583: bsngos la sa slong tshig kyang brjod //
NG0204:2584: nga rgyal rdo rje khro bo yis //
NG0204:2585: rdo rje'i 'gros kyis sa bskor te //
NG0204:2586: sa bslang sa gzhi sbyang ba ni //
NG0204:2589: ram las ye shes me yis dngos mtshan kun bsregs te //
NG0204:2590: yam las rlung gis gtor nas kham las chu yis bkrus //
NG0204:2591: don dam stong pa'i ngang du bsgom //
NG0204:2592: de nas kun rdzob mtshams bcad de //
NG0204:2593: dkyil 'khor rgya bcad dbus su bskor bar bya //
NG0204:2594: rin chen sna lnga ldan pa'i chang phud sba //
NG0204:2595: phung shul sa blangs mi rta'i khrag gis ljib //
NG0204:2596: sa sbyangs grub nas dur khrod chag chag gdab //
NG0204:2597: rdo rje dri chu rak+ta dang *//
NG0204:2598: dug la sogs pa'i chag chag rab tu gdab //
NG0204:2599: de nas thig gdab thig gi rgyu bstan pa //
NG0204:2600: zhing gi rgyu ma yugs mo'i skra //
NG0204:2601: gri bo log gnon ro sha kha ral skras //
NG0204:2602: thig skud byas la byin brlab thig kyang gdab //
NG0204:2603: shar dang nub dang de bzhin byang *//
NG0204:2604: de bzhin byang shar mtshams su bya'o //
NG0204:2605: shar lho nub byang lho nub dang *//
NG0204:2606: de bzhin byang shar mtshams su'o //
NG0204:2607: dbus kyi shar nub dbus kyi lho dang byang *//
NG0204:2608: snam bu brgyad la gnyis gnyis bcu drug dag tu bshad //
NG0204:2609: mtha' thig la sogs bri ba'i las su shes //
NG0204:2610: dang po dur khrod ras brgyangs te //
NG0204:2611: 'khor lo bri ba man ngag las su shes //
NG0204:2612: ma ra ya yi gzugs bcas la //
NG0204:2613: dri chen dri chu rkang rjes sa //
NG0204:2614: ngar snabs gos kyi dum bu la //
NG0204:2615: nang du tsher ma rus pas dgang *//
NG0204:2616: ming rus mgo dang snying gar gzhug / lus la
NG0204:2617: dug chu tsha ba gsum gyis byug / skud pa
NG0204:2619: skud pa nag po dag gis ske nas gdabs //
NG0204:2620: de nas thod pa mtshan ngan zhig btsal te //
NG0204:2621: lus kyi ngos la yab bri sbyi bo'i ngos la yum //
NG0204:2622: de bzhin gzugs de 'khor lo'i bar du gzhug /
NG0204:2623: 'khor lo thod pa'i nang du gzhug / mi lpags
NG0204:2625: de nas phur pa bcu gcig la //
NG0204:2626: gu gul dud pas rab tu bdug / yungs kar
NG0204:2627: rgyal po dag kyang brdeg / gru gsum dbyings nas
NG0204:2629: spyan drang bzhugs su gsol te rang rang gdan la dgod //
NG0204:2630: shar du kong tse brag gyon dri za 'dul //
NG0204:2631: lho phyogs 'chi bdag ya ba ti //
NG0204:2632: nub tu klu bdag rmig pa 'dul //
NG0204:2633: byang du lha mchog gnod sbyin 'dul //
NG0204:2634: shar lhor glang mgo me lha 'dul //
NG0204:2635: lho nub mig dmar srin po 'dul //
NG0204:2636: nub byang tel pa rlung lha 'dul //
NG0204:2637: byang shar las grub dbang ldan 'dul //
NG0204:2640: de dag gshin rje'i yum rnams kyang *//
NG0204:2641: phur pa rang rang grib la gnas //
NG0204:2642: ku ma da ri bdud 'dul shar //
NG0204:2643: k+shu ma da ri btsan 'dul lho //
NG0204:2644: kang ka da ri gza' 'dul nub //
NG0204:2645: tsa mun da ri klu 'dul byang *//
NG0204:2646: phur pa bzhi yang sgo bzhi la'o //
NG0204:2647: gshin rje'i bris sku lho ru dgram //
NG0204:2648: thod pa 'khor lo bcas pa ste //
NG0204:2649: gru gsum phub ste steng du gzhag / g.yang gzhi 'phan la sogs pas brgyan //
NG0204:2650: sha chen tshil chen keng rus dang */
NG0204:2653: ske thag gshin rje'i phur la gdags //
NG0204:2654: gtor ma la sogs gong bzhin gzhag / nyung dkar ske tshe dug khrag rnams //
NG0204:2655: g.yas g.yon dag tu gzhag par bya //
NG0204:2656: mchod pa lnga dang gtor ma gsum //
NG0204:2657: chang phud la sogs bshams nas kyang *//
NG0204:2658: dkon mchog gsum po spyan drangs la //
NG0204:2659: mchod dang sdig pa bshags pa bya //
NG0204:2660: de nas chos kyi srung ma rnams //
NG0204:2661: lha mgon klu mgon la sogs dang *//
NG0204:2662: bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad cu dang *//
NG0204:2663: 'gro ba drug rnams la sogs par //
NG0204:2664: gtor ma bsngos la bden pa bdar //
NG0204:2665: 'di yi grogs ma byed par bsgo //
NG0204:2666: dkyil 'khor bskor zhing dpang yang gzug / mtha' ma rdo rje'i 'gros kyis bskor //
NG0204:2667: bgegs rnams bskrad la mtshams rnams gcad //
NG0204:2668: de nas lho ru kha yang blta //
NG0204:2669: de bzhin nyid dang kun tu snang *//
NG0204:2670: rgyu dang ting 'dzin rnam gsum bsgom //
NG0204:2671: e yam ra sum kem ram b+h+ru~m las //
NG0204:2672: gzhal yas gdan bcas gsal bar bsgom //
NG0204:2673: de nang lha rnams gsal bar bsgom //
NG0204:2674: dbus kyi ma he'i gdan thog tu //
NG0204:2675: mthing nag 'bar ba'i hum gcig bsgom //
NG0204:2677: phyag mtshan rdo rje gcig tu gyur //
NG0204:2679: rdo rje mthing nag 'od du gyur //
NG0204:2680: om a kro te ka ya man+ta ka ka la ru pa badzra kro d+ha hum phat /
NG0204:2683: zhal gsum phyag drug mthing nag la //
NG0204:2684: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NG0204:2685: ral pa'i rtse las me 'bar ba'i //
NG0204:2686: ral pa'i sked nas khrag 'dzag pa'i //
NG0204:2687: ral pa'i rtse nas rgya mtsho 'khrugs //
NG0204:2688: sdigs mdzub rgyu zhags lcags kyu g.yas //
NG0204:2689: dung dmar mdung thung gsal shing g.yon //
NG0204:2690: zhabs bzhi brkyang bskum ma he brdzis //
NG0204:2691: dur khrod rgyan gyi rab tu brgyan //
NG0204:2692: klad par om bsam mgrin par amh / tsit+ta'i nang du hum gcig bsam //
NG0204:2693: ye shes lnga ru byin brlabs te /
NG0204:2694: a+om sarba ta tha ga ta ma ha kro d+ha dz+nya na pany+tsa swa  b+ha wa at+ma ko\u0f85 ham //
NG0204:2695: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlabs te /
NG0204:2696: om sarba ta tha ga ta ka ya waka tsit+ta at+ma ko\u0f85ham /
NG0204:2697: khro bo'i nga rgyal bskyed pa la //
NG0204:2698: om sarba ta tha ga ya man+ta ka ma ha kro d+ha hum /
NG0204:2699: de nas hum zhes rab brjod pas /
NG0204:2700: khro bo'i thugs kar hum bton te //
NG0204:2701: g.yon phyogs zhing gi gdan stengs su /
NG0204:2702: hum de 'phros shing gnas pa las /
NG0204:2703: om ahhum be ta li rak+sha man /
NG0204:2704: brjod pas hum nyid yum du gyur /
NG0204:2705: khram bam g.yas la b+han+d+ha g.yon //
NG0204:2706: sku mdog nag mo gsal bar bskyed //
NG0204:2707: yab kyi gsang ba'i rdo rje ste //
NG0204:2708: om las nor bu bu gar phat //
NG0204:2709: de nas yum gyi gsang gnas su //
NG0204:2711: e las nang du gru gsum ste //
NG0204:2712: 'di skad brjod la gsang sgo dbye //
NG0204:2713: pad+ma gu h+ya pra we sha phat /
NG0204:2714: ces brjod gsang sgo phye ba yis //
NG0204:2717: lhag pa'i byang chub sems nyid de //
NG0204:2718: rdo rje'i lam nas rab byung ste //
NG0204:2719: yum gyi mkha' la 'phros pa dang *//
NG0204:2720: de la hum zhes brjod pa yis //
NG0204:2721: byang sems hum bsgril bcur gyur te //
NG0204:2722: mkha' las bton nas 'khor lo yi //
NG0204:2723: rtsibs kyi steng du gdan steng du //
NG0204:2724: hum hum bsgril ma re re bsam //
NG0204:2725: 'khor lo shar gyi rtsibs gdan la //
NG0204:2726: hum hum bsgril ma de nyid las //
NG0204:2727: om ya man badzra kro d+ha hum /
NG0204:2728: om ya man badzra kro d+hi hum /  brjod pas hum las khro bo'i sku //
NG0204:2729: kong tse brag gyon kham rgya ma //
NG0204:2730: zhal gcig phyag gnyis sku mdog gnag / dur khrod rgyan dang ldan pa ste //
NG0204:2731: g.yon pa b+han dmar yum la 'khyud //
NG0204:2732: g.yas pa bdug pa'i mtshon cha 'dzin //
NG0204:2733: yum yang g.yas kyis yab la 'khyud //
NG0204:2734: g.yon pa dung dmar yab la stob //
NG0204:2735: dur khrod rgyan rnams yab dang mthun //
NG0204:2736: rtsa ba'i sngags de brjod nas kyang *//
NG0204:2737: phyogs skyong yab yum kun kyang bskyed //
NG0204:2738: rgyan dang cha lugs phyag mtshan rnams //
NG0204:2739: gong bzhin thams cad gsal bar bskyed //
NG0204:2740: g.yas kyi hum las yab tu bskyed //
NG0204:2741: g.yon gyi hum las yum du bskyed //
NG0204:2745: b+h+yo las du khrod ma mo gsum //
NG0204:2746: zla gam gsum la bskyed par bya //
NG0204:2747: sgo bzhir rdo rje bse mo bzhi //
NG0204:2748: ku la d+ha ri shar du+u bskyed //
NG0204:2749: k+shu la d+ha ri lho ru bskyed //
NG0204:2750: kang ka d+ha ri nub tu bskyed //
NG0204:2751: tsa mun d+ha ri byang du ba skyed //
NG0204:2752: ke'u sing dbang phyug ging dang bdud //
NG0204:2753: man ngag las su shes par bshad //
NG0204:2755: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:2756: drag po'i phrin las kyi skabs te le'u nyer gcig pa'o ///
NG0204:2757: / de nas yang bcom ldan 'das 'jigs byed chen pos drag po 'khor lo'i skabs 'di gsungs so //
NG0204:2758: dur khrod ro ras rnying pa'am //
NG0204:2759: gri bor shi ba'i ro shul la //
NG0204:2760: mi tshig la sogs mi smra bar //
NG0204:2761: ske tshe lan tshwa nyung nag mar //
NG0204:2762: dug dang nim pa'i lo ma dang *//
NG0204:2763: ka na ka yi khu ba dang *//
NG0204:2764: ro bsreg pa yi sol ba dang *//
NG0204:2765: rang ngam phal gyi mdzub mo'i khrag / de rnams sbyar la snag tsha bya'o //
NG0204:2766: bya rog hu lu'i sgro rtsa la //
NG0204:2767: 'khor lo bri ba'i smyu gu bya //
NG0204:2768: 'khor lo rtsibs can gnyis bris te //
NG0204:2769: srid gsum sems can thams cad kun //
NG0204:2770: gshin rje'i lto na yod rtags su //
NG0204:2771: 'khor lo rim pa gsum du+u bri //
NG0204:2772: dbus su re'u mig dgu par bya //
NG0204:2773: phyi rim rtsibs ni bcu gnyis bri //
NG0204:2774: tha ma dag la bcu drug bya //
NG0204:2775: yab yum 'khor lo dag la bskyon //
NG0204:2776: 'khor lo'i nang du sngags bri ba //
NG0204:2777: re'u cha dgu dang bcu gnyis la //
NG0204:2778: nyi ma bzhi yi gshed bzhi bri //
NG0204:2779: bcu drug hrihsh+t+r-ih dam dam 'di med pa mang dam dam dam tshigs sngags //
NG0204:2780: phyi rim ka kha bzhi bcu gnyis //
NG0204:2781: yang rim dbyangs yig bcu drug bri //
NG0204:2782: de yi phyi mar yang rim la //
NG0204:2783: dzahhum bam hoh bri bar bya //
NG0204:2784: yi ge re ga re'u mig
NG0204:2787: de yang pho yi 'khor lo ni //
NG0204:2788: yi ge'i kha rnams phyir la bstan //
NG0204:2789: mo yig rnams ni nang du bstan //
NG0204:2795: do dang do mnyam ru dang    //
NG0204:2796: na dang na mnyam yo dang  no //
NG0204:2797: da dang da mnyam ya dang [  ]//
NG0204:2800: ra dang ra mnyam ya dang [  ]//
NG0204:2804: ni dang ni mnyam ra dang [  ]//
NG0204:2806: g.yas skor g.yon skor pho mo gnyis //
NG0204:2807: ma nor ma log bri ba gces //
NG0204:2808: dam tshig yi ge dgod pa yang *//
NG0204:2811: kr-i dang kri mnyam ta dang ta //
NG0204:2812: na dang na mnyam na dang na /
NG0204:2813: che dang cha mnyam ge dang   //
NG0204:2817: dam tshig yi ge dgod par yang *//
NG0204:2818: ka kha dbyangs yig la sogs te //
NG0204:2819: yi ge rnams kyi dgod phyogs so //
NG0204:2820: gnyis ka rnal mar bris gyur na //
NG0204:2821: yab yum cho rol song gyur te //
NG0204:2823: de la dgug dang gnan dang myos //
NG0204:2824: bskrad dang myos 'bros la sogs pa //
NG0204:2825: zla gsang las las shes par bya //
NG0204:2826: de ltar 'khor lo bri ba dang *//
NG0204:2827: rabs chad pho mo'i thod pa dang *//
NG0204:2828: 'khor lo gong ma ltar bris la //
NG0204:2829: de yi bar du bcug byas la //
NG0204:2830: tshon skud nag pos phyogs bzhir bcings //
NG0204:2831: gzhan yang zhi rgyas las byed na /
NG0204:2832: kham sa'i gab tser gong bzhin bzhug / so so'i rigs kyi gzungs thag gdags /
NG0204:2833: de yis gang yang gdon mi za //
NG0204:2834: las rnams 'grub ces gshed pos gsungs //
NG0204:2835: dpal gshin rje zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:2836: 'khor lo bca' gzhi'i skabs te le'u nyer gnyis pa'o ///
NG0204:2837: / de nas yang bcom ldan 'das 'jigs byed chen pos 'di skad ces gsungs so //
NG0204:2838: dang por ting 'dzin rnam gsum gyis //
NG0204:2839: las kyi bya ba gzhan zin nas //
NG0204:2841: ngas gsungs pa la sems thud cig / hum /
NG0204:2842: log rtog gzung 'dzin 'khrul pa'i chos nyid de //
NG0204:2843: sems kyi brtags pas cir yang mi snang ste //
NG0204:2844: mi g.yo mi bsam chos kyi dbyings nyid ngang *//
NG0204:2845: rig pa spros bral mi rtog bsgom //
NG0204:2846: om ma ha shu n+ya dz+nya na badzra swa b+ha wa at+ma ko\u0f85ham /
NG0204:2848: dbyings nyid nam mkha' stong pa'i rang bzhin las //
NG0204:2851: 'od kyi thig le nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor bsam //
NG0204:2854: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor 'od kyi dkyil 'khor te //
NG0204:2855: hum las rdo rje rtse lnga rab 'bar ba //
NG0204:2856: brtan cing mi g.yo rdo rje 'bar bar bsgom //
NG0204:2858: rdo rje'i gur dang sa gzhi bsgom //
NG0204:2860: 'jig rten khams gsum ma lus kun //
NG0204:2861: ram yam kham gis bsreg sbyangs nas //
NG0204:2862: ye shes 'bar ba lnga ni rim gyi bsgom //
NG0204:2863: e yam ram bam sum kem e //
NG0204:2864: nam mkha' stong pa'i rang bzhin la //
NG0204:2865: brtan pa rlung gi dkyil 'khor bsgom //
NG0204:2866: de steng ram las gru gsum me //
NG0204:2867: bam las bdud rtsi ngo bo las //
NG0204:2868: smin pa sa yi dkyil 'khor bsam //
NG0204:2869: keng rus ri rab steng dag tu //
NG0204:2870: ye shes 'bar ba'i gzhal yas bsgom //
NG0204:2871: b+h+rum las ye shes 'bar ba'i gzhal yas mchog / gru bzhi sgo bzhi rta babs bcas //
NG0204:2872: dkyil 'khor tshul du gzhal yas bsgom //
NG0204:2874: gzhal yas dbus su nyi zla'i steng *//
NG0204:2875: chu skyes steng du sems nyid d+hih / 'phro 'dus ral gri d+hihsa mtshan pa //
NG0204:2877: om a ra pa tsa na d+hih 'jam pa'i rdo rje gzhon tshul zur phud can //
NG0204:2878: sku ni gser mdog zhi ba'i cha lugs 'chang *//
NG0204:2879: zhal gcig phyag gnyis shes rab ral gri g.yas //
NG0204:2880: gzhon nu'i skur sprul phyag g.yon ut+pal te //
NG0204:2881: mi 'gyur shes rab po tis mtshan par bsgom //
NG0204:2882: snying dkyil nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor d+hi las ni //
NG0204:2883: 'od 'phros phyogs bcu'i bde gshegs spyan drangs nas //
NG0204:2884: nyi ma la zhugs mgon po nyid dang ni //
NG0204:2885: bde gshegs spyan drangs 'od kyi gong bur bsam //
NG0204:2886: 'od dpung de nyid kha dog nag po'i hum //
NG0204:2887: 'phro 'du'i tshul gyis rdo rje rtse lnga gnag / shin tu 'bar zhing brtan pa nyid du bsgom //
NG0204:2888: badzra de las 'od zer rab 'phros pas //
NG0204:2890: khro bo'i rgyal po gshin rje gshed //
NG0204:2891: dbu gsum phyag drug 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NG0204:2892: gyad kyi 'dor thabs yi dwags gnon //
NG0204:2893: tri shul ral gri dbyug dgra s+t+wa //
NG0204:2894: 'byin pa'i phyir na phyag brgyad pa //
NG0204:2895: lcags kyu'i mtshon cha phyag na bsnams //
NG0204:2896: thod pa shag ti to ma ra //
NG0204:2897: sdigs dang zhags pa g.yon pa ste //
NG0204:2898: las la gsang ba'i yum gnyis kyang *//
NG0204:2899: g.yas g.yon gnyis su bsam pa yang *//
NG0204:2900: lus dang grib ma'i tshul du bsgom //
NG0204:2901: om a kro te ka ya man+ta ka hum /
NG0204:2902: be ta li yak+sha rak+sha hum hum /
NG0204:2903: pad+ma rdo rje byin brlab pa //
NG0204:2904: hum las rdo rje rtse lnga pa //
NG0204:2905: pam las pad+mar byin brlabs nas //
NG0204:2906: brda yis bskul ba tshul bzhin bya //
NG0204:2910: ra ga ya mi /  hum /   hum /  hum /   hum /  hum /   hum //
NG0204:2911: yab yum mkha' la hum bcu gnyis //
NG0204:2912: gshin rje bcu gnyis gsal ba'i rtsa //
NG0204:2913: 'khor rnams bsam pa'i dbang gis bskyed //
NG0204:2916: gshin rje gshed pos gsungs pa'i don //
NG0204:2917: dpal gshin rje zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las //
NG0204:2918: bsgom khog gi skabs te le'u nyer gsum pa'o ///
NG0204:2919: / de nas yang mthu stobs bdag pos 'di skad ces zhus so //
NG0204:2920: gshin rje gshed pos gsungs pa'i don //
NG0204:2921: bdag sdud 'di yi don shod cig / bsod nams tshogs kyi yan lag bshad pa dang *//
NG0204:2922: bsnyen pa dang ni nyer bsnyen po //
NG0204:2923: dngos grub len dang bsgrub pa dang *//
NG0204:2924: 'chi bdag bdud dang gshin rje'i bsnyen pa dang *//
NG0204:2925: gsad pa las kyi bsnyen pa gang la bgyi //
NG0204:2926: gshin rje gshed pos bka' stsol gcig / gshin rje gshed pos bka' stsal pa //
NG0204:2927: nyon cig lag na rdo rje 'dzin //
NG0204:2928: 'chi bdag rnams kyi bshad bya ba //
NG0204:2929: ngas gsungs pa la sems thud cig / dang por yid 'thad gnas btsal nas //
NG0204:2931: bsod nams dag pa'i tshogs bsag pa //
NG0204:2932: tshad med bzhi dang yan lag lnga //
NG0204:2933: bdun gyis kun rdzob sems bskyed la //
NG0204:2934: don dam byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa //
NG0204:2935: rnam par mi rtog ngang du ci rigs bsgom //
NG0204:2936: de ltar ma rtogs rnams la snying rje bskyed //
NG0204:2937: ting 'dzin gnyis kyis rang rgyud dag sbyangs nas //
NG0204:2938: rig pa'i yi shes ye ge mum du gsal //
NG0204:2939: spros bsdus 'jam dpal sems dpa'i skur bskyed de //
NG0204:2940: gong ma lta bu'i las dang bya ba ni //
NG0204:2941: bsod nams tshogs kyi las dag go / rdo rje
NG0204:2942: sems dpas rab tu sems la zhog / dpal zla
NG0204:2944: bsod nams tshogs kyi yan lag gi skabs te le'u
NG0204:2945: nyer bzhi pa'o // // de nas 'jam dpal gshin
NG0204:2947: yid 'thad mtshan ldan gnas dag tu //
NG0204:2948: gong gis bsod nams tshogs la gnas pa yang *//
NG0204:2949: phyi nang gsang ba dag gi mtshams bcad nas //
NG0204:2950: zhi khro la sogs bskang bshags dag par bya //
NG0204:2951: de nas ting 'dzin rnam gsum spro bsdu yis //
NG0204:2952: bdag nyid gshin rje'i gshed kyi skur bskyed la //
NG0204:2953: g.yon du yum bskyed mdun du sras mchog bskyed //
NG0204:2954: g.yas su yum bskyed la sogs rab byas te //
NG0204:2955: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlabs pa dang *//
NG0204:2956: ye shes chen po lnga ru dbang bskur nas //
NG0204:2957: ye shes sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor spyan drangs dang *//
NG0204:2958: mchod bstod la sogs rdzogs pa dang *//
NG0204:2959: bdag thugs phyag rgya bzhi las mchod pa'i lha mo bzhi //
NG0204:2960: spros te spyan drangs phyag 'tshal bzhugs pa dang *//
NG0204:2961: mchod pa la sogs lha mo bzhis byas te //
NG0204:2962: bzlas brjod bsnyen pa'i 'dzab grangs dbul ba ni //
NG0204:2963: rang rig ye shes gnas su dag pa'i rtags //
NG0204:2964: snod kyi 'jig rten gzhal yas khang *//
NG0204:2966: dbyings nyid gting mtha' med pa las //
NG0204:2969: gshed po yab dang yum du ma gyur gang yang med //
NG0204:2970: dper na til 'bru mar gyis gang ba bzhin //
NG0204:2971: bdag nyid tsit+ta'i gzhal yas khang *//
NG0204:2972: rin chen gur phub 'dra ba ru //
NG0204:2973: bdag nyid zla ba'i man+dal bsam //
NG0204:2974: rig pa'i ye shes yongs su grub pa'i rtags //
NG0204:2975: ye shes sems dpa' tshon gang gsal bar bsgom //
NG0204:2976: thugs kar rdo rje rtse lnga bsam //
NG0204:2977: de yi bum pa dag la yang *//
NG0204:2978: sngags kyi sa bon yi ge hum //
NG0204:2979: de mtha' bcu bdun bskor ba bsgom //
NG0204:2980: lha rnams thugs kar de bzhin ci 'drar bsgom //
NG0204:2981: de nas bdag nyid thugs ka nas //
NG0204:2982: sngags bzlas ljags steng sngags 'phros pas //
NG0204:2983: 'dom gang pha rol phyir tshad du //
NG0204:2984: sku rnams phra mor gyur nas kyang *//
NG0204:2985: de dag zhal nas gsang sngags bzlas pa las //
NG0204:2986: 'od zer mchod pa'i lha dang lha mor gyur //
NG0204:2987: phar 'phros 'phags pa rnams la 'od zer phog / sku gsung thugs nyid mnyes pa'i mchod pa phul //
NG0204:2988: 'od zer de dag bdag la tshur 'dus pas //
NG0204:2989: sku gsung thugs kyi byin rlabs bdag la thim par bsam //
NG0204:2990: de ltar bsnyen pa drug 'bum byas pa ni //
NG0204:2991: sngon du 'gro ba'i bsnyen pa ste //
NG0204:2992: lag na rdo rjes rab tu zung *//
NG0204:2993: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:2994: lha yi bsnyen pa bgyi ba'i skabs te le'u nyer
NG0204:2995: lnga pa'o // // de nas bcom ldan 'das 'jigs
NG0204:2996: byed chen pos 'di skad ces gsungs so //
NG0204:2997: yid 'thad mtshan ldan gnas dag tu //
NG0204:2998: man+dal chag chag legs btab la //
NG0204:2999: me tog bris sku la sogs bkod nas kyang *//
NG0204:3000: gong ma lta bu'i bsnyen pa gsum 'bum bzlas pa ni //
NG0204:3001: nye ba'i bsnyen pa yin zhes gshed po bshad //
NG0204:3002: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:3003: nye ba'i bsnyen pa'i skabs te le'u nyer drug pa'o
NG0204:3004: // // de nas bcom ldan 'das gshin rje gshed
NG0204:3006: yid 'thad mtshan ldan gnas dag tu //
NG0204:3007: gong ma'i las rnams mthar phyung ste //
NG0204:3008: nye bsnyen las la gnas nas kyang *//
NG0204:3009: des ni rtags bzang mthong bar 'gyur //
NG0204:3010: grub pa'i rtags ni byung ba dang */
NG0204:3011: khyad par dngos grub rdzas bsags te //
NG0204:3012: dmar ser ba yi 'o ma dang *//
NG0204:3013: mar dang sbrang rtsi sbyar ba dang *//
NG0204:3014: dngos grub rdzas rnams bkod nas kyang *//
NG0204:3015: bdag gi thugs las 'od zer phar 'phros pas //
NG0204:3016: bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyi thugs dam bskul //
NG0204:3017: bris sku dngos grub rdzas la thim bsams shing *//
NG0204:3018: 'bum phrag gcig gi bzlas pa bya'o //
NG0204:3019: g.yal dang sbrid pa brkyang bskum gnyid kyang spang *//
NG0204:3020: de bzhin spangs pas ci bsam grub ces bshad //
NG0204:3021: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:3022: bsgrub pa chen po'i skabs te le'u nyer bdun pa'o
NG0204:3023: // // de nas yang gshin rje gshed pos 'di
NG0204:3025: nyon cig zung zhig rdo rje 'dzin //
NG0204:3027: la sems thud cig / yid 'thad mtshan ldan gnas dag tu //
NG0204:3028: 'bum phrag gcig gi bsnyen pa yang *//
NG0204:3029: snga ma'i las su bya bar gsungs //
NG0204:3030: bdag nyid gshed po'i mthu ldan pas //
NG0204:3031: mdun gyi ri rab bsam pa dang *//
NG0204:3032: de bzhin gshegs pa'ang bsam byas te //
NG0204:3033: bdag gi thugs kar yi ge ya //
NG0204:3035: de mthar bzlas pa'i yig 'brus bskor bsam la //
NG0204:3036: de bzhin bdag gi thugs ka nas //
NG0204:3037: sngags ni rab tu bzlas pa las //
NG0204:3039: de yi 'od zer phog gyur pas //
NG0204:3040: thugs dam bskul nas dar cig kyang *//
NG0204:3042: gshed po'i bka' nyan gsung sdod bsam //
NG0204:3043: las la sbyor ba'i bsnyen pa ste //
NG0204:3044: 'chi bdag las kyi gshin rje rnams //
NG0204:3045: gnas su gtong ba gshed pos bshad //
NG0204:3046: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:3047: 'chi bdag bdud dang gshin rje'i bsnyen pa'i skabs te
NG0204:3048: le'u nyer brgyad pa'o // // de nas yang 'di
NG0204:3050: nyon cig zung zhig rdo rje 'dzin //
NG0204:3051: ngas gsungs pa la the tshom med //
NG0204:3052: gsad pa las kyi bsnyen pa ni //
NG0204:3053: yid 'thad mtshan ldan gnas dag tu //
NG0204:3054: gong gi las la gnas byas te //
NG0204:3055: de yang 'chi bdag bsnyen pa ni //
NG0204:3056: sum cu rtsa gnyis dril la bzla zhes bshad //
NG0204:3057: las la sbyor ka'i dus de ru //
NG0204:3058: sna la ro tshas ras btsal te /
NG0204:3059: mas yar bgrang ba'i tshes brgyad dam //
NG0204:3060: nyi shu gnyis kyi nub mo ni //
NG0204:3061: dur khrod gling nas ras blangs la //
NG0204:3062: sme khrag gsum du bcug byas la //
NG0204:3063: 'chi bdag gshin rje de la bstim //
NG0204:3064: yab yum las la sbyor ka yin //
NG0204:3065: sngags 'di nyid kyang rab tu bzlas //
NG0204:3066: om sa ma ya many+dzu shri /
NG0204:3067: a kro te ka ka la ru pa hum phat //
NG0204:3069: nyi shu drug gi snga dro la //
NG0204:3070: ro ras bkru dang brgyang spyad bya //
NG0204:3071: nyid phyed man chad snag tsha mnye //
NG0204:3072: dbang du bsdu ba'i sngags 'di bzlas //
NG0204:3073: om du man+ta ka ra hum hum phat phat /
NG0204:3075: snag tsha mnye ba'i las zin nas //
NG0204:3076: de bzhin dgong ka 'khor lo bri //
NG0204:3077: bri ba zin nas lhar phyag 'tshal //
NG0204:3078: bka' bden pa 'grub par gyur cig ces bya //
NG0204:3079: yang na dur khrod ras med na //
NG0204:3080: thod pa dag la 'khor lo bri //
NG0204:3081: ag tse'i ngos su 'chi bdag gzugs bris la //
NG0204:3082: gzugs kyi snying gar ming byad bris //
NG0204:3083: dgra yi ming rus thod par gzhug / 'khor lo dbus kyi ya las kyang *//
NG0204:3084: 'chi bdag gshed po'i sku ru bskyed //
NG0204:3085: phyogs kyi ya me me de k+she //
NG0204:3086: bzhi las gshed bzhi'i skur bskyed pas //
NG0204:3087: bdag gi mdun du ri rab las //
NG0204:3088: gser gyi ri bdun bcas pa bsam //
NG0204:3089: bdag nyid gshin rje gshed po yi //
NG0204:3090: rnal 'byor cha byad ldan byas la //
NG0204:3091: lag pa g.yas pa'i mthe bong yang *//
NG0204:3092: chang par bcug la be con bsam //
NG0204:3093: ri rab bdag gi sbyir brdeg ste //
NG0204:3094: ri rab rgya gram gas par bsam //
NG0204:3097: om na mo bud+d+ha d+harma sang g+he b+h+yah sarba ta
NG0204:3098: tha ga ta kro d+ha bi dza ya ag+ni dz+wa
NG0204:3099: la ni dza hwa pre ta shi ya hum hum
NG0204:3101: ri rab rgya gram gshag bsam zhing *//
NG0204:3102: gnas kyi gshin rje 'gugs bsam zhing *//
NG0204:3103: thugs ka'i yi ge ya nag po //
NG0204:3104: tha ma dbang sdud sngags gyis bskor ba las //
NG0204:3108: rang dbang med par de bkug nas //
NG0204:3109: de la sha khrag sna tshogs kyis //
NG0204:3110: gtor ma rdzas kyis mchod par bya //
NG0204:3112: dbang du bsdu ba'i sngags bzlas la //
NG0204:3113: bdag las 'phros pa'i gshed po dag / grangs med 'phros pas 'chi bdag tshogs //
NG0204:3114: rang dbang med par bkug byas te //
NG0204:3115: thod pa'i nang du bcug pa la //
NG0204:3116: zhabs g.yas rdo rje'i phur pa yis //
NG0204:3118: rang dbang med par dbang du bsdus //
NG0204:3119: bka' nyan ci gsung brjod par bsgom //
NG0204:3120: skya rengs dang po shar ba la //
NG0204:3122: gtor ma byin te gshin rje nyid //
NG0204:3123: pho nyar bkye la dgra bo 'gug / lha dang dbral la sogs pa bya //
NG0204:3124: nyi ma rtse la shar ba dang *//
NG0204:3125: b+han+da dkyil 'khor gru gsum steng du gzhag / de bzhin bsad pa'i sngags bzlas te //
NG0204:3126: bdag nyid thugs kar yi ge ya //
NG0204:3127: sngo nag gnag la 'tsher ba bsam //
NG0204:3128: tha ma drag sngags 'bru bdun pa //
NG0204:3130: gsad pa las kyi sngags 'di bzlas //
NG0204:3131: om hrihsh+t+r-ihbi kr-i ta na na che ge mo sha trum na sha ya hum phat //
NG0204:3132: ya ma ra dza sa do me ya che ge mo a mu kam pra ma ya hum phat /
NG0204:3134: 'od zer bdag la phog gyur pas //
NG0204:3135: rang dbang med par bskul gyur nas //
NG0204:3136: gshed po ya ma ra dza bskul //
NG0204:3137: de yis phyogs skyong gshin rje bskul //
NG0204:3138: de yis ma mo mkha' 'gro dang *//
NG0204:3139: rdo rje ging pho ging mo dang *//
NG0204:3140: bdud la sogs pa dbang med bskul //
NG0204:3141: de bzhin gzas po dngos bkug nas //
NG0204:3142: thod par bcug ste gnas pa las //
NG0204:3143: gsad pa las kyi sngags bzlas pas //
NG0204:3144: star tshan rtsi sbur mi chags bzhin //
NG0204:3145: gang la bya ba brlag par bsam //
NG0204:3146: dgong gyi dmar thag chad pa dang *//
NG0204:3147: gshed chen ya ma ra dza la //
NG0204:3148: sha khrag sna tshogs gtor ma bsham //
NG0204:3149: be con phyag rgya bcas nas kyang *//
NG0204:3150: gnag pa'i spyi bor de brgyab pas //
NG0204:3151: tshangs pa'i rtsa bcad mgo 'khor bsam //
NG0204:3152: nyi shar rtse nas las brtsams te //
NG0204:3153: bdag nyid thugs kar yi ge ya //
NG0204:3155: gsad pa las kyi sngags 'di bzlas //
NG0204:3156: om hrihsh+t+r-ihbi kr-i ta na na che ge mo sha trum na sha ya hum phat /
NG0204:3157: ya me do ru na yo da ya che ge mo a mu kam mur tsa ya hum phat /
NG0204:3159: 'od zer bdag la phog gyur pas //
NG0204:3160: rang dbang med par bskul nas @#//
NG0204:3162: de yis myos byed 'bar ba bskul //
NG0204:3163: de yis phyogs skyong gshin rje bskul //
NG0204:3164: de bzhin ma mo mkha' 'gro dang *//
NG0204:3165: ging bdud 'dug pa'i dbang med bskul //
NG0204:3166: de bzhin dmigs pa'i dngos bkug nas //
NG0204:3167: 'dug pa'i dbang med thod par bcug / gsad pa las kyi sngags bzlas pas //
NG0204:3168: star tshan rtsi sbur mi chags bzhin //
NG0204:3169: gang la bya ba brlag par bsam //
NG0204:3170: de bzhin dmar thag chad pa dang *//
NG0204:3171: gshed po myos byed 'bar ba la //
NG0204:3172: mnyes pa'i sha khrag gtor ma sbyin //
NG0204:3173: gshed la bcol bskul drag tu bya //
NG0204:3174: phyag rgya gong bzhin bcas nas kyang *//
NG0204:3175: be con lte bar brgyab pas ni //
NG0204:3177: bdag gi thugs ka'i ya nag po //
NG0204:3178: drag sngags bdun gyis bskor ba la //
NG0204:3179: gsad pa las kyi sngags bzlas te //
NG0204:3180: om hrihsh+t+r-ihbi kr-i ta na na sha trum na sha ya hum phat /
NG0204:3181: ya da yo ni ra yak+she ya che ge mo a mu kam rak+ta tsa ra ya hum phat /
NG0204:3182: 'od zer bdag la phog gyur pas //
NG0204:3183: rang dbang med par bskul nas kyang *//
NG0204:3184: gshed chen ar+ya ma ru bskul //
NG0204:3185: de yis phyogs skyong gshin rje bskul //
NG0204:3186: de bzhin ma mo mkha' 'gro dang *//
NG0204:3187: ging dang ging mo bdud la sogs //
NG0204:3188: 'dug pa'i dbang med bskul bar bsam //
NG0204:3189: de yi gzas pa po bkug nas //
NG0204:3190: dbang med thod par bcug par bsam //
NG0204:3191: gsad pa las kyi sngags bzlas pas //
NG0204:3192: star tshan rtsi sbur mi chags bzhin //
NG0204:3193: gang la bya ba brlag par bsam //
NG0204:3194: de bzhin dmar thag chad pa dang *//
NG0204:3195: gshed chen ar+ya ma ru la //
NG0204:3196: sha khrag mnyes pa'i mchod pa dbul //
NG0204:3197: be con mgrin par brgyab pa yi /
NG0204:3198: khrag tsar lhug gis song bar bsam //
NG0204:3199: bdag gi thugs kar yi ge ya //
NG0204:3200: drag sngags 'bru bdun bskor ba la //
NG0204:3201: gsad pa las kyi sngags bzlas te //
NG0204:3202: om hrihsh+t+r-ihbi kr-i ta na na sha trum na sha ya hum phat //
NG0204:3203: ya k+she ya ts+tsha ni ra ma ya //
NG0204:3204: che ge mo a mu kam ma ra ya hum phat /
NG0204:3206: 'od zer bdag la phog gyur pas //
NG0204:3207: rang dbang med par bskul nas kyang *//
NG0204:3208: de yis ral pa tshar dgu bskul //
NG0204:3209: de yis phyogs skyong gshin rje bskul //
NG0204:3210: de bzhin ma mo mkha' 'gro dang *//
NG0204:3211: ging pho ging mo bdud la sogs //
NG0204:3212: 'dug pa'i dbang med bskul bar bsam //
NG0204:3213: gzas pa bkug nas thod par bcug / de bzhin bsad pa'i sngags bzlas pas //
NG0204:3214: star tshan rtsi sbur mi chags bzhin //
NG0204:3215: gang la bya ba brlag par bsam //
NG0204:3216: dgong ka'i dmar thag chad pa dang *//
NG0204:3217: gshed chen ral pa tshar dgu la //
NG0204:3218: sha khrag sna tshogs gtor ma sbyin //
NG0204:3219: drag po'i phrin las bcol bskul bya //
NG0204:3220: de bzhin be con phyag rgya yis //
NG0204:3221: snying khar brgyab pas srog bcad nas //
NG0204:3222: dbugs kun phyi la phyung bar bsam //
NG0204:3223: gsad pa ma ra'i man ngag 'di //
NG0204:3224: gshin rje gshed po bdag gis kyang *//
NG0204:3225: thugs kyi sgrom bu kha phye nas //
NG0204:3228: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:3229: gsang ba las kyi bsnyen pa'i skabs te le'u nyer
NG0204:3230: dgu pa'o // // de nas gsang ba'i bdag po
NG0204:3231: phyag na rdo rjes 'di skad ces gsol to //
NG0204:3232: yab kyi sku la 'khril zhing khams gsum sgrol mdzad tshogs //
NG0204:3233: 'jig rten dbang du sdud cing srid gsum zil gyis gnon //
NG0204:3234: bdud mo mi bzad tshogs kyi las rnams bshad du gsol //
NG0204:3236: 'jigs byed chen pos bka' stsal pa //
NG0204:3237: las kyi srin mo'i tshogs kyis su khrag ka la pa //
NG0204:3238: 'di ni nges par bstan gyis nyan par byos //
NG0204:3240: thig gdab rgya gram le'u tse brgyad cu gcig / bdud mo'i grong khyer bcu drug dang *//
NG0204:3241: bdud dang dkrug dang sdebs pa'i yan lag tshar //
NG0204:3242: 'di ni yun du las de rdug pa med //
NG0204:3243: mu khyud gsum gyi sngags kyi sbyor ba kun gyis 'gyur //
NG0204:3244: yab kyi sngags dang spu gri'i sbyor bas dus dang kun tu sbyar //
NG0204:3245: 'khrugs byed sbyor ba'i sngags ni 'di lta ste //
NG0204:3246: rag mo e ka dza ti dum shi dun ma
NG0204:3247: trag sham be ta li snying ro shan ram thun
NG0204:3248: dza snying kha rag hri shi pu rag k+she re
NG0204:3249: tra yam ud / tsit+ta rag ta hum /
NG0204:3250: 'di ni sbyor ba'i las chen te //
NG0204:3251: brgya rtsa bzhi yis las grub pa'o //
NG0204:3252: drag po spu gri'i sbyor ba ni //
NG0204:3253: u rmo lta bu don bstan pa //
NG0204:3254: ma mar thun gzer b+h+yo ru lu rbad //
NG0204:3255: ya ma de ma b+h+yo ma b+h+yo ru lu rbad /
NG0204:3256: kha rag de ma b+h+yo ru lu b+h+yo rbad //
NG0204:3257: di shi de ma b+h+yo ru lu rbad /
NG0204:3258: pu tra de ma b+h+yo ru lu rbad /
NG0204:3259: rag sha de ma b+h+yo ru lu rbad /
NG0204:3260: de ba da ra la de ma b+h+yo ru lu rbad /
NG0204:3261: pa tra mug b+h+yo ru lu rbad /
NG0204:3262: tsit+ta de ma b+h+yo ru lu rbad /
NG0204:3263: de ni mu la'i sbyor ba ste / mdo ru bsdus nas bshad pa yin //
NG0204:3264: zhes bka' bstsal pas 'khor rnams mos pas 'dun par gyur to //
NG0204:3265: de nas gzhan yang bshad bya ba //
NG0204:3267: dpa' bo chen po 'jigs byed gshed //
NG0204:3268: drag po gsang ba'i 'khor lo la //
NG0204:3269: skyod pa'i rta dang 'debs pa'i sngags //
NG0204:3270: sdeb pa'i grogs dang rno ba'i rdzas //
NG0204:3271: de bzhi'i rkyen dang ma ldan na //
NG0204:3274: mthu stobs bdag pos 'di skad gsol //
NG0204:3275: skyod pa'i rta ni gang la bgyi //
NG0204:3276: 'debs pa'i sngags ni gang la bgyi //
NG0204:3277: sdeb pa'i grogs ni gang la bgyi //
NG0204:3278: rno ba'i ngar ni gang la bgyi //
NG0204:3279: yab cig 'jam dpal bka' stsol cig / gshin rje gshed pos 'di skad brjod //
NG0204:3280: nyon cig zung zhig rdo rje 'dzin //
NG0204:3281: drag po gsang ba'i 'khor lo la //
NG0204:3282: skyod pa'i rta dang mi ldan na //
NG0204:3286: sdeb pa'i grogs dang mi ldan na //
NG0204:3287: dpa' bo gting gnon med pa 'dra //
NG0204:3288: rno ba'i ngar dang mi ldan na //
NG0204:3289: mtshon tsha rtse mo rtul ba 'dra //
NG0204:3290: de bzhin grogs rnams ngas bshad kyi //
NG0204:3291: lag na rdo rjes rab tu @#//
NG0204:3293: bka' dang gzhung bzhin ma nor ba'i //
NG0204:3294: bsrung ba'i sdom pa ma nyams par //
NG0204:3295: rdzas dang lag cha ldan pa dang *//
NG0204:3296: bsam ldan bzlas brjod sran tshugs shing *//
NG0204:3297: dam tshig bsrung zhing drag shul spyod //
NG0204:3298: lta spyod bsgrub pa ldan pa yi //
NG0204:3299: dpal rtul can gyi rnal 'byor pas //
NG0204:3300: bstan pa gnyen po bsrung don du //
NG0204:3301: dgon pa chen po gnas mal der //
NG0204:3302: bya byed zang zing 'du long spang *//
NG0204:3303: 'tshe ba'i yo byad dbags te bstar //
NG0204:3304: bya ba thams cad zin nas ni //
NG0204:3305: bde ba'i stan la 'dug nas ni //
NG0204:3306: bskyed dang rdzogs pa'i rim pa de //
NG0204:3307: ting 'dzin gsal dang brtan pa yi //
NG0204:3308: lha yi rnal 'byor rtse gcig bya //
NG0204:3309: thun mong dam tshig bsrung zhing bsgrub /
NG0204:3310: khyad par dam tshig spyod cing dor //
NG0204:3311: bsnyen bsgrub phrin las gzhung bzhin bya //
NG0204:3312: tshang zhing rdzogs pa'i grangs bsnyen la //
NG0204:3313: 'khor zhing phyin pa dus bsnyen yin //
NG0204:3314: mthong ngam thos sam nyams su len //
NG0204:3315: mtshan ma'i bsnyen pa rdzogs pa dang *//
NG0204:3316: zhi rgyas gnyis kyi 'khor los mchod //
NG0204:3317: dbang drag gnyis kyi 'khor los mnan //
NG0204:3318: zhi rgyas gnyis kyi bsrung phan gdags //
NG0204:3319: dbang drag gnyis kyi bsgral bar bya //
NG0204:3320: 'khor lo gzhan yang ci rigs par //
NG0204:3321: dbye bskrad dgug sogs gzhung bzhin bya //
NG0204:3322: gang 'dod las de bsgrub byas na //
NG0204:3323: 'khor lo'i rgyu dang snag tsha dang */
NG0204:3324: phyogs dang bsam sbyor rim pa dang */
NG0204:3325: kha dog so so'i mthun rdzas ni //
NG0204:3326: rim pa can gyi de shes bya //
NG0204:3327: de la 'khor lo zhes grags pa //
NG0204:3328: ngo bo nges tshig rnam grangs so //
NG0204:3329: ngo bo spyi yi mtshan nyid ni //
NG0204:3331: so so rang gi mtshan nyid ni //
NG0204:3332: gang la btab pa de ltar snang *//
NG0204:3333: nges pa'i tshig kyang de bzhin te //
NG0204:3336: lte ba 'khor zhing rtse mos gcod //
NG0204:3337: de la grangs ni mtha' yas te //
NG0204:3338: mdor na rnam pa gsum du shes //
NG0204:3339: thugs rje sprul pa'i 'khor lo dang *//
NG0204:3340: las dang srid pa'i 'khor lo dang *//
NG0204:3341: 'jig rten phan gnod byed pa yi //
NG0204:3343: dper na mo 'phang mgal me dang *//
NG0204:3344: glog dang sgra ldan 'khor lo dang *//
NG0204:3345: shing rta zo chu'i 'khor lo sogs //
NG0204:3346: las dang 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid ni //
NG0204:3347: thugs rje sprul pa'i 'khor los ni //
NG0204:3348: nyon mongs gcod cing sdug bsngal 'joms //
NG0204:3349: bsgrub dang bsgrub par bya ba yi //
NG0204:3350: sems bskyed pa dang rgyud dgrol zhing *//
NG0204:3351: ye shes sems mtshon rnam grol byed //
NG0204:3352: de las rnam pa gzhan du yang *//
NG0204:3353: zhi dang rgyas dang srung ba dang *//
NG0204:3354: dgug dang dbang du bya ba dang *//
NG0204:3355: dbye bskrad dgug dang smyo 'bog dang *//
NG0204:3356: gsad dang mnan pa la sogs pa //
NG0204:3357: de yi rkyen dang rtsol ba dang *//
NG0204:3358: dus dang las thabs byed pa yi //
NG0204:3359: 'phen zhing bskyod pa nus pa yi //
NG0204:3363: gzir zhing gnan cing 'bigs pa dang *//
NG0204:3364: brdeg cing rnam par 'joms par byed //
NG0204:3365: las dang srid pa'i 'khor lo ni //
NG0204:3368: nyon mongs las dang sdug bsngal gyi //
NG0204:3370: 'das dang da ltar gnas pa dang *//
NG0204:3372: skad kyi 'byung ba'i rgyun gyis na //
NG0204:3373: skad cig ma yi rgyun gyis 'khor //
NG0204:3374: de bzhin phyi rol don rnams kyang *//
NG0204:3375: dbyar dgun ston dpyid zla ba los /
NG0204:3377: ngo bo nges tshig rnam grangs su //
NG0204:3378: 'khor lo'i rang bzhin bstan pa yin //
NG0204:3379: bde gshegs bka' la gnod pa la //
NG0204:3381: yi dwags grong khyer bcom byas la //
NG0204:3382: snel gri mu su'i mgo thod blangs //
NG0204:3383: yi dwags gos la khram bris te //
NG0204:3384: dbyibs ni zla ba lta bu ste //
NG0204:3385: kun nas yongs su zlum pa ste //
NG0204:3386: rim pa gsum ldan le'u tse dgu //
NG0204:3387: bcu gnyis bcu drug rtsibs bcas te //
NG0204:3388: le'u tse dgu dang bcu gnyis la //
NG0204:3389: bcu bdun la sogs sngags kyis mdzes //
NG0204:3391: phyin ci log gi bcings pa yi //
NG0204:3392: log pa'i shes pa ldan pa des //
NG0204:3393: rgyu mthun mtshan ma'i 'khor lo la //
NG0204:3394: man ngag can gyi rnal 'byor pas /
NG0204:3395: kha nas drag po'i sngags bzlas te //
NG0204:3396: chos kyi rgyal po la sogs pa'i //
NG0204:3397: las kyi shan pa'i go bkram ste //
NG0204:3398: lcags kyu shag ti to ma ra /
NG0204:3399: kha twam ber ka la sogs pas //
NG0204:3400: brdeg cing 'joms par byed pa ni //
NG0204:3402: 'dzin cing gsod par bsam pa yis //
NG0204:3403: gang la bya ba'i rnam shes de //
NG0204:3404: log pa'i stabs kyis gnas su mthong */
NG0204:3405: khro bdag gshin rje gshed po ru //
NG0204:3406: bdag nyid bsam pa'i rnal 'byor gyis //
NG0204:3407: mtshan ma'i ming rus bcas pa la //
NG0204:3408: ske tshe dug dang nyung nag dang *//
NG0204:3409: thal chen gu gul nyung dkar gyis //
NG0204:3410: brab dang gzir dang dbab pa dang *//
NG0204:3411: dgug cing rdo rje'i mtshon gyis gdab //
NG0204:3412: sngon dmar byad du gzhug byas la //
NG0204:3413: ga'u kha sbyar nang du gzhug / smra bcad zhi khro'i sngags bzlas pa'i //
NG0204:3414: drag po'i sngags kyi phog 'gyur na / gang la dmigs pa'i bsgrub bya ste //
NG0204:3415: mgo 'khor ba dang khrag skyugs pa //
NG0204:3416: myos par ma ra gdon mi za //
NG0204:3417: drag po'i las rnams rdzogs pa dang */
NG0204:3418: mtshan ma ming rus bcas pa rnams //
NG0204:3419: thod pa nag por rgyas btab la //
NG0204:3420: sme bas bkrus pas tshan chus byug / mu sa la yi g.yogs shing gtum /
NG0204:3421: kha ral ma yi zhabs mas gril //
NG0204:3422: yi dwags grong ngam sme btsog khyim //
NG0204:3423: mchod rten 'og gam lha khang sgo //
NG0204:3424: rgya mtsho'i 'gram mam lung mdo ru //
NG0204:3425: rdo la ri rab gzugs bris la //
NG0204:3426: steng du lam dang d+h+ri yis hri yang mnan //
NG0204:3427: gshin rje'i lag tu gtad khram bya //
NG0204:3430: sbos pa dug thun lkugs pa kha //
NG0204:3431: nyi ma dang po'i thun gyi mnan //
NG0204:3432: gzer ba mda' thun brla la gzer //
NG0204:3433: nyi ma gnyis pa'i thun kyis brab //
NG0204:3434: lkugs pa khrag thun myos pa phur //
NG0204:3435: nyi ma gsum pa'i thun gyis brab //
NG0204:3436: gsang ba nyung nag sa yi tshon //
NG0204:3437: nyi ma bzhi pa'i thun gyis mnan //
NG0204:3438: mtshan ngan thod pa khrag gis byug / khrag sna dug sna sbyar byas nas //
NG0204:3439: shan mar dug skyog dug thun bzlas //
NG0204:3440: glen lkugs thod pa'i kha thun te //
NG0204:3441: lcags mda' lcags gzhu mda' thun bzlas /
NG0204:3442: bzlas pa'i tshe dang bklag pa'i tshe /
NG0204:3443: 'dra min 'dug / gri bo'i thod par mtshon brdar ba'o //
NG0204:3444: mkhris nad thod par sa sar gser //
NG0204:3445: gla ba gser thun sngags kyis so //
NG0204:3446: smyo ba'i thod pa khrag 'thung dang *//
NG0204:3447: smyos pa phur thun bzlas pa bya //
NG0204:3448: rabs chad thod pa nyung thun dang *//
NG0204:3449: sa tshon thun du shes par bya //
NG0204:3450: chu shel sgron ma rlab po che //
NG0204:3451: lkugs pa mon mo'i lag g.yas kyi //
NG0204:3452: srid pa'i dmag dpung ra mda' bzlog / ya ma ra dza'i g.yab kyis g.yab //
NG0204:3453: gsur dang sme ba'i dud pas bdug / gcer bu'i spyi tshugs ngu 'bod bya //
NG0204:3454: mi mthun gnyen po'i phyogs dag tu //
NG0204:3455: gzir gnon drag po'i mngon spyod bya //
NG0204:3456: drag po'i thun sngags kha nas bzlas //
NG0204:3457: zhung thun ya rbad na thun ya rbad phung gung yang thun ya rbad /
NG0204:3459: gang po dang lo lo kyi gye /
NG0204:3460: srog la yam yam snying la thun /
NG0204:3461: kha brgyad thun yang brdeg par bya //
NG0204:3462: lha srin sde brgyad la sogs pa'i //
NG0204:3463: srid pa'i dmag dpung phab nas ni //
NG0204:3464: drang srong dmod pa'i sngags zor dang *//
NG0204:3465: sna tshogs sngags kyi sbyor ba dang *//
NG0204:3466: lha yi rnal 'byor ldan pas bya //
NG0204:3467: khru gang gru bzhi zabs yod par //
NG0204:3468: ga'u rdzas kyi sbyor ba de //
NG0204:3469: 'byung po'i gtor ma gshin rje la //
NG0204:3470: byin la lag tu gtad khram bya //
NG0204:3471: rang gi yi dam bsgom bya zhing *//
NG0204:3472: byin gyis brlabs pa'i gtor ma ni //
NG0204:3473: sa sros tshe na lho phyogs gtang *//
NG0204:3474: sgrol ba'i drag sngags brnag pa'i lung *//
NG0204:3475: bstan pa'i bsrung ba gnan pa'i gter //
NG0204:3476: phrin las drag po sngags kyi mtshon /
NG0204:3478: rdo rje sems dpa' gzungs shing chongs //
NG0204:3479: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyun las //
NG0204:3480: 'khor lo thun sdebs kyi skabs te le'u sum cu
NG0204:3481: pa'o // // de nas gshin rje gshed pos 'di
NG0204:3482: skad brjod // bstan pa srung ba brnag pa'i lung *//
NG0204:3483: thugs kyi man ngag sngags zor mchog / sgrol ba'i phrin las sbyor thabs su //
NG0204:3485: bka' yi bstan pa bsrung ba'i phyir //
NG0204:3486: rang sems dag pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NG0204:3487: snying rje rtag tu srog ltar brten //
NG0204:3488: byams dga' btang snyoms de bzhin du //
NG0204:3489: mdo sogs 'don zhing bsam gtan bya //
NG0204:3490: rgyun gyi yi dam rtse gcig pas //
NG0204:3491: bla ma dag la rtag tu bkur //
NG0204:3492: des kyang dkyil 'khor tshul bzhin gzhug / theg chen @#//
NG0204:3494: rang gi sngags dang phyag rgya dang *//
NG0204:3495: sgrub thabs man ngag legs par blang *//
NG0204:3496: de nas mchod pa cho ga bzhin //
NG0204:3497: nyin re dag tu byas nas kyang *//
NG0204:3498: sku gzugs dag kyang 'bad de bya //
NG0204:3499: bde ba'i stan la lus sems gzhag / sum 'bum mi skyo'i bar du bzlas //
NG0204:3500: de 'og ri rtser gnas byas la //
NG0204:3501: rlung za zhing ni bzlas pa bya //
NG0204:3502: 'bum bcu'i mtha' ru phrin las brtsams //
NG0204:3503: nam mkha'i sgron ma mar dus tshe //
NG0204:3504: yi dwags grong bcom shi gos la //
NG0204:3505: yi dwags 'khor lo gdug pa yi //
NG0204:3506: 'khor lo gdug pa'i lte ba la //
NG0204:3507: re'u mig dgu yi mtshams bor te //
NG0204:3508: bcu gnyis 'khor lo gdug pa'i nang *//
NG0204:3509: bcu bdun la sogs gsad sngags dang *//
NG0204:3510: zlum pos bskor ba'i phyi rim na //
NG0204:3512: dur khrod sol ba dug sol gyis //
NG0204:3513: srin mtheb gung mdzub sbyar ba yis /
NG0204:3514: khru gang gos gnyis ras mchog la //
NG0204:3515: gdug pa'i yi ge g.yas g.yon bzlog / de nang chud pa'i skyes bu gnyis //
NG0204:3517: phyag zhabs mgur chu ro nyes brgyan //
NG0204:3518: mi smra dbang po bsdams te bri //
NG0204:3519: gnyis sbyar rgyab la ro nye yis //
NG0204:3520: bsdams pa'i tshul du mkhas pas bri //
NG0204:3521: gdug pas bzung zhing thod nang du //
NG0204:3522: gdug pa grub gcig thod nang du yang 'dug / dril byas sngon dmar byad kyis bsdams //
NG0204:3523: gdug pa'i thod nag ltos 'gro bri //
NG0204:3524: mngar dang klu sman rtsi mchog gis //
NG0204:3525: mchod cing sbal la mgu bar bya //
NG0204:3526: gdug pas bzung zhing thod par gzhug / sngon dmar byad thag bzhis btab la //
NG0204:3527: bzung ste nyin mtshan ma nor bzlas /
NG0204:3528: kha nas drag po'i sngags bzlas pas //
NG0204:3529: rdo rje rlung lce sbyar ba las //
NG0204:3530: sngon dmar gdug pa'i ro nye'i tshogs //
NG0204:3531: dur khrod sol bas dug sogs sbyar //
NG0204:3532: lcags sam 'ug pa'i sgro rtsa yis //
NG0204:3533: gsang ba'i sngags dang ming rus bri //
NG0204:3534: dug can nad kyis bsgrub bya la //
NG0204:3535: dug lce nag pos bsdams par bsam //
NG0204:3536: 'chi bdag bshan pa'i yi dwags tshogs //
NG0204:3537: gtum po dug gi kha rlangs can //
NG0204:3538: chos kyi rgyal po la sogs pas //
NG0204:3539: 'jab cing sgugs shing bzung nas ni //
NG0204:3540: gshin rje gdug pa'i khang pa ru //
NG0204:3541: dbang med las kyis 'jug par bsam //
NG0204:3543: hum dang ming spel a kar sha //
NG0204:3544: dza gnyis dgug pa'i gsang sngags bzlas //
NG0204:3545: ske tshe dug nyung sngags kyis brab //
NG0204:3546: zla ba nag po'i mar dus tshe //
NG0204:3547: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi gru gsum ste //
NG0204:3548: lcags khri nag po'i steng dag tu //
NG0204:3549: yi dwags gdug pa'i ga bu [\[]'u [\]]gzhag / ya sogs gdug pa'i gsang sngags rnams //
NG0204:3550: zhi khro rdzogs nas ga bu [\[]'u [\]]de //
NG0204:3551: rdza mkhan sa la ga bu [\[]'u [\]]rgyu //
NG0204:3552: gdug pa'i ga bu [\[]'u [\]]shong ba'i tshe //
NG0204:3553: gnyis byas nang du ro nye gnyis //
NG0204:3557: me yi smin ma ga bu [\[]'u [\]]gnag / gdug pa'i thod nag ga bur [\[]'ur [\]]gzhug /
NG0204:3558: sngon dmar gnyis kyi the gus bsdams //
NG0204:3559: shar nub lho byang phyogs mtshams su //
NG0204:3560: gdug pa gnas pa'i yul dag la //
NG0204:3561: sgo bltas khyim nas 'dom gang du //
NG0204:3562: rdo la 'jig rten gzugs bris la //
NG0204:3563: sa sgo phye la khyim bdag rbad //
NG0204:3564: mthun pa'i rdzas byin mgu bar bya //
NG0204:3565: ga bu [\[]'u [\]]gdug pa'i sbyor ba de //
NG0204:3566: legs sbas steng nas 'jig rten gzhug / gang la bya ba'i dus dang lo //
NG0204:3567: gnyen po gang shis mkhas pas dpyad //
NG0204:3568: zla ba nag po'i mar dus tshe //
NG0204:3569: drang srong rgyu ba'i sa phyogs su //
NG0204:3570: byad stems 'khor lo'i btsan dug spyo /
NG0204:3571: khyab 'jug mchod cing khyim bdag rbad //
NG0204:3573: ma nyes dpang gzug ru dung 'dud //
NG0204:3574: mi mthun gnyen po'i phyogs dag tu //
NG0204:3575: bos shing mchod cing gtad khram bya /
NG0204:3576: khyab 'jug gdug pa'i dmod pa bor //
NG0204:3577: yi dwags gdug pa'i smon lam gdab //
NG0204:3578: na ga gdug pa'i dmod bcol bya //
NG0204:3579: rang nyid lha yi nga rgyal gyis //
NG0204:3580: dkar po rdo rje rgya bsam la //
NG0204:3581: sa sgo bcad la rgya yis mnan //
NG0204:3582: sdom la gnas pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NG0204:3583: g.yeng ba med pa'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NG0204:3584: phrin las rdzogs dang gsang sngags bzlas //
NG0204:3585: bsgrub bya'i gzugs phung ma zhig par //
NG0204:3586: gdug pa sbrul gyi sems 'dra bas //
NG0204:3587: ma zhig bar du gtang mi bya //
NG0204:3588: zhig ste mngon du gyur pa dang *//
NG0204:3589: spar zhing g.yo ba'i cho ga bya //
NG0204:3590: bskyed dang spyan drang mchod bskul rnams //
NG0204:3591: sgom rgyud mdzes thun nang du'o //
NG0204:3592: bla ma'i gdams ngag dam pa yang *//
NG0204:3593: yid la nan tan gzhag par bya //
NG0204:3594: byang chub sems nyid sems la gzhag / dam tshig bsrung sdom mi nyams bsrung *//
NG0204:3595: bka' la bshad pa rjes mthun par //
NG0204:3596: rdzas dang lag cha mthun bsdebs shing *//
NG0204:3597: rtag tu dur khrod dgon par dga' //
NG0204:3598: dus dang lo tshigs dam bcas pa //
NG0204:3599: mi 'da' gzhung ltar byed pa ste //
NG0204:3600: mtshan ma mthong dang bzlas pa rdzogs //
NG0204:3601: rgyun gyi yi dam che ba ste //
NG0204:3602: de lta bu yi rnal 'byor pa //
NG0204:3603: bden pa grub pa'i nus pa yod //
NG0204:3604: shes rab snying rje rab ldan pa'i //
NG0204:3605: dbang thob dam tshig srog ltar bsten //
NG0204:3606: mi 'jigs dpa' bo brtul bzhugs can //
NG0204:3607: man ngag yod pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NG0204:3608: rang don phran tshegs ma yin pa'i //
NG0204:3609: dkon mchog dbu 'phang smod pa dang *//
NG0204:3610: bstan la zhe sdang gnod byed pa //
NG0204:3611: bka' gsang ston pas bshad pa yi //
NG0204:3612: drag po'i mngon spyod zab mo'i lung *//
NG0204:3613: gshin rje gshed po bdag gis kyang *//
NG0204:3614: thugs kyi sgrom nas bton pa 'di //
NG0204:3615: 'khor lo byad stems brnag pa'i lung *//
NG0204:3616: man ngag can gyi de shes bya //
NG0204:3617: las kyi bya ba thun tshags rnams //
NG0204:3618: man ngag don gyis shes par bya //
NG0204:3619: cung zad mi mthun mchod bstod rnams //
NG0204:3621: gsang nag po'i rgyud dag las //
NG0204:3622: gsang ba mdzes thun gzhung ltar bya //
NG0204:3623: de la mchod pa gsungs pa ni //
NG0204:3624: mchod pa chen po 'dod chags che //
NG0204:3625: dkyil 'khor chen po yangs pa yin //
NG0204:3626: tshigs bcad bcu drug tha ma la //
NG0204:3627: 'jam dpal dpal dang ldan pa'i mchog / 'gro la phan pa'i gtso chen gyis //
NG0204:3628: sman par dgongs te bzhes su gsol //
NG0204:3629: tshig gnyis btag la dbul bar bya //
NG0204:3630: bstod pa la sogs byed pa na //
NG0204:3631: de bzhin rtsa ba mtshan brjod las //
NG0204:3633: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas a las byung *//
NG0204:3634: 'dud sogs kun gyis bstod byas mthar //
NG0204:3635: mtshan gyi sngags brjod bstod chen bya //
NG0204:3636: sngags mchog mnga' bdag rig sngags rgyal //
NG0204:3638: ma rig sgo nga'i sbubs 'byed pa //
NG0204:3639: srid pa'i dra ba 'joms pa po //
NG0204:3640: zhes bstod pa tshig rkang drug pa dang *//
NG0204:3641: drug cu rtsa bzhis bstod pa dbul //
NG0204:3642: yang na 'dud pa nyi shu nas //
NG0204:3643: mtshan sngags brjod la bstod chung bya //
NG0204:3644: yang na mdzes thun gzhung bzhin bya //
NG0204:3645: bskal pa sbrul nag khyil ces gtad //
NG0204:3647: dkon mchog gnod cing bstan pa 'jig / mngon spyod thugs rjes bsgral ba'i phyir //
NG0204:3648: mi tshig tha snyad tsam du brjod mi bya //
NG0204:3649: chu srin mgrin par rin chen chud pa ltar //
NG0204:3650: khong du sbas te yongs su bsgrags pa min //
NG0204:3651: gshin rje gshed po'i thugs kyi yang bcud 'di //
NG0204:3652: phyag na rdo rjes rab tu gzung zhing nyon //
NG0204:3653: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:3654: tshon gyi gru gu sngon dmar byad stems kyi skabs
NG0204:3655: te le'u so gcig pa'o // // de nas yang
NG0204:3656: bcom ldan 'das gshin rje gshed pos 'di skad ces
NG0204:3657: gsungs so // las kyi bya ba gzhan zin nas //
NG0204:3659: lag na rdo rjes rab tu zung *//
NG0204:3660: shin tu dgon pa'i gnas nyid du //
NG0204:3661: dur khrod gling nas ras blangs te //
NG0204:3662: 'khor lo rim pa tshul bzhin du //
NG0204:3663: ma ra ya yi ling+ga nyid //
NG0204:3664: ji bzhin 'dod pa'i dbyibs su bca' //
NG0204:3665: gong ma'i bsnyen pa rdzogs pa dang *//
NG0204:3666: 'khor lo thabs can gyi dang chos kyi yang */
NG0204:3668: mchod rten 'og tu gnan par bya //
NG0204:3669: bdag nyid gshed por bsgom byas la //
NG0204:3670: mchod rten de nyid ngo bo yang *//
NG0204:3671: ri rab gling bzhi chas par bsgom //
NG0204:3672: ri rab lto na bzhugs pa ste //
NG0204:3673: sgrol ba'i yum dang sbyor ba'i yum //
NG0204:3674: shar dang nub tu gnas par bsam //
NG0204:3675: byang na sras mchog gnas par bsgom //
NG0204:3676: de bzhin rab tu mnan cing gzir //
NG0204:3677: ri rab bzung bzhir lam ser bzhi //
NG0204:3678: de las gling phran bcu gnyis bsam //
NG0204:3679: ri rab 'og tu gzas pa po //
NG0204:3680: gshin rje ral pa tshar dgu yis //
NG0204:3681: lcags thag sngon pos bcings pa de //
NG0204:3682: bam ril mnan nas lcags phur la //
NG0204:3683: dpag bsam shing tsam btags pa ste //
NG0204:3684: sgra sgrogs kha nas khrag skyugs gan bu @#//
NG0204:3687: ci mdzad thong zhig zer zhing mnan par bsam //
NG0204:3688: 'khor lo br-i ba'i dus su yang *//
NG0204:3689: dmigs pa'i ming dag gzhug pa ni //
NG0204:3690: 'khor lo nyid la mi shong zhing *//
NG0204:3691: mi btub pa rnams gud du bri //
NG0204:3692: de dag bris te gdags par bya //
NG0204:3693: gnas dang thabs ni 'di yin te //
NG0204:3694: ya la sogs pa'i ye ge lnga //
NG0204:3695: gra bzhi hum phat bar mtshams bzhi //
NG0204:3696: rtsibs kyi re'u cha bcu gnyis dang *//
NG0204:3697: mtha' bskor ming rus le'u tse brgyad //
NG0204:3698: de dag nyi shu rtsa dgu la //
NG0204:3700: gud du ming gi mjug tu yang //
NG0204:3701: ma ra ya zhes bris pa'i 'khor lo gnyis /
NG0204:3702: kha sbyar ba yi nang du gzhug / 'khor lo
NG0204:3703: skud pas sbrel la bzhag / ngan sngags bzlas pa'i
NG0204:3704: dus su yang *// bzhi pa'i ngan sngags khri phrag 'don //
NG0204:3705: de dag bton pa'i rjes la yang *//
NG0204:3706: yi ge bcu pa nus tshad bzlas //
NG0204:3707: de tshe mchod pa 'bul ba dang *//
NG0204:3708: de tshe gtor ma gtong ba dang *//
NG0204:3709: ye shes lha la thugs dam bskul //
NG0204:3710: las kyi gshin rje ma mo rnams //
NG0204:3711: rak+ta gsol zhing dgug pa'i pa'i phrin las bya //
NG0204:3712: 'khor lo sbed pa'i dus su yang *//
NG0204:3713: gshin rje dag la gtad pa ni //
NG0204:3714: rdzas kyi mchod pa bshams pa dang *//
NG0204:3715: bdag nyid gshed por bsgom pa dang *//
NG0204:3716: 'chi bdag dgongs su gsol ba dang *//
NG0204:3717: rang gi las kyi ltang brtsi dang *//
NG0204:3718: bsgrub bya'i chad pa brtsi ba dang *//
NG0204:3719: gshin rje'i rgyal po spyan drangs nas //
NG0204:3720: dam tshig phyag rgya rab bstan cing *//
NG0204:3721: dam tshig snying po rab tu bzlas //
NG0204:3722: de bzhin dam las mi 'da' dang *//
NG0204:3723: dam rdzas mchod pas mnyes byed dang *//
NG0204:3724: las kyi phyag rgya bca' ba dang *//
NG0204:3725: dam tshig bskul te las kyi gnyer gtad dang *//
NG0204:3726: mnas bsgags rnams kyis gtad pa'i las rdzogs te //
NG0204:3727: 'khor lo sba ba'i dus su yang *//
NG0204:3728: gshin rje dag la gtad pa ni //
NG0204:3729: drang srong dmod pa'i smon lam gdab par bya //
NG0204:3731: de la mnan rdzas bsag pa ni //
NG0204:3732: mi khrag ra khrag dug la sogs //
NG0204:3734: srin bya'i snying dang 'ug pa'i mig / btsong dang la phug ske tshe dang *//
NG0204:3735: g.yer ma bra 'o sga dang nas //
NG0204:3736: de la sngags te gnan pa'o //
NG0204:3737: spyir na gnan pa'i las byas na //
NG0204:3738: gshed pa'i dgongs pas gnan pa dang */
NG0204:3739: phyag rgya'i stobs kyis gnan pa dang *//
NG0204:3740: gtad khram bcu gnyis cho gas gnan pa dang *//
NG0204:3741: ya stags gdugs pas gnan pa dang *//
NG0204:3742: de dag rdzas kyis gnan pa'o //
NG0204:3743: drag po'i sngags kyis gnan pa dang *//
NG0204:3744: smon lam gdab cing gnan pa dang *//
NG0204:3745: drang srong dmod pa'i gnan pa'o //
NG0204:3746: 'di nas lho yi phyogs rol na //
NG0204:3747: dpag tshad brgyad khri bzhi stong pha rol na //
NG0204:3748: thod pa lcags kyi grong khyer na //
NG0204:3749: yi dwags kun gyi sde dpon po //
NG0204:3750: ma mo kun gyi tshogs rje mo //
NG0204:3751: gson gshin gnyis kyi zam kha ba //
NG0204:3752: gson po skos la 'debs pa po //
NG0204:3756: dge ba can gyi ltang 'dzin la //
NG0204:3757: sdig pa can gyi chad pa mkhan //
NG0204:3758: legs nyes chos bzhin gcod pa yis //
NG0204:3759: chos rgyal gshin rje zhes bya ba //
NG0204:3760: mngon shes rdzu 'phrul mthu ldan pas //
NG0204:3761: 'khor bcas khyed la gtad par bya //
NG0204:3762: de dag rab tu mnan gyur na //
NG0204:3763: de yi cho ga 'dir ma bshad //
NG0204:3764: lag na rdo rjes rab tu zung *//
NG0204:3765: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:3766: 'khor lo mnan pa'i skabs te le'u so gnyis pa'o
NG0204:3767: // // de nas bcom ldan 'das gshin rje'i gshed
NG0204:3769: bdag don ma yin gzhan don nam //
NG0204:3770: dkon mchog bla ma'i don ched du //
NG0204:3771: ru tra gdug pa tshar bcad na //
NG0204:3772: sngags kyi dngos grub thob nas 'grub //
NG0204:3773: dper na dpa' bo skyes bu yis //
NG0204:3774: g.yung ngo bzlog par 'dod pa yis //
NG0204:3775: go dang mtshon la nan tan bskyed //
NG0204:3776: des ni g.yul rnams bzlog par 'gyur //
NG0204:3777: go mtshon mgar la rag las phyir //
NG0204:3778: dpa' bos mgar la brten par bya //
NG0204:3779: mgar gyis rdo la lcags su bzhu //
NG0204:3780: lcags la go dang mtshon cha brdung *//
NG0204:3781: de nas 'thar la nan tan bskyed //
NG0204:3782: til mar ngar yang yid 'thad blud //
NG0204:3783: de nas brdeg thabs shes par bya //
NG0204:3784: de bzhin rnal 'byor chen pos kyang *//
NG0204:3785: thog mar bla ma mnyes bya'i phyir //
NG0204:3786: rab tu gces dang yid 'thad dbul //
NG0204:3787: gnang bar dka' ba'i dbang yang mnos //
NG0204:3788: man ngag gnad nas smyur la bsgrub //
NG0204:3789: snying po don thabs lhar shes bya //
NG0204:3791: gzhan yang 'bum gcig shes par bya //
NG0204:3792: de nas mkhas pas phrin las bya //
NG0204:3793: dus dang phyogs ni mkhas pas brtag / khri khri bar du spyi rgyug bya //
NG0204:3794: phrin las dag la rnam pa gsum //
NG0204:3796: dang po 'khor lo'i las byas nas //
NG0204:3797: de nas gnan pa'i las shes bya //
NG0204:3798: tha mar me yi las bya ste //
NG0204:3799: me lha bsnyen pas las rnams 'grub //
NG0204:3800: dang por bsnyen pa rdzogs nas kyang *//
NG0204:3801: 'khor lo bskor ba'i las byas nas //
NG0204:3803: gnan pa'i las thabs byas nas ni //
NG0204:3804: hom dang bsreg pa'i las bsham pa //
NG0204:3805: thab khung gru gsum brtsig pa la //
NG0204:3806: rdo rje rgya gram nag po bri //
NG0204:3807: gzas pa'i ling+ga gzhag par bya //
NG0204:3808: de nas hom shing tsher ma can //
NG0204:3809: bam po bsgreng dang gru gsum brtsib //
NG0204:3810: dug chu khrag gis byug par bya //
NG0204:3812: smad phud til dmar 'bru bshos dang *//
NG0204:3813: mtshe thun lcags phye zangs phye dang *//
NG0204:3814: rdo phye dug chu 'bru nag po //
NG0204:3815: sha chen rus pa gtub pa dang *//
NG0204:3816: de dag la sogs mdun du gzhag / gos nag gyon zhing thod nag bcing *//
NG0204:3817: rak+sha'i phreng ba se ral kha //
NG0204:3818: dpral bar me long zhing gi stan //
NG0204:3819: rus sbal 'dug stangs lho phyogs blta //
NG0204:3820: lcags sam mi rkang gzar bu thogs //
NG0204:3821: dri chen dri chu gos dum gyis //
NG0204:3824: snying gar ming dang rus bcas gzhug / gzhan yang ming yig mang po dang *//
NG0204:3825: mi bsad mtshon gyis ling+ga gtub //
NG0204:3826: dum bu re dang ming byang re //
NG0204:3827: sha chen gtub pa re sbag la //
NG0204:3828: drag po'i sngags kyis khros la brdeg / ting nge 'dzin gyi rim pa ni //
NG0204:3829: ting 'dzin rnam gsum tshig bshad dang *//
NG0204:3830: bcas pa'i phrin las gzhung bsrang bya //
NG0204:3831: om swa b+ha wa shud+d+hahsarba d+harma swa b+ha ba bi shud+d+ho\u0f85ham /
NG0204:3832: chos rnams stong pa'i rang bzhin sbyang *//
NG0204:3833: de yi ngang las nga rgyal lha //
NG0204:3834: ya man+ta ka gsal bsgoms te //
NG0204:3835: zhal drug phyag kyang bcu gnyis te //
NG0204:3836: rgyan dang cha lugs gsal bar bsgom //
NG0204:3837: thab khung e las 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang *//
NG0204:3838: drag po 'bar ba'i gnas su gsal bar bsgom //
NG0204:3839: yugs sa rdo nag shing nag gtsubs pa'i me //
NG0204:3840: rlung g.yab nag pos g.yab pa'am //
NG0204:3841: drag po sngags kyi rab tu sbar //
NG0204:3842: me yi nang du ram nag ma tsha me yi lha //
NG0204:3843: rgyan dang cha lugs nag po gsal bar bsgom //
NG0204:3844: ting nge 'dzin gyi 'phro 'dus gnas nas kyang *//
NG0204:3845: 'od zer lcags kyus ye shes me lha de //
NG0204:3846: spyan drangs gnyis su med par bzhugs par bsam //
NG0204:3847: me yi lha nyid sngags 'dis spyan drangs te //
NG0204:3848: om ag+ne ha bya dzah ag+ne ka bya dzah dzahhum
NG0204:3849: bam hoh sku mdog nag po ra skyes kham pa
NG0204:3850: zhon / rwa la 'ja' tshon sna lnga 'khyil //
NG0204:3851: zhing gi ya mgal snga ru la //
NG0204:3852: zhing gi ma mgal phyi ru la //
NG0204:3853: zhing gi pags pas sga g.yogs bgyis //
NG0204:3854: sbrul nag gis ni gong rmed bgyis //
NG0204:3855: phyag na dril bu bgrang phreng bsnams //
NG0204:3856: dbu la me yi thod bcings shing *//
NG0204:3857: me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs //
NG0204:3858: shar lho mtshams nas gnyis su med par bzhugs //
NG0204:3862: zhes pas me yi mdun rgyab sta zur bzhi /
NG0204:3863: pra mo ha spyan gsum phyag bzhi pa /
NG0204:3864: g.yas dang po na chu srin rgyal mtshan bsnams pa /
NG0204:3865: g.yas bar ma na ye shes kyi me mgal bsnams pa /
NG0204:3866: g.yon dang po na me dar bsnams pa /
NG0204:3867: tha ma gnyis gnyis dril bu bsnams par bsgom /
NG0204:3870: ag+ne dmar ser me yi lha /
NG0204:3872: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:3873: 'khor lo hom sbrel gyi skabs te le'u so gsum
NG0204:3874: pa'o // // de nas bcom ldan 'das dpal gshin
NG0204:3875: rje gshed pos 'di skad brjod do //
NG0204:3877: lag na rdo rje 'dzin pa khyod //
NG0204:3878: dus ngan tha ma byung ba'i tshe //
NG0204:3879: dkon mchog dbu 'phang smod pa'i dus //
NG0204:3880: bstan pa gnyen po 'jig pa la //
NG0204:3882: snod dang ldan la bstan gyur na /
NG0204:3884: snod min kun la bstan gyur na //
NG0204:3885: dus min bar ni srog zad skems //
NG0204:3886: sngags la bye brag mang bzhugs kyang *//
NG0204:3887: rtsa ba'i snying po lngar 'dus te //
NG0204:3890: yon tan phrin las lnga ru 'dus //
NG0204:3891: bzhi ni nye bar bsnyen pa dang *//
NG0204:3892: bsgrub dang las la sbyor la 'jug / rgyun du grangs shing las la sbyor //
NG0204:3893: las la sbyor kar 'bum phrag re'o //
NG0204:3894: grangs te rtsa gnyis pa ru bshad //
NG0204:3895: tha ma phrin las snying po ni //
NG0204:3896: las la sbyor ba'i sngags kyang gdab //
NG0204:3897: thugs kyi yang thugs nyi ma bzhi //
NG0204:3898: phyi nang gsang ba gsum du gsungs //
NG0204:3899: de la gsum gsum dgu ru bshad //
NG0204:3900: phyi yi nyi ma bzhi pa la //
NG0204:3901: yi ge 'bru brgyad g.yon du bskor //
NG0204:3902: phyi yi nang ni bzhi snying dril la bskor //
NG0204:3903: phyi yi gsang bar bskor ba ni //
NG0204:3904: bzhi snying dril la g.yas su bskor //
NG0204:3905: nang la gsum du dbye ba ni //
NG0204:3906: phyi yi dus su bskor ba ni //
NG0204:3907: a kro te ka bcu bdun pa'o //
NG0204:3908: nang gi nang du bskor ba ni //
NG0204:3909: ya ma me da bcu bdun pa //
NG0204:3910: g.yon du bskor te bzlas pa'o //
NG0204:3911: nang gi gsang bar bskor ba ni //
NG0204:3912: ya ma me da k+she la sogs //
NG0204:3913: yig 'bru bcu bdun g.yas su bskor //
NG0204:3914: gsang ba'i gsum du phye ba las //
NG0204:3915: phyi yi dus su bskor ba ni //
NG0204:3916: bsgrub pa'i drag sngags bcu bdun pa //
NG0204:3917: g.yon du bskor te bgrang ba'o //
NG0204:3918: gsang ba'i nang du bskor ba ni //
NG0204:3919: gsang ba'i drag sngags bcu bdun pa //
NG0204:3920: g.yas su bdun skor bgrang ba'o //
NG0204:3921: gsang ba'i gsang bar grangs pa ni //
NG0204:3922: rtsa ba dam tshig yang snying ni //
NG0204:3923: las la sbyor ba'i dus su yang *//

NG0204:4927: phyi nang gsang ba gsum du 'dus //
NG0204:4928: gshin rje de dag re re la //

NG0204:4943: g.yas dang g.yon gyi bye brag gis //

NG0204:4948: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /

NG0204:4950: gnyis pa'o // // gshin rje gshed kyis gsungs pa'i
NG0204:4951: don // nyon cig zung zhig rdo rje 'dzin //

NG0204:4953: don gnyis dag tu shes par bya //
NG0204:4954: bsnyen bsgrub dang ni phrin las so //
NG0204:4955: bsnyen pa la yang rnam gnyis te //
NG0204:4956: sngon du 'gro ba'i cho ga ste //
NG0204:4957: bsod nams bsag par bstan pa dang *//
NG0204:4958: bsnyen pa dngos nyid bstan pa'o //
NG0204:4959: thabs dang dgos pa rnam gnyis kyis //
NG0204:4960: bsod nams bsag pa'i cho gar
NG0204:4963: ngo bo dbye ba nges pa'i tshig / dgos ched rnam pa bzhi yin no //
NG0204:4964: bsnyen pa'i dbye ba bstan pa yin //
NG0204:4965: bsgrub pa la yang bcu gnyis te //
NG0204:4966: gnas dang brtul bzhugs mtshan ma gzhag / mchod rdzas gzhag dang dngos grub rten //
NG0204:4968: grub pa'i rtags dang blang ba'i thabs //
NG0204:4969: bar du gcod pa'i bgegs dang ni //
NG0204:4970: sgrub pa'i dus dang spogs pa'i thabs //
NG0204:4971: spogs pa chen po'i cho ga ste //
NG0204:4972: drag shul ting 'dzin bcu gnyis kyis //
NG0204:4973: dngos grub blang ba'i cho gar 'dod //
NG0204:4974: phrin las dag la rnam gsum te //
NG0204:4975: 'khor lo bskor dang mnan bsreg pa'o //
NG0204:4976: dus dang gang zag bskor ba'i gnas //
NG0204:4977: ngo bo dbye ba nges pa'i tshig / 'khor lo rgyu rkyen mthun pa'i dpe //
NG0204:4978: sgrub byed grogs dang ma grub skyon //
NG0204:4979: grub pa'i thabs dang spogs pa'i thabs //
NG0204:4980: dbye ba bcu gsum ma yi ngag / ces gshin rje gshed pos rab tu brjod //
NG0204:4981: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:4982: las kyi mdo byang gi skabs te le'u zhe gsum
NG0204:4983: pa'o // // de nas yang bcom ldan 'das gshin
NG0204:4984: rje gshed pos 'di skad ces gsungs so //
NG0204:4985: dus tshod mtshon cha rnon po la //
NG0204:4986: rdo rje slob dpon sku dgra sogs //
NG0204:4987: the tshom med par bsgral bas 'grub //
NG0204:4988: phag sbrul ston dpyid ra ba la //
NG0204:4989: byi ba rta ni ston dpyid 'bring *//
NG0204:4990: ston dpyid tha chung glang lug la'o //
NG0204:4991: stag spre'u dbyar dgun ra bar shes //
NG0204:4992: dbyar dgun 'bring po bya yos la'o //
NG0204:4994: de ni lo gshed zla ba'i keg khyad par nyi ma'i gshed gnyis te //
NG0204:4996: de yi dus su gsad pa shis //
NG0204:4997: zhag gi gshed du gyur pa yang *//
NG0204:4998: ra ba bzhi la bcu bzhi shis //
NG0204:4999: 'bring po bzhi yi bco lnga la //
NG0204:5000: tha chung bzhi yi bcu drug go / tshes bzhi brgyad dang bcu gcig dang *//
NG0204:5001: bco lnga bco brgyad nyi shu gnyis //
NG0204:5002: nyi shu lnga dang nyi shu dgu //
NG0204:5003: dus ni srod dang snga dro dang *//
NG0204:5004: 'jing dang nam gung gung chung dang *//
NG0204:5005: nyi myur skya rengs shar ba dang *//
NG0204:5006: nyin mtshan zhag gi go rim bzhin //

NG0204:5008: btsal nas gsod pa'i dus bstan pa //
NG0204:5009: dpyid ra tshes bdun dag la shis //
NG0204:5010: 'bring po bcu bdun dag la shis //

NG0204:5012: dbyar ra tshes brgyad 'bring po ni //
NG0204:5013: bco brgyad tha chung nyi shu brgyad //
NG0204:5014: ston ra tshes dgu 'bring po ni //
NG0204:5015: bcu dgu tha chung nyi shu dgu / dgun zla gsum yang de bzhin te //
NG0204:5016: dus su gsad pa'i las la 'jug / sa yi khams sa dpyid zla gsum //
NG0204:5017: shing gi dbyar zla ston zla @#//
NG0204:5019: dgun ni lcags khams 'chi ba'i dus //
NG0204:5020: de dus zhag gshed btu bar bya //
NG0204:5021: ra ba bzhi ni rta dar yang la gcod //
NG0204:5022: tha dar chung yang chung dus su 'bring bzhi ste //
NG0204:5023: tha chung khra la brdeg par bya //
NG0204:5024: dgun gsum skar ma gsum 'char te //
NG0204:5025: skar ma'i gshed kyi dus su ni //
NG0204:5026: sbyor ba thams cad rab na yang */
NG0204:5027: khrag thun la sogs zor rnams shis //
NG0204:5028: lo zla zhag gi dus bstan nas //
NG0204:5029: dusatshod rnon po bstan par bya //
NG0204:5030: sems can yid ni gnyid log pas //
NG0204:5031: da dus rgyu zhing 'khyams pa'i tshe //
NG0204:5032: kun kyang rnam rtog las byung bas //
NG0204:5033: sbyor ba'i stobs bskyed bsad par shis //
NG0204:5034: sha ba srod dang nam phyed na //
NG0204:5035: lug dang gnyan gyi bla yang rgyu //
NG0204:5036: pag pa tho rangs bya nyid ni //
NG0204:5037: nyi ma zer la rgyu bar bshad //
NG0204:5038: ra bla nyi ma nub ka ste //
NG0204:5039: bya bla nyi ma zer la rgyu //
NG0204:5040: g.yag dang glang bla srod la rgyu //
NG0204:5041: rta bla nyi ma gung la rgyu //
NG0204:5042: de dag dgug cing bsad par shis //
NG0204:5043: thun mong bsgral ba'i thabs su gsungs //
NG0204:5044: dngos po gcig kyang 'gyur ba'i tshe //
NG0204:5045: 'gyur ba'i bla dang sbyar te bya'o /
NG0204:5046: khams kyi gshed du bstan pa ni //
NG0204:5047: sgrub pa po dang lo zla dang *//
NG0204:5048: dus tshod kyis ni gsod par byed //
NG0204:5049: keg ni gshed po glang dang lug / lo dgra bya dang sprel nyid de //
NG0204:5050: dgun zla dbyar zla tha chung gnyis //
NG0204:5051: dus tshod nyid phyed nam phyed yol //

NG0204:5053: bsgrub pa'i sbyor bas smos ci dgos /
NG0204:5054: khyi 'brug ji yi gshed po ste //
NG0204:5055: phag dang byi ba lo dgra nyid //
NG0204:5056: mi mthun bdun zur the tshom med //
NG0204:5057: zla gshed ston dpyid tha chung ste //
NG0204:5058: zla ba'i bdun zur rdo rjes gcod //
NG0204:5059: tho rangs srod la gsod par byed //
NG0204:5061: sbyor bas bdun rgyud the tshom med //
NG0204:5062: gung la khyi 'brug shing khams pa //

NG0204:5064: gsod pa'i las la the tshom med //

NG0204:5066: bdun zur gshed du gyur pa ste //
NG0204:5067: tshangs pa'i me bzhin gsod par byed //
NG0204:5068: zla gshed srog dang mi mthun pa'i //

NG0204:5074: lo dgra glang lug gnyis kyis te //

NG0204:5080: drag sngags tshogs kyis cham la dbab //
NG0204:5081: nyi ma gru sogs bre ru 'byor //

NG0204:5083: mig dmar khrum smad la ro sman //
NG0204:5086: phur bu rgyal stod rgyal smad mthun //
NG0204:5087: pa sangs byed zhug rta chung nyid //
NG0204:5088: spen pa sa ri sa ga ste //

NG0204:5093: zla ba rgyal smad bre ru gsod //

NG0204:5095: gza' lhag dbyug pa nyid kyis 'jig / phur bu

NG0204:5097: lag sor gsum // spen pa bya ma bdud kyi nyi //

NG0204:5100: mi 'phrod bdun du bshad pa ni //
NG0204:5101: nyi ma khrums smad zla ba dang *//

NG0204:5112: sangs la bya gzhug 'jig / spen pa la ni

NG0204:5121: khra'am spyang ki lta bus skyob //
NG0204:5122: dgra bla yin te gsur chen btang */
