NG0204:5941: gro ga shing shun bris la gzhug / bya rog gsob dang spyang ka'i gsob //
NG0204:5942: brgyad ste shar nub kha bstan gzhag / chang phud nang du gser brdar la //
NG0204:5943: dngul skyogs gang yang gzhag par bya //
NG0204:5944: g.yab dar nag pos g.yab tshul bya //
NG0204:5945: lug nag lcags ru gser mig la //
NG0204:5946: re ba'i sgye ni khal du bkal //
NG0204:5947: g.yas su pho rnams ming rus gzhug / g.yon du
NG0204:5948: mo rnams ming rus gzhug / sngo dmar skud pas
NG0204:5949: gong rmed bya // ra la dar lce mthing nag gdab //
NG0204:5950: mig gnyis nang du rin chen brdar //
NG0204:5951: dar dkar yug gis mig gnyis dgab //
NG0204:5952: dkyil 'khor byang shar gra ru dgod //
NG0204:5953: dur khrod ras la 'khor lo bca' //
NG0204:5954: thod pa dug khrag bsres la dgang *//
NG0204:5955: gos nag gyon la thod nag bcings //
NG0204:5956: bdud kyi g.yab dar lag tu thogs //
NG0204:5957: gtum chen bstod la bdud rnams rbad //
NG0204:5959: hum phat ba hum le ma sa sha sta ha
NG0204:5960: sta ba ba le rang ba mang sha sa ra
NG0204:5961: ya hum ma he sa mang ga la ya hum
NG0204:5962: phat / gsum 'bum bzlas na gang yang 'grub //
NG0204:5963: de bzhin bsgrub na mngon du 'gyur //
NG0204:5964: dpal 'jam dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:5965: bdud gsang ba ltar bsgrub pa'i skabs te le'u lnga bcu @#//
NG0204:5967: / de nas bcom ldan 'das gshed pos 'jig rten
NG0204:5968: gyi khams mer bsreg pa'i btsan phyi ltar bsgrub pa
NG0204:5969: 'di gsungs so // brag dmar rtsa'am dur khrod du //
NG0204:5970: sa bdag zhi byang klu gtor gtang *//
NG0204:5972: ra dmar khrag gis chag chag gdab //
NG0204:5973: dbus kyi lte ba dmar po la //
NG0204:5974: zla gam dmar po brgyad kyis bskor //
NG0204:5976: zla gam re la ma ra ya //
NG0204:5977: ra dmar bse 'gram phyi rten bca' //
NG0204:5978: dbus su bshos bu gru gang gzhag / ra khrag
NG0204:5979: dag gis dmar por byug / za 'og dmar po
NG0204:5980: mda' gang gdags // ra lpags dmar po mda' gang la //
NG0204:5981: zer mo ldam pa'i phod kyis brgyan //
NG0204:5982: dbus kyi zla gam steng du gzhag / de 'khor zla gam brgyad po la //
NG0204:5983: bshos cha brgyad la mda' dmar brgyad //
NG0204:5984: dar dang ra lpags dmar po dang *//
NG0204:5985: zer mo'i phod kyis brgyan pa brgyad //
NG0204:5986: phyi rim zla gam brgyad la dgod //
NG0204:5987: gser brdar chang phud bya'o dgu //
NG0204:5988: 'bras dang til nag la sogs pas //
NG0204:5989: zla gam dgu la phul dgu gzhag / dur khrod ras la 'khor lo ni //
NG0204:5990: rtsibs brgyad ba ru bya bar bshad /
NG0204:5991: om la li bra ma ni re rtse thal ba ni /
NG0204:5992: tri nyi nyi sham tri mu tri ri tri tri /
NG0204:5993: de tri ham sham stamm sarba karma se ba be ba swa ha /
NG0204:5994: 'di ni dbang dang drag po'i sngags //
NG0204:5995: dgug dang rbad pa'i sngags 'di brjod //
NG0204:5996: srog la li pra ma ni bam ril dgra bo nr-i dza /
NG0204:5998: bam ri li li dgra bo nr-i dza /
NG0204:5999: kro d+hi ko ya bam ri li li dgra bo nr-i dza /
NG0204:6000: kro d+hi ki la ya sha la bam ri li li dgra bo nr-i dza /
NG0204:6001: om tri gam sham ma ra ya bam ri li li dgra bo nr-i dza /
NG0204:6002: mu tri ma ra ya bam ri li li dgra bo nr-i dza /
NG0204:6003: re tri ma ra ya bam ri li li dgra bo ma ra ya nr-i dza /
NG0204:6004: ham sham stam bu ma ra ya bam ri li li dgra bo nr-i dza /
NG0204:6005: rang gsang dpon g.yog dgu'i snying po brjod par bya'o //
NG0204:6006: srog la li pra ma ni dam nyams dgra bo'i snying la dza dza dza /
NG0204:6007: srog la ma ra ya nr-i dam nyams dgra bo'i srog la dza dza dza /
NG0204:6008: srog kro d+hi ki la ya ma ra ya dgra bo'i snying la dza dza dza /
NG0204:6009: srog kro d+hi sho la ya ya ma ra ya dgra bo'i snying la dza dza dza //
NG0204:6010: srog kam ti kam sham ma ra ya dam nyams dgra bo'i snying la dza dza dza /
NG0204:6011: srog gi sham tri ma ra ya dam nyams dgra bo'i snying la dza dza dza /
NG0204:6012: srog mu tri re'u hri dam nyams dgra bo'i snying la dza dza dza /
NG0204:6013: dmigs pa'i gzugs la sngags kyis brdeg / gshin rje bstod la btsan rnams rbad //
NG0204:6017: mi ring dmar po mthu rtsal can //
NG0204:6018: dbu la skra med bskal pa'i me dpung @#//
NG0204:6020: 'jig rten khams kun me yis bsreg / smin ma lcags kyu 'khril ba 'dra //
NG0204:6021: spyan rtsa dmar po dam nyams dgra la bzlog / sku la le brgan dmar po'i 'jol ber gsol //
NG0204:6022: g.yas nas btsan gyi rgyu zhags dgra la 'debs //
NG0204:6023: g.yon nas hu lu'i ltas ngan dgra la 'bebs //
NG0204:6024: zhabs la lcags lham yu thung gsol //
NG0204:6025: sbrul nag stong gi chun bskor can //
NG0204:6026: sbrul nag gzhibs pa'i sku regs bcings //
NG0204:6027: skar chen dmar po'i tshar tshar can //
NG0204:6028: bzhugs ni gling bzhi khyab par bzhugs //
NG0204:6029: nam gyi gung la rgyu tsa na //
NG0204:6030: brag gi wa mo kha nag chibs //
NG0204:6031: nyi ma'i zer la rgyu tsa na //
NG0204:6032: chibs su ltas ngan gla ba chibs //
NG0204:6033: nyi ma'i gung la rgyu tsa na //
NG0204:6034: chibs su bra bo rting dkar chibs //
NG0204:6035: dam rdzas gtor ma 'di longs la //
NG0204:6036: yab gcig 'jam dpal bka' byung gis //
NG0204:6037: 'khor gyi btsan rnams las la bskul //
NG0204:6038: 'jig rten khams su me yi bskal pa thobs //
NG0204:6039: dgra bo'i rnam shes brgyad po thal bar rlogs //
NG0204:6040: skyes bu chen po dgra la ya //
NG0204:6041: rang gsang mched dgu dgra la ya //
NG0204:6042: btsan gyi zhags pa da sdogs la //
NG0204:6043: thar ma dgra la da thob cig khrag skyug gzer thabs phur gyis thob //
NG0204:6045: tsa ra kham rog rten du bca' //
NG0204:6046: lo dang zla bar brlag par 'gyur ro //
NG0204:6047: be'u rdzi wa dang rta chung dang *//
NG0204:6048: lag sor rnams la gong bzhin bskul //
NG0204:6049: chang phud gtor zhing las gnyer gtad //
NG0204:6050: rtags phyin pa dang gtang rag gtang *//
NG0204:6051: gsob dang bshos cha dbul bar bya //
NG0204:6052: gshin rje zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:6053: 'jig rten khams kun mes bsregs pa'i btsan gyi zla
NG0204:6054: gsang phyi ltar bsgrub pa'i skabs te le'u nga gcig
NG0204:6055: pa'o /// / de nas bcom ldan 'das 'jigs byed chen pos /
NG0204:6056: btsan nang ltar bsgrub pa 'di gsungs so //
NG0204:6057: gong gsum kha'am brag dmar rtsa //
NG0204:6058: dur khrod nags tshal mthug po ru //
NG0204:6060: dug dang khrag gis chag chag gdab //
NG0204:6061: dbus su gru gsum mthur du brko //
NG0204:6062: mu su ra yi thod pa ru //
NG0204:6063: rdo sol spra ba ras la sogs //
NG0204:6064: til mar bsres te gzhag par bya //
NG0204:6065: de la zla gam gsum gyis bskor //
NG0204:6066: phyi rim 'dzam bu'i gling bzhi bris //
NG0204:6067: lcags ri la sogs me 'od bris //
NG0204:6068: dbus su ya ma gshed po ste //
NG0204:6069: zla gam gsum la yum sras dgod //
NG0204:6070: zla gam steng du btsan gyi rgyal //
NG0204:6071: rdo rje reg bya gser mig dgod //
NG0204:6072: lho ru rdo rje grags mchog dgod //
NG0204:6073: nub tu rdo rje mgyogs byed rtsal //
NG0204:6074: byang du rdo rje shu bo 'bar //
NG0204:6075: yab yum rdzas su bshams pa yang *//
NG0204:6076: mi sha rta sha'i gtor ma dang *//
NG0204:6078: chen gcig la brten te bsgrub //
NG0204:6079: phyogs bzhir gtor ma bzhi byas la //
NG0204:6080: shu bo mched bzhi'i rdzas su dgod //
NG0204:6081: ra dmar snying dang bya se'i snying *//
NG0204:6082: rta 'tshal snying la btsan rnams brten //
NG0204:6083: bya rgod mda' la le brgan dar //
NG0204:6084: lag tu thogs la rtag tu g.yab //
NG0204:6085: gri bo'i thod par thar ma bca' //
NG0204:6086: rtag tu ra gsur rgyun du gtang */
NG0204:6087: gser skyems la sogs gser sbyar bas //
NG0204:6088: rtag tu btsan la mchod pa bya //
NG0204:6089: spyugs pa'i glu blang rnga gling 'bud //
NG0204:6090: rtag tu nyung dkar nyung nag la //
NG0204:6091: sngags bzlas gru gsum thod par gsib //
NG0204:6092: rnam gsum ting 'dzin btsan rnams bskyed //
NG0204:6093: a pi shu sa ma ya ra dza pe ni
NG0204:6094: a na na sta tri sha la rbad dz+ha ra
NG0204:6095: gting pa na d+ha ra shu na tsit+ta b+hasmi ku
NG0204:6096: ku dza dza / khri'am 'bum du bzlas gyur na //
NG0204:6097: sku yang dngos su ston par 'gyur //
NG0204:6098: gzhan yang rta med srab sgra dang *//
NG0204:6100: de bzhin las la sbyor bar bya //
NG0204:6101: gshed po bskul la btsan rnams rbad //
NG0204:6103: rdo sol rdzas sbyar dam rdzas la //
NG0204:6104: rtsa ba'i sngags la ram ram sbyar //
NG0204:6105: de yi sngags rnams rab tu bzlas //
NG0204:6106: zla gsang bu la shes bya zhing *//
NG0204:6107: gsad pa'i las kyang gong dang 'dra //
NG0204:6108: gtso ru rang gi dam tshig bsrung *//
NG0204:6109: ting nge 'dzin gyi spyod lam bya //
NG0204:6110: yengs na gang yang mi 'grub ste //
NG0204:6111: rtag tu mi dang nye mi bya //
NG0204:6112: thar ma bcas pa'i thod pa de //
NG0204:6114: brag btsan klu btsan yod sar sba //
NG0204:6116: 'jam dpal gshin rje zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:6117: 'jig rten gyi khams mes bsreg pa btsan gyi zla
NG0204:6118: gsang nang ltar bsgrub pa'i skabs te le'u nga gnyis
NG0204:6119: pa'o // // de nas bcom ldan 'das 'jigs byed
NG0204:6120: chen pos btsan gsang ba ltar bsgrub pa 'di gsungs
NG0204:6121: so // dgon pa dur khrod lta bu ru //
NG0204:6122: dkyil 'khor mthing nag gru gsum brtsig / dbus su rabs chad thod pa ru /
NG0204:6123: khrag sogs dug sogs rdo sol dang *//
NG0204:6124: dur khrod ras dang til gyi mar *//
NG0204:6125: ra dmar snying dang ra khrag blugs //
NG0204:6126: ming dang rus bris thod par gzhug / bse phor zangs gzhong gtor mas dgang *//
NG0204:6127: drung gzhag srog snying tshad du grangs //
NG0204:6128: om de ba tri mang gan dza mu sa mu
NG0204:6129: sa ma ra na ya ma ra na ya dgra
NG0204:6130: bo che ge mo'i srog breng breng thum b+h+yo dza
NG0204:6131: dza / 'di ni rab tu mi bsgyur yang 'grung sngags //
NG0204:6132: thod pa'i nang du 'bum du bzlas //
NG0204:6134: ri la sbas na ri mes tshig khyad par rgya mtsho lta bu'am //
NG0204:6135: chu mig sbas na chu yang khol //
NG0204:6139: de nas sngags de nyid 'o zu'i sdong po la /
NG0204:6140: lan stong du bzlas nas byin na smyo bar 'gyur ro //
NG0204:6141: d+ha du ra'i lo ma dang sha pra pa de dang */
NG0204:6142: ka ka ri la bzlas nas byin na mdzer 'gyur ro //
NG0204:6143: be'u be dang ka ne la bzlas nas byin na /
NG0204:6145: dza yi 'bras la bzlas nas phyogs su gtor na /
NG0204:6146: sbrul chen po khang pa'i nang du 'ong bar 'gyur ro //
NG0204:6147: rdo sol la bzlas nas b+han d+ha'i nang du chang
NG0204:6148: dang sbyar nas rtswa gseb bam shing gseb tu sbas
NG0204:6150: rdo sol la bzlas te chang gral du grogs po'i
NG0204:6151: chang la btab na mer reng gis 'gro bar 'gyur
NG0204:6152: ro // bse zho dang btsan dug sbyar la btab
NG0204:6153: nas dgra'i lus sam sha la reg pa'i gos la
NG0204:6154: bskus na lhog pa dkar pos 'chi bar 'gyur ro
NG0204:6155: ro // // 'jam dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:6156: 'jig rten mes bsreg btsan gyi zla gsang gsang ba
NG0204:6157: ltar bsgrub pa'i skabs te le'u nga gsum pa'o //
NG0204:6158: // de nas bcom ldan 'das gshin rje gshed pos
NG0204:6159: / chu 'khyags drag tu dbab pa khyab 'jug gza'i drag sngags 'di gsungs te /
NG0204:6160: gza' phyi ltar bsgrub pa'i thabs bshad pa /
NG0204:6161: thog mar dad pa rab tu bskyed //
NG0204:6162: ri gsum rtse 'am dur khrod du //
NG0204:6163: dbang thob bya phyir snga ma mnyes bya zhing *//
NG0204:6164: dkyil 'khor bris nas dam tshig dbang dag nod //
NG0204:6165: dgos pa bsgrub phyir man ngag thob par bya //
NG0204:6166: man ngag thob nas bsnyen bsgrub mtha' ru dbyung *//
NG0204:6167: bsnyen pa bya zhing mthun rdzas 'bad de bsag khyab 'jug las kyi go rim ni //
NG0204:6168: gzhan dang mthun par cho ga dang *//
NG0204:6169: mchod dang gzu+u dpang gsol ba gdab //
NG0204:6170: gtor ma la sogs cho ga bya //
NG0204:6171: dbab gsad las kyi go rim ni //
NG0204:6172: tshes grangs phyogs dang dus tshod dang *//
NG0204:6174: go rim bzhin du so sor sbyar //
NG0204:6175: bzhi la nub nas shar du srod //
NG0204:6176: ma mor sprul te rkang pa g.yas //
NG0204:6177: brgyad la shar lho mtshams nas su //
NG0204:6178: nyi ma dros te nub byang du //
NG0204:6179: dgra lha'i rgyal mo mjug ma sprul //
NG0204:6180: bcu gcig 'jing la byang nas lhor //
NG0204:6181: bdud du sprul te lag pa gnyis //
NG0204:6182: bco lnga nam phyed lho nub nas //
NG0204:6183: byang shar mtshams su rgyu ba ste //
NG0204:6184: srin por sprul te mgo bo rgyu //
NG0204:6185: bco brgyad nam yol shar nas nub //
NG0204:6186: dmu ru sprul nas dpung mgo g.yon //
NG0204:6187: nyi shu gnyis la nyi ma myur //
NG0204:6188: nub byang mtshams nas shar lho ru //
NG0204:6189: gshin rjer sprul nas lag pa g.yon //
NG0204:6190: nyi shu lnga la lho nas byang *//
NG0204:6191: skya rengs chas te dpung mgo mig / klu btsan gdon du sprul te rgyu //
NG0204:6194: byang shar mtshams nas lho nub tu //
NG0204:6195: gza' bdud chen por sprul te rgyu //
NG0204:6196: de yi dbab gsad sbyor ba ni //
NG0204:6197: phyogs kyi gdon sprul re re la //
NG0204:6198: gsad pa'i sbyor ba so sor bya //
NG0204:6199: gdon sprul so sor rgyu+u ba ste //
NG0204:6200: ma mor sprul pa'i gzugs brnyan ni //
NG0204:6201: nag mo chen mo ral pa can //
NG0204:6202: 'jig pa'i rgyan cha mang po dang *//
NG0204:6203: lag na thod khrag 'thor zhing rgyu //
NG0204:6204: rlung drag thog dang rdzi kha rgyu //
NG0204:6205: rgyal mo sngo skya ka dar thogs //
NG0204:6206: sngo skya zhon te 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NG0204:6207: sgra dang ser ba mtshan mo'o //
NG0204:6208: sprul pa bdud ni mdog nag po //
NG0204:6209: lag na gri nag zhags pa thogs //
NG0204:6210: rta nag zhon te gdon dang bcas //
NG0204:6211: btsan thabs drag po'i nad rnams dang *//
NG0204:6212: dus med mtshan ma mang du 'byung *//
NG0204:6213: 'jigs pa'i srin po sngo nag la //
NG0204:6214: mig rtsa dmar la sdang mig bgrad //
NG0204:6215: mche ba gtsigs te za ba'i tshul //
NG0204:6216: mda' gzhu thogs te gdon dang rgyu //
NG0204:6218: sprul pa dmu ste thog ser 'bebs //
NG0204:6219: dmar po khrag gi thig le can //
NG0204:6220: ba glang zhon te 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NG0204:6221: mtshan ma thob dang sprin nag 'khrugs //
NG0204:6222: klu gdon drag por sprul pa ni //
NG0204:6223: sbrul nag chen po 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NG0204:6225: chu drag glog dang chas pa'o //
NG0204:6226: nag po chen po 'khor lo thogs //
NG0204:6227: gdon gyi gtso bor sprul te 'ong *//
NG0204:6228: rgyu ba'i dus dang mtshungs nges na //
NG0204:6229: mtshan ma myur du phung bar 'gyur //
NG0204:6230: de la dbab gsad sbyor ba brgyad //
NG0204:6231: nges par rgyu ba'i dus su bya //
NG0204:6233: gru bzhi'i dkyil 'khor dbus su ni //
NG0204:6234: 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad dbus su e //
NG0204:6235: phyogs mtshams brgyad la e brgyad bkod //
NG0204:6236: e dgu nag po'i 'khor lo bskor //
NG0204:6237: 'khor lo'i rtsibs la sprul pa brgyad //
NG0204:6238: bskyed la dbab gsad sbyor ba bri //
NG0204:6239: dbus su gshed po yab yum ste /
NG0204:6240: kha hir bcas pas gtor ma sbyin //
NG0204:6241: phyogs mtshams brgyad kyi sprul pa la //
NG0204:6242: so so'i las kyi bya ba brtsam //
NG0204:6243: dgug dang brdeg dang bstab pa'i las //
NG0204:6244: 'grogs pa'i tshul te gdong tshugs med //
NG0204:6245: bsreg dang mchod pa la sogs pa //
NG0204:6246: phyogs mtshams brgyad nas drangs te dbul //
NG0204:6247: phyogs mtshams brgyad du gsad pa ste //
NG0204:6248: dbus kyi e la bsreg pa'o //
NG0204:6249: sprul pa'i mgo bo rgyu ba'i tshe //
NG0204:6250: brnag pa'i dpral ba'i dbyings su gdab //
NG0204:6251: rkang pa g.yas g.yon rgyu ba ni //
NG0204:6252: bol gong g.yas g.yon gnyis su gdab //
NG0204:6253: sprul pa yan lag go rim bzhin //
NG0204:6254: gdab pa'i las kyang de bzhin gdab //
NG0204:6255: tsher ma can gyi shing la bsreg / rgyu ba'i dus su mtshungs @#//
NG0204:6257: phung bar 'gyur te gdon mi za //
NG0204:6258: gdon dang phye ma rnam pa gnyis //
NG0204:6259: gdon gyi rdzas la nus pa yod //
NG0204:6260: phye ma gdon gyi bya ba de //
NG0204:6261: zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las gsungs //
NG0204:6262: gza' bdud rgyu ba'i dus nges na //
NG0204:6263: rjes dang dri ma'i 'dag pa la //
NG0204:6264: gos dum dri ma rnying pa dang *//
NG0204:6265: gdug pa'i gzugs brnyan bzhi byas te //
NG0204:6266: rnam grangs nad du gsad bya na //
NG0204:6267: gong ma'i rdzas dang tsha ba gsum //
NG0204:6268: bsres te gzugs brnyan bya bar gsungs //
NG0204:6269: myur du gsad pa'i sbyor ba ni //
NG0204:6270: gong ma'i steng du ha las bya //
NG0204:6271: gong ma bzhi la lcags phye dang */
NG0204:6272: khrag gi sbyor bas dri nyid du //
NG0204:6273: til dang ske tshe nyung nag dang */
NG0204:6274: khrag sna zi ra gu gul dang *//
NG0204:6275: gong gi rdzas kyis ma nges gsad //
NG0204:6276: dur khrod ras sam shing shun la //
NG0204:6277: skyang nul byas te smug nag gam //
NG0204:6278: yang na sngo nag dmar por bya //
NG0204:6279: de la brnag pa'i sbyor ba bya'o //
NG0204:6280: myur du dbab pa'i las bya na //
NG0204:6281: dam sri yul gyi chu sogs bsag / yugs sa mo'am rabs chad thod //
NG0204:6282: yang na mdze can thod pa ru //
NG0204:6283: mi khrag khyi khrag ra khrag dang *//
NG0204:6284: mngal khrag la sogs dme khrag sogs //
NG0204:6285: ba dkar 'o ma mdzo dang ra'i //
NG0204:6286: 'o ma la sogs sbyar bar bya //
NG0204:6287: sngo sna dug sna gu gul sbyar //
NG0204:6288: gang 'bebs chu mig klu yod sar //
NG0204:6289: bsregs sam bskol na klu rnams dang *//
NG0204:6290: dus tshod gza' yi gdong thug na //
NG0204:6292: ma ha tsan+d+ha rak+sha tri tha ni ma tha ya /
NG0204:6293: che ge mo la tri b+h+yo /
NG0204:6294: zhes pa ni sprul pa srin po'i gdon gyis dbab cing gsad pa'o //
NG0204:6295: na ga ra dza be ni ni a nan sta /
NG0204:6296: na ga ra dza ra sha ting pan d+ha ra k+shu na /
NG0204:6299: klu'i gdon gyis dbab cing gsad pa'o //
NG0204:6300: rmu tri tsa d+ha dum dum bum bum kha la rak+sha thum ri li li /
NG0204:6301: kha shag bam raka s+t+wam thum ri li li /
NG0204:6302: dmu bdud sprul pas dbab cing gsad pa'o //
NG0204:6303: ma ma sa ma ya ma trag sha ma tra
NG0204:6304: 'ga' nas kha ya ku ru te tso pa la
NG0204:6305: ya a / yu shwa ha ra d+ha ra /
NG0204:6306: u ma ma da ma ni sha trum na sha
NG0204:6307: ya ni dza dzah ma mo'i gdon gyis dbab gsad
NG0204:6308: pa'o // tri dkar mo tri dul dul snying khrag la ril ril /
NG0204:6309: chom chom rtsa la thun shig ma ra na dza /
NG0204:6310: rgyal mo sngo skyas dbab gsad pa'o //
NG0204:6311: ya ma tsan d+ha d+hi ta dza la tsakra d+ha
NG0204:6312: ra na sha ya dgra bo nr-i ma ra ya
NG0204:6313: sod sod chom chom shig shig gshin rje'i gdon gyi
NG0204:6314: dbab gsad pa'o // ma ha bi d+he ba tra
NG0204:6315: bish+nu tsan+d+ha ru ba ni ra hu la dgra bo'i
NG0204:6316: dbab gsad pa'o // tsit+ta la / shu na tsa to kha hi /
NG0204:6317: he ka li ma ha tsan d+ha ma ra ya nr-i khug khug dza dza /
NG0204:6318: gza' bdud chen pos dbab gsad pa'o //
NG0204:6319: bdud tri ni ri tra pa na tri ya /
NG0204:6322: srog rtsa thun che ge mo nr-i nr-i dzah / @#//
NG0204:6323: ces bzlas gar dmigs thogs pa med //
NG0204:6324: gtum chen nyid la rab bstod cing *//
NG0204:6325: gza' bdud chen po rab tu rbad //
NG0204:6326: hum ri rab phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad nas //
NG0204:6327: lha srin sde brgyad bskul re ran //
NG0204:6328: khyab 'jug chen po sku bzhengs shig / gtum po chen po bskyod tsa na //
NG0204:6330: de yis ki kang 'bebs byed na //
NG0204:6331: gza' bdud chen po mi srun pa //
NG0204:6332: khyab 'jug chen po kun tu rgyug / 'jigs byed rog ti sprul pa'i lus //
NG0204:6333: lus po gcig la mgo bo dgu //
NG0204:6334: mgo lus med par mig gis khengs //
NG0204:6335: ro stod mi la ro smad sbrul //
NG0204:6336: lus ni brjid pa'i dud ka la //
NG0204:6337: lag na chu srin zhags pa thogs //
NG0204:6338: pha ni srin la ma ni klu //
NG0204:6339: klu srin tshogs pa'i mthu bo che //
NG0204:6340: lho nub mtshams nas sku bzhengs nas //
NG0204:6341: zla ba'i rjes gcod shar du rgyug / nyi ma'i
NG0204:6342: rjes gcod nub tu rgyug / nyin mo rgyu zhing
NG0204:6343: mtshan mo 'joms // bar snang khams nas rgyu tsa na //
NG0204:6344: 'jig rten khams kun sgrol bar mdzad //
NG0204:6345: lo nyes 'khrugs pa yams nad gtong *//
NG0204:6346: nyi ma zla ba lto ru za //
NG0204:6347: rgya mtsho'i gting nas gnas pa'i tshe //
NG0204:6348: klu rnams kun kyang 'khrug cing slong *//
NG0204:6349: thog ser sa g.yos ki kang 'bebs //
NG0204:6350: 'jigs byed chen po mi srun pa //
NG0204:6351: ming brgya pa la mtshan stong po //
NG0204:6352: dus tshod tshes grangs kun gyi bdag / lha 'dre kun gyi nang dbyen byed //
NG0204:6353: lha srin sde brgyad dmag dpon byed //
NG0204:6354: 'byung ba lnga yi bdud chen po //
NG0204:6355: mtshan ni rnam pa dgu ru grags //
NG0204:6356: steng 'og phyogs mtshams thams cad nas //
NG0204:6357: kun nas rgyug cing ki kang 'bebs //
NG0204:6358: lho nub mtshams nas bskyod pa'i tshe //
NG0204:6359: srin po rak+sha bi tri pa //
NG0204:6360: ki kang pa ta chen po bya //
NG0204:6361: srin po'i king kang chen po 'bebs //
NG0204:6362: shar lho mtshams nas bskyod pa'i tshe //
NG0204:6363: drang srong chen po ra hu la //
NG0204:6364: drang srong gi ni king kang 'bebs //
NG0204:6365: ki kang bdag nyid can zhes bya //
NG0204:6366: byang shar mtshams nas bskyod pa'i tshe //
NG0204:6368: byi na ya ga pho nyar 'gyed //
NG0204:6369: ki kang 'bebs pa'i las la brtson //
NG0204:6370: nub byang mtshams nas bskyod tsa na //
NG0204:6371: du ba mjug ring chen po bya //
NG0204:6372: 'jig rten khams na mthu bo che //
NG0204:6373: 'jig rten g.yo 'gul byed pa'i bdag / lho yi phyogs nas bskyod pa'i tshe /
NG0204:6374: khyab 'jug chen po bya ba ste //
NG0204:6375: dus tshod tshes grangs kun tu rgyug / sprul pa'i sku ni ki kang 'bebs /
NG0204:6376: shar gyi phyogs nas bskyod pa'i tshe //
NG0204:6377: dmu bdud chen po ha li ka / byi nu ra tsa'i ki kang 'bebs //
NG0204:6378: dmu yi ki kang 'bebs par byed //
NG0204:6379: byang gi phyogs nas bskyod pa'i tshe //
NG0204:6383: ki kang 'bar ba tsa ra ka / nub kyi phyogs nas bskyod pa'i tshe //
NG0204:6384: srid pa'i ma mo rnams dang rol //
NG0204:6385: ma mo'i ki kang kun gyi bdag / ljang sngon chen po'i ki kang 'bebs //
NG0204:6386: lho nub mtshams nas bskyod tsa na //
NG0204:6387: rog ti bya rog mgo brtsegs te //
NG0204:6389: sngon du su phrad khyur mid za /
NG0204:6390: khyod ni khro chen sprul pa ste //
NG0204:6391: lho nub mtshams nas sku bskyod nas //
NG0204:6392: lha srin sde brgyad dmag dpon byed //
NG0204:6393: nub nas shar du bskyod tsa na //
NG0204:6394: srid pa'i ma mo'i dmag dpon byed //
NG0204:6395: nad ngan ki kang dbab pa'i dus la babs //
NG0204:6396: shar lho mtshams nas bskyod tsa na //
NG0204:6397: dgra lha'i rgyal po dmag dpon byed //
NG0204:6398: thog dang bu yug ki kang ni //
NG0204:6399: dam sri gdug pa'i snying la 'bebs //
NG0204:6400: byang nas lho ru bskyod tsa na //
NG0204:6401: bdud dmag kun gyi dmag dpon byed //
NG0204:6402: bdud kyi ki kang hur thum 'bebs //
NG0204:6403: bdud kyi ki kang dgra la ya //
NG0204:6404: byang shar mtshams nas bskyod tsa na //
NG0204:6405: srin po 'bum gyi dmag dpon byed //
NG0204:6406: srin po'i ki kang dgra la ya //
NG0204:6407: gri thabs sna tshogs ki kang ya //
NG0204:6408: shar nas nub tu bskyod tsa na //
NG0204:6409: dmu bdud yongs kyi dmag dpon byed //
NG0204:6410: dmu rdo 'bebs pa'i las byed cing *//
NG0204:6411: gar rbad dmu yi ki kang gtong *//
NG0204:6412: nub byang mtshams nas bskyod tsha na //
NG0204:6413: gshin rje yongs kyi dmag dpon byed //
NG0204:6414: skye 'gro yongs kyi bla tshe sdud //
NG0204:6415: gshin rje'i ki kang dbang med 'bebs //
NG0204:6416: lho nas byang du bskyod pa'i tshe //
NG0204:6417: klu btsan kun gyi dmag dpon byed //
NG0204:6418: thog dang ser ba'i sna 'dren cing *//
NG0204:6419: thog ser mdze nad ki kang 'bebs //
NG0204:6420: nub byang mtshams nas bskyod tsa na //
NG0204:6421: gtib grir gsod pa'i ki kang 'bebs //
NG0204:6422: mdun du gang byung khyur mid byed //
NG0204:6423: ki kang sna tshogs 'bebs pa'i bdag / ki kang sna tshogs dgra la ya //
NG0204:6424: zhes brjod cing rak+ta sbreng phrin las bcol //
NG0204:6425: gsad na bla phur gzugs la brdeg / om badzra ki li ki la ya /
NG0204:6426: shi kri bi tri ki li ki la ya /
NG0204:6427: che ge mo ma ra la hum phat /
NG0204:6431: ba ra ta thum ru thum ru pa ra pa shu+u da na ta pa ra pa ta ya /
NG0204:6432: ru ti ru ti sha sa ya /
NG0204:6433: shan ti ku la tri dza /
NG0204:6434: zhes ni gsad pa'i las sbyor bya //
NG0204:6436: sngags kyi man ngag zhag gcig bya //
NG0204:6437: om me kha kha thun kha thun /
NG0204:6439: na pu ta na na kha le ra thun ra thun tu /
NG0204:6440: zhes pa'i sngags bzlas khro tshul bstan /
NG0204:6441: mig bzlog kha bgrad mig sprin las /
NG0204:6442: khrag sprin dmar pos 'khrigs shing 'gril bar bsam //
NG0204:6446: gnam sa ri brag kun tu yang *//
NG0204:6447: 'ba' ri sha yas gdon mi za //
NG0204:6448: 'jam dpal gshin rje zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:6449: chu 'khyags ser ba dbab pa khyab 'jug gza' yi drag sngags skabs te le'u nga bzhi pa'o ///
NG0204:6450: / de nas yang bcom ldan 'das 'jigs byed chen pos /
NG0204:6451: chu 'khyags drag tu dbab pa'i phyir //
NG0204:6452: rog ti gza' yi nang bsgrub gsungs //
NG0204:6453: dur khrod la sogs dgon pa ru //
NG0204:6454: dkyil 'khor gru gsum sbrag ma bya //
NG0204:6455: gru gsum sbrag ma'i nang rol du //
NG0204:6456: snel gri'i thod pa 'og tu gzhag / mngal khrag la sogs khrag sna tshogs //
NG0204:6457: dug dang snga sngo dkar gsum blug / rabs chad thod pas steng nas dgab //
NG0204:6458: gru gsum nang du gzhag par bya //
NG0204:6459: bsnyen pa bya ba'i thabs dag la //
NG0204:6460: lha bsnyen sum stong byas nas ni //
NG0204:6461: tshes bzhi bco lnga brgyad dus la //
NG0204:6462: gza' chen nyid kyi snying po bzlas //
NG0204:6463: stong rdzogs thun la nyung gis brab //
NG0204:6464: om bya sha me ke du ru ma shi ri
NG0204:6465: kha ra dz+wa la a ka ta swa ha /
NG0204:6466: stong rdzogs thun khrag la bstim /
NG0204:6467: om dza ba ti ra hu ma ha kro d+ha sha ra na hum phat /
NG0204:6468: sngags la stong ngam khri ru bzlas //
NG0204:6469: bzlas pa rdzogs nas nyung gis brab //
NG0204:6470: nyi shu dgu 'am tshes gcig la //
NG0204:6471: bsnyen pa rdzogs nas sa btsang sba //
NG0204:6472: thun gcig gnas su rten du bca' //
NG0204:6473: mis ma 'phrigs par gsang sngags bzlas /
NG0204:6474: om kro d+hi tra lo glo bur skying 'dang phob //
NG0204:6475: trag rak+sha snying kha rag b+h+yo /
NG0204:6476: khrag ma mu sha ma b+h+yo /
NG0204:6483: rkyang rje rkyang mo tsu ru tsu ru hum phat /
NG0204:6484: de nas zor sngags mdzub bstan la //
NG0204:6485: yul gyi phyogs su bzlas pa bya //
NG0204:6486: ri bo'i rtser song thab zor 'phang *//
NG0204:6487: chu skyes zla ba tshes bzhi nas //
NG0204:6488: nyi shu dgu mthar bsnyen rdzogs nas //
NG0204:6489: chu 'khyus zla ba kun tu dbab //
NG0204:6490: de ltar las rnams byas gyur na //
NG0204:6492: skyi 'dang ri rnams nyil bar byed //
NG0204:6493: 'jam dpal gshin rje zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:6494: chu 'khyags khrag tu dbab pa'i zla gsang nang bsgrub kyi skabs te le'u nga lnga pa'o ///
NG0204:6495: / de nas yang bcom ldan 'das 'jigs byed chen pos 'di skad ces gsol to //
NG0204:6496: 'gal ba chom la dbab slad du /
NG0204:6497: khyab 'jug gza' yi gsang bsgrub gsungs //
NG0204:6498: sgra gcan chen po nyi zla'i gnyen //
NG0204:6499: drag po chen po ra hu la /
NG0204:6500: khrag tu dbab pa'i las 'di yin //
NG0204:6501: dur khrod la sogs gnas dag tu //
NG0204:6502: man+dal chag chag thig gdab bri //
NG0204:6503: dbus su gru gsum brtsegs ma @#//
NG0204:6505: mu khyud zlum po thod phreng can //
NG0204:6506: sgo bzhi rigs dang mthun par bri //
NG0204:6507: sbrul sngon dag gi shun pa la //
NG0204:6508: rdzas kyi phud blugs mi rus gzhug khyil ba'i tshul
NG0204:6509: gyis ga'ur gzhag / gru gsum dbus su bzhag la
NG0204:6510: bsgrub // dkar thab dmar thab sngo thab gsum //
NG0204:6511: gru gsum rgyab ma dag la gzhag / sha rul khrag rul btsos dang rjen //
NG0204:6512: ra mchin sgrub sman gu gul nag / la phug til sgog pha ltar ma lus kyang mos //
NG0204:6513: snel gri'i thod par blugs la gzhag / dkar gsum klu sman mngar gsum dang *//
NG0204:6514: gu gul dkar po 'bras chan rnams //
NG0204:6515: ma ltar mos pas 'khar gzhong blugs //
NG0204:6516: mthun rdzas bsdus la thod par gzhag / tsa ra rog po'i rwa la ni //
NG0204:6517: sngags bris steng du ming byang gdags //
NG0204:6518: lha srin sde brgyad mchod rdzas dgram //
NG0204:6519: thun rdzas thod phreng steng du gzhag / rang nyid gshin rje gshed po ste //
NG0204:6520: yi dam bcas pa rdzogs pa dang *//
NG0204:6521: srog snying 'di ni nus thang brjod //
NG0204:6522: om bi sha la du ru ma shi kha dz+wa la a ta swa ha /
NG0204:6523: stong rdzogs thun la mchod pa bya //
NG0204:6524: hum 'jigs byed chen po ra hu la //
NG0204:6525: sku mdog dud kha mig gis khengs //
NG0204:6526: gshin rje gshed po'i zhabs drung du //
NG0204:6527: rgyal ba'i bstan bsrung khas blangs pa //
NG0204:6529: dam rdzas gtor ma 'di longs la //
NG0204:6530: dam nyams srog rtsa gcad pa dang *//
NG0204:6531: yul du lo nad ser ba phob //
NG0204:6532: hab pa sha mi ki du ru ma shi ki dz+wa la ti a tsi ti swa ha //
NG0204:6533: dus tshod brgyad la gtor ma sbyin //
NG0204:6534: bsnyen cing bsgrub pa'i mtshan ma rnams //
NG0204:6535: gzhung mthun nyams su lon pa dang *//
NG0204:6536: drag po thun gyi rdzas kyang blang *//
NG0204:6538: om mu ka ye ka pa ye a pa ye hrihsh+t+r-ihbi kri na te yul 'di'i lo thog la /
NG0204:6539: tsa pa tri ra hu la ma ha kro d+ha ka pa ta /
NG0204:6540: shar shar ro sha la te hum phat /
NG0204:6541: thig nig gcig med gnyis trag / brgyad bcad dud phrom gnam mthongs phye /
NG0204:6544: rkyang rje rkyang mo tsu ru tsu ru hum phat /
NG0204:6545: stong ngam khri thon rdzas kyis brab //
NG0204:6546: de nas lha srin sprul pa brgyad //
NG0204:6547: sngags kyis gang gi mchan du brab //
NG0204:6550: de ni ma mo'i drag sngags so //
NG0204:6551: om a sa le ma b+h+yo /
NG0204:6552: ru lu ru lu ma ma trag rak+sha hril hril shar b+h+yo /
NG0204:6553: dgra bla'i rgyal mo'i drag sngags so //
NG0204:6554: om pa sha mi ki ra hu la hum /
NG0204:6556: de ni bdud kyi drag sngags so //
NG0204:6557: om ser khrag la mu sha gtub swa ha /
NG0204:6558: de ni srin po'i drag sngags so //
NG0204:6559: om ram tram thum shag ril ram shar b+h+yo /
NG0204:6560: de ni dmu'i drag sngags so //
NG0204:6561: om ya ma ra dza ra ma hril shar ram ram /
NG0204:6563: ni gshin rje'i drag sngags so //
NG0204:6564: om na ga hril se na shag sad dun sa ma ya hril b+h+yo /
NG0204:6565: de ni klu btsan gyi drag sngags so //
NG0204:6566: ya ma snying ya ma khrag / ra hu la
NG0204:6567: hril hril shag shag sen sen ya ya b+h+yo b+h+yo
NG0204:6569: de ni bgegs kyi drag sngags so //
NG0204:6570: zla gcig dus brgyad phyogs nas brdeg / ling+ga bsnur
NG0204:6571: zhing thun rdzas brdeg / gtum chen bstod la gza'
NG0204:6572: mchog rbad // bla phur ling+ga dag la brdeg / tshes grangs thems nas grub rtags 'byung *//
NG0204:6573: rdzas dang thun zor sngags dang ming *//
NG0204:6574: dbus kyi rabs chad thod par blugs //
NG0204:6575: sa gzer yul dbus la sogs su //
NG0204:6576: skya rengs gzer du btab la gzhag / de nas thun gyi zor bya ste //
NG0204:6577: dam rdzas man+dal gong bzhin bya //
NG0204:6578: dam sri yul gyi chu sogs bsags //
NG0204:6579: lha bsnyen bsgrub sngags phyed du ste //
NG0204:6580: phyed ni man chad sngags 'di bzlas //
NG0204:6581: om mu ka ye ka ba ye a pa ye
NG0204:6582: hrihsh+t+r-ihbi kri na te yul 'di'i lo thog la bdud
NG0204:6587: dz+wa la ti ra hu la /
NG0204:6589: shar shar ta phob hum phat /
NG0204:6591: ag ne rag mo ko ra te swa ha /
NG0204:6592: rkyang rje rkyang mo tsu ru tsu ru hum phat /
NG0204:6593: ho ho phrom mu+u ra mu+u ra sha ru ru phrom /
NG0204:6594: gang gi thig nig btags nas kyang *//
NG0204:6595: de la sham bu 'di yang gdags /
NG0204:6600: dgra bo'i lo thog snar mo la ma ra ya hum phat /
NG0204:6601: snying po sngags kyi bar bar du //
NG0204:6602: mchod cing gtor ma dbul bar bya //
NG0204:6603: rab bsgral thabs kyis thugs dam bskang *//
NG0204:6604: thon nas gnam gzer ri la bya //
NG0204:6605: dkar thab dmar thab sngo thab gsum //
NG0204:6606: gcig tu dril la bzhi ru bya //
NG0204:6607: dmar ring zor ni phyogs su 'phangs //
NG0204:6608: gong gi sngags bzlas mdzub ris bya //
NG0204:6610: yang na chu skyes rdzogs pa la //
NG0204:6611: khyab 'jug gtor ma rtag tu gtang *//
NG0204:6612: ba phur btab la gsad las bya //
NG0204:6613: bar bar lha lnga dbye bar bya //
NG0204:6614: de ltar byas na rab 'bring gi / gnam lcags lce dang dmu rdo dang *//
NG0204:6615: chu 'khyags khrag tu dbab par bya //
NG0204:6616: de la 'di'i las ni dus gang yang rung bar yang */
NG0204:6617: khrag dang gu gul dang lcags zangs kyi phye ma
NG0204:6618: rnams la sngags la yul gang yang rung ba de'i
NG0204:6619: lha rten nam chu mig tu sbas na /
NG0204:6620: yul de rlung gis khyer te 'gro bar 'gyur ro //
NG0204:6621: yang rdzas de rnams la bzlas te ri lu byas nas dgra'i khang thog tu bskyur na /
NG0204:6623: yang de rnams la brjod nas chu mig kha byang du bltas par sbas nas gang ltar drangs pas /
NG0204:6626: dang 'khar ba chags pa la bzlas nas khyab 'jug
NG0204:6627: rgyu ba'i dus su brag kha byang du bltas par
NG0204:6628: sbas na / thog drag po 'bebs par 'gyur ro //
NG0204:6630: 'brug gi rus pa dang chu srin gyi sder mo
NG0204:6631: la bzlas nas 'og tu sbas nas phyogs su gtor
NG0204:6632: na / ser ba drag tu 'bebs par 'gyur ro //
NG0204:6634: khyi nag po'i mche ba la sngags nas dgra phyogs su gtor na skrang nad du 'gyur /
NG0204:6635: de la sogs te las thams cad 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NG0204:6637: shwa bzlog pa yang de dang 'dra ste /
NG0204:6638: nyung dkar la sngags nas gtor na bzlog par 'gyur /
NG0204:6639: mang ga ya ti ma ga ti'i bye ma yang
NG0204:6640: la brjod nas gtor na thog bzlog par 'gyur ro
NG0204:6641: // gshin rje zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:6642: chu 'khyags drag tu dbab pa gza'i drag sngags gsang
NG0204:6643: bsgrub kyi skabs te le'u nga drug pa'o // //
NG0204:6644: yang de nas 'jigs byed kyi rgyal po khrag 'thung
NG0204:6645: chen po ya man+ta ka la ngan sngags kyi bdag
NG0204:6646: mo bzhis phyi nang gsang ba gsum gyi mchod pas
NG0204:6647: mchod de / bskor ba lan du mas bskor te /
NG0204:6650: bdag cag rnams kyis khas blangs pa'i //
NG0204:6651: g.yal thog nag po'i las 'di dag / snying po'i mchog tu gyur pa dang *//
NG0204:6652: yang zhun lta bur dril ba'i don //
NG0204:6653: dpa' bo lha rjes bshad du gsol //
NG0204:6655: de nas 'jigs byed chen pos 'di skad ces bka' stsal to //
NG0204:6656: nyon cig rdo rje 'dzin pa dang *//
NG0204:6658: dkon mchog rgyal mtshan ltar byed cing *//
NG0204:6659: rnal 'byor can la phan bya'i phyir //
NG0204:6661: drag po sngags kyi rim pa 'di //

NG0204:7006: dbus su lha chen ma ha de ba yang *//
NG0204:7007: sku mdog nag po spyan gsum mche ba can //
NG0204:7008: rtse gsum 'bar ba khyung gi rgyal mtshan g.yas //
NG0204:7009: zhags pa be con rdo rje g.yon pa na //
NG0204:7010: smin mtshams glog 'gyu bskal pa'i thog 'bebs bsgom //
NG0204:7011: 'khor gyi lha yang rta zhon thogs 'bebs pa'o //
NG0204:7012: de bzhin ting nge 'dzin gyis gsal bsgom la //
NG0204:7013: gshin rje gshed pos lus bsrung dbang du bsdu //
NG0204:7015: las rnams rim gyis bgrod pa'i yang rtse nas //
NG0204:7016: smon lam dbang gis bstan pa 'phel mdzad cing *//
NG0204:7017: ma ha de ba lha chen dbang phyug gtso //
NG0204:7018: bstan pa bshigs pa'i dgra rnams bsgral ba dang *//
NG0204:7019: sangs rgyas bstan bsrung dkon mchog bstod pa'i phyir //
NG0204:7020: 'khor bcas ma lus gshegs su gsol //
NG0204:7021: om pra ma na rag sha e h+ya hi dzah
NG0204:7022: hum bam hoh dga' zhing gus pa'i thal sbyar pus
NG0204:7023: btsugs nas // lha mchog khyed kyi yon tan rab brjod cing *//
NG0204:7024: tsam pa ka dang pad+mas rab gtor nas //
NG0204:7025: deng 'dir bstod de khyed la phyag 'tshal lo /
NG0204:7026: khyed kyi thugs ni nam mkha'i dkyil 'dra zhing *//
NG0204:7027: 'od zer cha las 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NG0204:7028: thogs med mkha' lding ngang pa'i gdan stengs su //
NG0204:7029: brtan par bzhugs nas bdag la dngos grub gsol //
NG0204:7030: 'khor gyi lha chen mi bzad thog 'bebs bzhi //
NG0204:7031: shugs kyi thogs med rta mchog gdan la bzhugs //
NG0204:7032: ma ha de wa pra man tsar zhi sa ma ya tish+tha lhan //
NG0204:7033: lha yul gtsang ma dag la rab bshams te //
NG0204:7034: bram ze mtshan ldan chags pas @#//
NG0204:7036: 'bras dang ku sha bcas pa'i yon chab dang *//
NG0204:7037: ga bur gur gum gla rtsi ce pog sogs //
NG0204:7038: til mar bsung can rab gsal mar me'i mchog / du ru ka la sogs pa dri yi chu //
NG0204:7039: lag pan mar dang bcas pa'i bu ram bshos //
NG0204:7040: dung dang bye ru zangs dang kra shel dang *//
NG0204:7041: rnga ting rdza rnga mun dza ti mi li //
NG0204:7042: cha lang pi wang tam bu rgyud gcig pa //
NG0204:7043: glu gar rtsed 'jo rol mo dag la sogs //
NG0204:7044: bde ba'i yo byad thams cad ma lus kun //
NG0204:7045: mchod par 'bul lo thugs rjes bzhes su gsol /
NG0204:7046: om sarba pu dza push+pe d+hu?pe a lo ke gan+d+he
NG0204:7047: ba lim pu dza hoh sku mdog nag po spyan
NG0204:7049: drang srong cha lugs pad+ma'i phreng bas brgyan //
NG0204:7050: zhal bzhi gling bzhi yongs la khyab par gzigs //
NG0204:7051: snyan pa'i dril sgra gsung gi gdangs skad can //
NG0204:7052: dbang phyug chen po khyed la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0204:7053: 'khor gyi lha yi blon po bzhi //
NG0204:7054: rta la zhon nas ral gri bskor //
NG0204:7055: thog ser 'bebs pa'i las la brtson /
NG0204:7056: khyod la bdag cag bstod phyag 'tshal //
NG0204:7057: sngags 'dis lha rnams rab tu bsnyen //
NG0204:7058: om ma ha de wa ti dza ti dza lam
NG0204:7059: pra ma na pra ma na rak+sha kang kang la
NG0204:7060: yang hum / de ba ra tsa dza ma ha
NG0204:7061: ni dgra bo che ge mo ni thum thum rbad
NG0204:7062: yang hum / // shag len se na se na
NG0204:7063: yang */ pa na dzah dzahhum hum / de skad
NG0204:7065: rang gis ma nyes dpang yang gzug / nyes byas bris sku'i mdun du bshags //
NG0204:7067: gshed po bstod la lha rnams bskul //
NG0204:7068: g.yas nas bskor zhing thugs dam bskul //
NG0204:7069: 'dod khams nyi shu'i yang rtse nas //
NG0204:7070: gzugs khams lha yi dga' tshal nas //
NG0204:7071: pho brang bde ba'i gzhal yas nas //
NG0204:7072: chos kyi rgyal mtshan dbang bskur ba'i //
NG0204:7073: lha chen dbang phyug chen po ni //
NG0204:7074: sku ni dmar ser 'bar ba la //
NG0204:7075: tshad med dbu bzhi gling bzhi 'joms //
NG0204:7076: g.yas kyi pad+ma skyon dang bral //
NG0204:7077: tha mas bgrang phreng rigs sngags spel //
NG0204:7079: tha ma blug rlung yang snod dgra bgegs sbyong *//
NG0204:7080: ngang pas bsam par yud kyis phyin //
NG0204:7081: pad+ma ser pos brgyan byas nas //
NG0204:7082: ras kyi kha tshar mgul rgyan can //
NG0204:7083: thugs dam drag tu bskul byas nas //
NG0204:7084: log pa'i dgra bgegs 'joms pa'i tshe //
NG0204:7085: sku ni sngo nag chen po la //
NG0204:7086: zhal gyi mche ba gdangs pa yis //
NG0204:7087: dgra bo bdun rgyud rtsad nas gcod //
NG0204:7089: thal mo brdab pas thog chen 'bebs //
NG0204:7090: mdzub mo bskul bas gling bzhi 'khrugs //
NG0204:7091: ljags brkyang srid pa g.yo bar mdzad //
NG0204:7092: dkon mchog gsum gyi sku dgra 'di //
NG0204:7094: bas lnga phung shig / tshe srog chod la bdun rgyud chod //
NG0204:7095: 'khor gyi blon bzhi las la bskul /
NG0204:7096: bar snang thog chen 'brul du chug / dbang po rnam lnga kha long kha //
NG0204:7097: bu smad 'khor g.yog nor phyugs la //
NG0204:7098: gser thog lcags thog tsa la la //
NG0204:7100: zangs thog 'khar thog rams se ram //
NG0204:7101: me 'od glog dmar khyugs se khyug / 'khor rnams shugs chen rta zhon cing *//
NG0204:7102: ral gri me 'od klad la bskor //
NG0204:7103: ki kang gshed bzhi'i las la 'gyed //
NG0204:7105: thog chen sna tshogs skar ltar 'khrugs //
NG0204:7106: nyams pa'i dgra la thog mda' ya //
NG0204:7107: skad cig tsam la phung bar gyis //
NG0204:7108: zhes rta snying bstab cing rak+ta sbreng *//
NG0204:7109: rtags su 'brug dang ser ba dang *//
NG0204:7110: glog dang thog dang shwa bud 'ong *//
NG0204:7111: grub pa'i rtags byung thog gta' gzhug / mkhar rmang lha rten chu mig gam //
NG0204:7113: lhag par dgra yi gro ga 'am //
NG0204:7114: nyal ba'i sngas sam stan 'og tu //
NG0204:7115: 'khor lo bcas pa'i thod pa sba //
NG0204:7116: drag sngags 'di bzlas thod par gsib //
NG0204:7117: om sa ma dur bu rak+sha pra ma na /
NG0204:7118: ma ha de wa dgra yi yul khams su /
NG0204:7119: ro kha du kha la hum phra ba swa ha /
NG0204:7120: zhes pa ni thod pa'i nang du bzlas /
NG0204:7121: gtor ma gtong zhing smon lam gdab //
NG0204:7122: bris sku dag la rten bcas la //
NG0204:7123: dra phying man+dal dag la dril //
NG0204:7124: rtag tu lha rnams mchod gyur na //
NG0204:7126: gshin rje zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:7127: 'jig rten du thog dbab pa lha'i zla gsang skabs te le'u nga dgu pa'o ///
NG0204:7128: / de nas yang bcom ldan 'das 'jigs byed chen
NG0204:7129: po gshin rje gshed pos 'gal byed cham la dbab
NG0204:7130: pa'i slad du / thog 'bebs lha yi nang bsgrub gsungs //
NG0204:7131: srid par ma srid mgar gyis ma brdungs mtshon //
NG0204:7132: ye srid byang chub sems kyi dpal ngar can //
NG0204:7133: rlung gis ma blud gshags pa'i ngar //
NG0204:7134: ye blud chen po'i mtshon dbal ngar can des //
NG0204:7135: 'byung ba gzhan gyis mi brdzi mi tshugs shing *//
NG0204:7136: nyid kyis gang la thogs chag med par 'joms //
NG0204:7137: de nyid bsgrub phyir dur khrod la sogs su //
NG0204:7139: dbus su gru gsum e brtsigs te //
NG0204:7140: 'khor lo bzhi dang rol mtsho bdun //
NG0204:7141: gser ri'i dbus su ya man+ta ka ste //
NG0204:7142: steng du lha chen dbang phyug yab yum dgod par bya //
NG0204:7143: 'khor lo bzhi la lha yi blon po bzhi /
NG0204:7144: khrag zhag mar khu chang dang sprang rtsi 'o ma dang *//
NG0204:7145: rgya mtsho'i chu la sogs pa'i mtsho bdun no //
NG0204:7146: lha chen lnga la phur pa lnga dgod de //
NG0204:7147: dngul gyi phur la sor brgyad shar du dgod //
NG0204:7149: yi blon por mnga' yang gsol //
NG0204:7150: gser gyi phur pa lho yi rtsibs la dgod //
NG0204:7151: gshin rje lha yi blon por mnga' yang gsol //
NG0204:7152: zangs kyi phur pa nub kyi rtsibs la dgod //
NG0204:7153: klu dbang lha yi blon por mnga' yang gsol //
NG0204:7154: lcags kyi phur pa byang gi rtsibs la dgod //
NG0204:7155: gnod sbyin lha yi blon por mnga' yang gsol //
NG0204:7156: 'khar ba'i phur pa dbus kyi e la dgod //
NG0204:7157: dbang phyug chen po ma ha de bar mnga' yang gsol //
NG0204:7158: gro ga shing shun ras sam dar dkar la //
NG0204:7159: lha rnams rang rang rtsa ba'i snying po dang *//
NG0204:7160: dbab pa'i sngags dang dmigs pa'i yul ming bri //
NG0204:7161: sngon dmar skud pas phur pa'i mgul du gdags //
NG0204:7162: rabs chad nag po'i thod pa kha sbyar la //
NG0204:7163: thod pa'i phyi nang med par khrag gis byug / steng gi thod pa yab tu mnga' yang gsol //
NG0204:7164: 'og gi thod pa yum du mnga' yang gsol //
NG0204:7165: thod pa steng mar yab kyi sku yang bri //
NG0204:7166: thod pa 'og mar yum gyi sku yang bri //
NG0204:7167: thod pa'i rtsibs rim dmigs pa'i ming rus bri //
NG0204:7168: dpral bar rus bri kha ru ming yang bri //
NG0204:7169: snying gar nr-i bri 'doms su bla dag bri //
NG0204:7170: de yi tha mar ltau sbyar dza yis bskor //
NG0204:7171: gro ga shing shun zhing gi pags pa la //
NG0204:7172: dgra bo'i gzugs bris dbang phyug yum la glan //
NG0204:7173: 'khar ba'i phur pa thod pa'i nang du gzhag / gro ga shog shog shing gi lo ma la //
NG0204:7174: lha chen tshogs bdag dbang phyug chen po khyod /
NG0204:7175: khyod kyi btsun mo ma ra ya 'dis sbyar //
NG0204:7176: 'khor gyi lha rnams myur du bskul mdzod la //
NG0204:7177: 'di la drag po'i thog chen phob ces bri //
NG0204:7178: phur pa de yi mgul du gdags par bya'o //
NG0204:7179: thod pa'i nang du dme khrag skam po dang *//
NG0204:7180: gser phye zangs phye lcags phye 'khar phye dang *//
NG0204:7181: dngul dang thog lcags thog grir shi ba yi //
NG0204:7182: snying dang rus pa sha yang stsal //
NG0204:7183: thod pa kha sbyar mi yi rgyu mas bcings //
NG0204:7184: sgyed gsum kha la gru gsum steng du gzhag / chu skyes me tog sna tshogs dang *//
NG0204:7185: rin chen sna lnga sman rnams dang *//
NG0204:7186: 'dod pa'i longs spyod zas rnams dang *//
NG0204:7187: rgun chang sbrang dang 'bras chang dang *//
NG0204:7188: 'bru chang dang ni a su sha / de dag mchod pa'i rdzas su dgram //
NG0204:7189: sna tshogs snying dang khrag tu sbyar //
NG0204:7190: bu ram 'bras kyi gtor ma bzhi //
NG0204:7191: lha yi blon po bzhi la dgod //
NG0204:7193: gzugs ming byas pa mdun du gzhag / sngags kyis brab cing gsang las bya //
NG0204:7194: ting 'dzin gzhal yas gdan dang bcas pa bskyed //
NG0204:7195: ya man+ta ka gsal bar bsgom //
NG0204:7196: gdan du yi dwags gding bar bya //
NG0204:7197: dbang phyug chen po gsal bsgoms te //
NG0204:7198: 'khor gyi lha bzhis bskor bar bsam //
NG0204:7201: zhes brjod dbang phyug chen po yang *//
NG0204:7202: nag po chen po mche ba rab tu gtsigs //
NG0204:7203: phyag mtshan rtse gsum khyung gi rgyal mtshan g.yas //
NG0204:7204: zhags pas 'dren tshun be con rdeg tshul g.yon //
NG0204:7205: chibs su 'brug rta sngon po chibs //
NG0204:7206: gser gyi ral gri 'bar ba klad la bskor //
NG0204:7207: gnam lcags 'bar ba'i shang lang glo la btags //
NG0204:7208: de 'dra rab tu gsal bsgom bya //
NG0204:7209: shar phyogs lha yi phyag na dngul gyi gzhu bdungs shing *//
NG0204:7210: dngul gyi mda' ltong dngul gyi 'khor lo bskor //
NG0204:7211: 'brug rta zhon nas ki kang 'phral la 'jug / dngul gyi thog 'bebs ser ba'i skyin 'dang gtong *//
NG0204:7212: lho nas gser gyi thog chen gong bzhin 'bebs //
NG0204:7213: nub nas zangs thog byang nas lcags thog 'bebs //
NG0204:7214: de 'dra gang la bsgoms la yengs par mi bya'o //
NG0204:7216: rnam snang mdzad nyid mi g.yo gtsug tor brtan //
NG0204:7217: byang chub chen po mchog gi phyag rgya ni //
NG0204:7218: bdud 'dul chen po'i sku ru sprul pa'i rgya //
NG0204:7219: byang shar mtshams nas shin tu sku bde bstan //
NG0204:7220: me lce bar snang sprin gtibs dkyil 'khor nas //
NG0204:7221: sku stod sngo nag mi bzad 'bar ba'i 'od phung can //
NG0204:7222: shin tu khro brjid dbang phyug gtum bag che //
NG0204:7223: thugs rjes sprin ltar gtibs shing nam mkha' gang bar khyab //
NG0204:7224: gzir gnon stabs kyis dregs pa gzir zhing gnon //
NG0204:7225: bdud po nag po spyan gsum mche ba can //
NG0204:7226: bstan pa 'jig pa'i srog la spyan 'dren na //
NG0204:7227: dbang phyug lha chen 'khor bcas gshegs su gsol //
NG0204:7228: dbang phyug chen po gnas nas spyod tsam na //
NG0204:7229: rtse gsum 'bar ba khyung gi rgyal mtshan phyar te gshegs //
NG0204:7230: zhags pas 'dren cing be con snying la brdeg / nag po spyan gsum sdang mig bzlog pa'i bdud //
NG0204:7231: dbu skra 'bar ba phrog gzer ral pa can //
NG0204:7232: sku lus mon pa spyan gsum ser ba 'dril //
NG0204:7233: rno dbal mche ba zla tshes gyen du 'khyil //
NG0204:7234: spyan mig bzlog pas skyi 'dang rma 'dang 'bebs //
NG0204:7235: shangs nas rlung ni 'thor 'bud bu yug 'khrugs //
NG0204:7236: mdung dang gri rkang sku yi rten du bcas //
NG0204:7237: spyan mig mi mthun las kyi zla ba 'dril ba ltar //
NG0204:7238: 'od zer me ltar 'bar zhing gshegs su gsol //
NG0204:7239: e h+ye ma ha ka la tri dza ka ru ni ka dr-i sh+ya ho /
NG0204:7242: lha chen dbang phyug 'khor ba'i g.yul bzlog nga *//
NG0204:7243: sprul pa'i rlabs chen lha yi dmag dpung sdud //
NG0204:7244: dbang phyug legs ldan nag po'i 'khor gyis bskor //
NG0204:7245: dbang phyug lha chen sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0204:7246: dbang phyug bsod nams gzi byin 'phags la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0204:7247: ston pas lung bstan 'phags la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0204:7250: ma rig sgrib pa ma lus sel mdzad pa'i //
NG0204:7251: 'khor bcas lha yi tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0204:7252: me tog phreng la sogs pa dang *//
NG0204:7253: rin chen dbyig dang sgog btsong dang *//
NG0204:7254: la phug la sogs kun dang ni //
NG0204:7255: 'bras bu yid bzhin sna tshogs zas //
NG0204:7256: phyogs bcu chu skyes dang ni longs spyod rgyan //
NG0204:7257: ris su ma chad mchod pa'i longs spyod dbul //
NG0204:7258: dkyil 'khor mdzes pa'i rgyan gyis brgyan //
NG0204:7259: zhal zas bdud rtsi dza gad sman gyis mchod //
NG0204:7260: e h+ye hi ma ha ka ru ni ba ti ma ha rak+sha du pa kha kha kha hi /
NG0204:7262: ma ha be ta li kha kha kha hi /
NG0204:7264: dbang phyug chen po 'khor bcas la //
NG0204:7265: mchod sprin la sogs sna tshogs dang *//
NG0204:7266: rdzas dang yo byad dpag mi lang *//
NG0204:7267: bla med dad pas mchod 'bul bstod //
NG0204:7269: gdug pa ril mid mdzad pa'i khro gnyer can //
NG0204:7270: dug gsum rtsad gcod mche ba gtsigs pa po //
NG0204:7271: ye shes spyan gsum nyi zla'i ga'u la //
NG0204:7272: ston pa'i bka' brgyud bla med lung bstan dpal //
NG0204:7273: dam tshig chos kyi 'khor lo rnam snang mdzad //
NG0204:7274: bla re cod pan brjid pas bcings pa na //
NG0204:7275: nges par ston pa bcu yi bdag pos 'phags //
NG0204:7276: rtag tu dur khrod 'bar ba'i gnas na bzhugs //
NG0204:7277: dur khrod gnas na ma mo'i tshogs kyis bskor //
NG0204:7278: nad gtong shri'i tshogs rnams kun mchod nas //
NG0204:7279: bstan pa bshigs pa'i mdangs 'phrog thal ba'i rdul du
NG0204:7280: rlog / stobs chen glang po'i pags pa gos su
NG0204:7281: gyon // lha klu gnyan gyi grong khyer thams cad du //
NG0204:7282: lha chen bdud dpung che btsan gsum pa nas //
NG0204:7283: log 'dren dgra bgegs gzir gdul gnon pa'o //
NG0204:7284: dpa' bo chen po stag gi pags pas mtshan //
NG0204:7285: 'khor du lha yi blon po bzhi yis bskor //
NG0204:7286: phyogs rnams phyogs cha kun tu rnam grangs la //
NG0204:7287: smon lam khyad par mang po'i mthus sbyangs la //
NG0204:7288: sgyu ma lta bur rnam par thar pas rol //
NG0204:7289: phan mdzad dmag dpon khyod la yang *//
NG0204:7290: sdug bsngal tsha bas gdungs pa'i sems can la //
NG0204:7291: drag po'i thog chen lu gu rgyud du 'bebs //
NG0204:7292: lha chen dbang phyug khyod la bdag bdud skyabs su mchi //
NG0204:7293: sngags 'dis lha rnams srog kyang bzung *//
NG0204:7294: om ma ha de ba ka la ka sti dza
NG0204:7295: re sde ri i na hri se ba na dza
NG0204:7296: na ga ru ru te pe ka na phu pe
NG0204:7297: he serbe da de bu se na de ba te
NG0204:7299: khri tsho re zhing bskul bskyed bstod //
NG0204:7300: 'od dang sgra dang dri zhim dang *//
NG0204:7301: 'brug dang glog dang thog dang shwa //
NG0204:7302: de rnams 'grub pa'i rtags su ste //
NG0204:7303: dbang du bsdu zhing phrin las bcol //
NG0204:7307: chibs su 'brug rta sngon po chibs //
NG0204:7308: rol du khyung dang seng ge khrid /
NG0204:7309: kha rlangs sprin dang na bun gtibs //
NG0204:7311: lcags kyi ser chen ljibs se ljib //
NG0204:7312: shel gyi khu 'phang ri li li //
NG0204:7313: gser thog lcags thog chems se chem //
NG0204:7314: gnam lcags ral gri klad la bskor //
NG0204:7315: gser gyi shang lang glog chen 'khyug / 'khor gyi lha chen thog 'bebs te //
NG0204:7316: shar phyogs dri za'i zhing khams nas //
NG0204:7317: dri za lha yi blon po yang *//
NG0204:7318: dngul gyi gzhu bdungs mda' ltong sta //
NG0204:7319: lag na dngul gyi thog chen 'bebs //
NG0204:7320: dngul gyi thog chen 'u ru ru //
NG0204:7321: ki kang pho mo khral la 'dzud //
NG0204:7323: de bzhin phyogs kyi blon bzhi bskul //
NG0204:7324: thog gi dbab sngags thod par bstim //
NG0204:7325: 'ur chom rbad nal ram shar shar b+h+yo dza rak+sha tsit+ta ma ra ya snying ling rbud /
NG0204:7326: tsit+ta bam ril kha rag tshal pa bam /
NG0204:7327: rak+sha yak+sha tsit+ta rbad su dza /
NG0204:7330: rag sha nag po srog la chums chums bob bob nal shig ma ra ya /
NG0204:7331: de ni lcags thog dbab pa'o //
NG0204:7332: 'ur chom rbad nal ram ram shad shad de ba srog la chum chum /
NG0204:7333: rbad rbad 'ur rbad nal shig ma ra ya /
NG0204:7334: de ni gser thog dbab pa'o //
NG0204:7335: 'ur 'ur chom chom shig shig ma ra ya ril ril kha la rbad pu dza /
NG0204:7336: ma ha ra dza kha la rak+sha tsig tsig tsig tsig hril hril bob ya /
NG0204:7337: de ni zangs thod dbab pa'o //
NG0204:7338: de bzhin thod pa kha sbyar te //
