NG0204:7683: ma las lha mo nyid kyis skur gyur te //
NG0204:7684: sku mdog nag mo shin tu gtum pa la //
NG0204:7685: shin tu sgeg pa zhal gcig phyag bzhi pa //
NG0204:7686: ral gri b+han+da dmar 'khyil g.yas rim bzhin /
NG0204:7687: shak+ti tri shul mgul nas dar dpyangs g.yon //
NG0204:7688: ral gcig sbreng ba'i lan bu g.yon du 'khyil //
NG0204:7689: skra sked sbrul la thod pa'i phreng thod can //
NG0204:7690: rna ltag me tog dar nag cod pan 'phur //
NG0204:7691: snyan g.yas sbrul gyi gdengs ka yi //
NG0204:7692: mgul nas sil snyan 'khrol ba la //
NG0204:7693: snyan cha g.yon pa seng ge 'phyo //
NG0204:7694: thod pa skam rlon do shal byas //
NG0204:7695: bong bu gwa pa'i chib la zhon //
NG0204:7696: gzhan yang che ba'i rgyan dang gdug pa'i rgyan //
NG0204:7697: stong gis brgyan pa gsal bar bsgom //
NG0204:7698: ting 'dzin sems dpa'i sku las 'od zer ni //
NG0204:7699: lcags kyu 'bar ba'i 'od zer phar 'phros te //
NG0204:7700: bdag nyid chen mo'i srog nas rab bskul te //
NG0204:7701: srid pa'i ma mos stong gsum khengs par byas //
NG0204:7702: gshin rje'i tshogs kyang de bzhin te //
NG0204:7703: srog la rngam pa kun gyis bskor bar bsam //
NG0204:7704: de lta bu ni yang nas yang du ste //
NG0204:7705: de ltar thib thib yod snyam cho 'phrul 'byung *//
NG0204:7706: de lta bu yi bar du bsgom par bya //
NG0204:7707: yengs par gyur na cis kyang mi 'grub bo //
NG0204:7708: gtso mo la sogs srid pa'i ma mo yis //
NG0204:7709: gang la bya ba'i snying nas rab bzung ste //
NG0204:7710: skra grol mig rtsa rig rig 'o dod tse re re //
NG0204:7711: gan bub rdul zhing kha nas khrag skyugs 'byung *//
NG0204:7712: ci mdzad 'on tang zer zhing dbugs dang bral la khad //
NG0204:7713: thun khung nang du rab tu 'jug par bsam //
NG0204:7714: de ltar bsgom la gshed pos dbang du bsdu //
NG0204:7715: mnyes pa'i tshul gyis bstod pa 'di skad dbul //
NG0204:7716: dpal ldan nag mo mi pham srid gsum mgon //
NG0204:7717: bdag don rnam thar gsum la thugs gzhol yang *//
NG0204:7718: snying rje'i dbang gis rjes la thob @#//
NG0204:7720: shes rab sna tshogs dag gis 'gro don mdzad //
NG0204:7721: lha mo sku mdog nag mo char sprin mdog / mtshan mo nag mo shin tu gtum pa'i sku //
NG0204:7722: shin tu sgaig cing keng rus lus 'chang ma //
NG0204:7723: zhal gcig phyag bzhi zhabs gnyis rab tu brjid //
NG0204:7724: ral pa gcig sbreng lan bu g.yon du 'khyil //
NG0204:7725: skra sked sbrul la thod pa'i phreng thod can //
NG0204:7726: rna ltag me tog dar nag cod pan 'phur /
NG0204:7727: khrag gi chang gis ra ro spyan gsum dmar //
NG0204:7728: mi ro rengs pa khar bcug mche ba bzhi //
NG0204:7729: rnam par gtsigs nas shin tu khrag la dgyes //
NG0204:7730: snyan g.yas sbrul gyi mgul nas dril gsil zhing *//
NG0204:7731: gdug pa btul nas tshangs pa'i sgra sgrogs ma //
NG0204:7732: snyan cha g.yon pa seng ge ral pa dmar //
NG0204:7733: dpa' mo seng ge sgra sgrogs ma //
NG0204:7734: phyag bzhi g.yas kyi dang po ral gri bsnams //
NG0204:7735: 'og ma thod pa b+han+da dmar bskyil 'dzin //
NG0204:7736: g.yon gyi dang po mtshon cha shak+ti bsnams //
NG0204:7737: 'og ma tri shul mgul na dar nag 'phyangs //
NG0204:7738: shag ti ral gri mtshon chas bcad pa yi //
NG0204:7739: lha ma yin la sogs pa'i thod pas do shal byas //
NG0204:7740: glang po che yi stod g.yogs gos su mdzes //
NG0204:7741: smad ni ban [\[]ba [\]]glang ko bas dkris pa la //
NG0204:7742: phyed ni re lde sngon po'i sham bu can //
NG0204:7743: klu yi dbang po bzhi yis sked bcings can //
NG0204:7744: zhabs gnyis lcags sgrog dag gis mdzes par brgyan /
NG0204:7745: khrag zhags thig le mang pos tshom bur bris //
NG0204:7746: bong gwa zhon nas mtshan mo dur khrod rgyu //
NG0204:7747: bong bu'i rmig pa glog gi shugs 'chang ma /
NG0204:7748: khams gsum skad cig tsam gyis 'khor bar byed //
NG0204:7749: skad ni dung dang 'brug gi sgra sgrogs shing *//
NG0204:7750: ma mo mkha' 'gro sha za dbang du sdud //
NG0204:7751: lho phyogs gshin rje'i pho brang rtag tu gnas //
NG0204:7752: dam pa'i sa nas gzugs sku gnyis gzigs ma //
NG0204:7753: ting 'dzin dbang thob gzugs khams gnas su byon //
NG0204:7754: tshangs pa'i rgyal po sogs kyis phyag byas ma //
NG0204:7755: gzhan 'phrul dbang byed ya thar byon pa'i tshe //
NG0204:7756: dbang phyug chen po'i sku+u la dgyes 'khril ba //
NG0204:7757: sum cu rtsa gsum tshar bzhi byon pa'i tshe //
NG0204:7758: lha rnams dbugs phyung brgya byin phyag byas ma //
NG0204:7759: lha ma yin rnams phung bar byed pa'i tshe //
NG0204:7760: lha min rgyal po kun gyis phyag byas ma //
NG0204:7761: sku mdog ri rab che dang 'gran pa'i tshe //
NG0204:7762: lte ba'i thad ka'i phyogs nas nyi zla 'char //
NG0204:7763: rgyal chen phyogs skyong lha yis phyag byas ma //
NG0204:7764: rgya mtsho'i gting nas me 'bar mtsho skem ma //
NG0204:7765: sa 'og dbang po kun gyis phyag byas ma //
NG0204:7766: lha mo khyod kyi cho 'phrul skur bstan pas //
NG0204:7767: bdud dang gshin rje'i rgyal po 'dar zhing lud //
NG0204:7768: ma mo mkha' 'gro sha za sngangs shing brgyal //
NG0204:7771: nyi zla brtsegs pa'i dkyil 'khor ga bur 'bar //
NG0204:7772: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten drug gi bcud bsdus nas //
NG0204:7773: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor dag la thim mdzad ma / dug gi rlangs pas nag po'i phyogs rnams kyi //
NG0204:7774: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad ni khong nas bslangs //
NG0204:7775: de phyir nad kyi bdag mo dam la 'du //
NG0204:7776: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten bdud rtsi'i bcud bsdus nas //
NG0204:7777: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor dag la thim mdzad ma //
NG0204:7778: bdud rtsi bslangs pas dkar po'i phyogs rnams kyi //
NG0204:7779: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad ni rtsad nas gcod //
NG0204:7780: de phyir bdud rtsi sman gyi rgyal mo dam la 'du //
NG0204:7781: gang zhig khyod la dad na ma bas byams //
NG0204:7782: de phyir ma gcig nad 'joms sman gyi gtso //
NG0204:7783: lha mo khyod la rtag tu bdag gis bstod //
NG0204:7784: rgyal ba shakya thub pa'i spyan snga ru //
NG0204:7785: dus 'dir bdag gis dam bcas ji srid du //
NG0204:7786: dkar po'i phyogs kyi nad dang sdug bsngal sogs //
NG0204:7787: zhi bar byed cing tshe dang longs spyod sdud //
NG0204:7788: nag po'i tshogs ni dgug cing dbang du sdud //
NG0204:7789: smyo 'bog lkugs pa'i las 'di myur du bgyi //
NG0204:7790: bstan pa bsrung phyir myur du grub par bgyi //
NG0204:7791: 'di las 'das na rgyal ba'i bka' bslus pas //
NG0204:7792: dus gsum rgyal ba'i rdo rjes mgo dang snying 'gems
NG0204:7793: shog / de skad rgyal ba'i spyan sngar dam bcas
NG0204:7794: pa'i // dam bcas bzhin du phrin las myur du gyis //
NG0204:7795: rnal 'byor bdag dang bdag gi 'khor rnams la //
NG0204:7796: khyed kyi zhal nas bdud rtsi'i char phob la //
NG0204:7797: nad sogs sdug bsngal tshogs ni zhi bar mdzod //
NG0204:7798: tshe dang bsod nams longs spyod 'phel bar mdzod //
NG0204:7799: zang zing longs spyod 'bru yi phung po dang *//
NG0204:7800: rin chen rkang 'gros phyugs rnams 'phel bar mdzod //
NG0204:7801: bla ma smod cing dkon mchog dbu 'phang smod //
NG0204:7802: bdag la dge ba'i bar chad byed pa'i dgra //
NG0204:7803: khyod kyis khong nas dug gi rlung bus la //
NG0204:7804: 'du ba rnam bzhi'i nad ni 'du ru chug /
NG0204:7805: bag bzhi sa la lhung nas rdebs su chug /
NG0204:7806: don snying rnam lnga khong nas khrag skyugs chug /
NG0204:7807: las ngan 'khor tshogs cho nges brdung du chug /
NG0204:7808: mkha' lding rgyal po'i tshogs kyis ltas ngan phob //
NG0204:7809: dam bcas bzhin du phrin las myur du grub par mdzod //
NG0204:7810: ces bstod cing phrin las bcol gyur na //
NG0204:7812: ma mos srog bsdus te gsad par bya'o //
NG0204:7813: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:7814: yams nad kyi bdag mo ma mo'i zla gsang gi skabs te le'u re gsum pa'o ///
NG0204:7815: / de nas bcom ldan 'das gshin rje gshed pos 'di skad gsungs so //
NG0204:7819: ma mo gsang bsgrub zla gsang gsungs //
NG0204:7820: zla gsang nag po'i rgyud dag la //
NG0204:7821: thabs kyi sbyor ba mang yod kyang *//
NG0204:7822: bsdu na rnam pa bzhi ru 'dus //
NG0204:7823: bla med bsgrub mthu rang byung ste //
NG0204:7824: 'jig rten bsgrub pa don gyi mthu //
NG0204:7825: rten 'brel sgyu ma'i sbyor ba bzhin //
NG0204:7826: rdzas kyi nus pa dag las 'byung *//
NG0204:7827: gdon dang rdzas su bcas pa las //
NG0204:7828: rnam grangs ma nges khyad par mang *//
NG0204:7829: rnam pa gnyis ni gsal bya ste //
NG0204:7830: rdzas dang gdon du bcas pas bstan //
NG0204:7831: myur du gsad pa'i sbyor ba ni //
NG0204:7832: gang yang 'di las yod ma yin //
NG0204:7833: ma mo nag smug dkar mo dang *//
NG0204:7834: dmar mo tshogs kyi nang dag nas //
NG0204:7835: rims nad gtang ba mang yod kyang *//
NG0204:7836: kun gyi phyag brnyan re ma ti //
NG0204:7837: 'di dag bsgrub ste las sbyar na //
NG0204:7840: rgyu gzer dag gis shi ba'i khrag / btsan dug thar nu bsres nas kyang *//
NG0204:7841: bse zho dag dang mar du sbyar //
NG0204:7842: sngags 'dis btab te ltor yang gtang *//
NG0204:7843: ru ru shi tri kri ma du sod srog thum mug sod /
NG0204:7844: ma rag ru rbad ya sod /
NG0204:7845: ni ya ni ya tsa thun sod /
NG0204:7849: ma ma thum thum sod sod /
NG0204:7850: ces 'bum 'bum bzlas te ltor gtang na /
NG0204:7851: rgyu gzer khrag tu bshal te 'chi /
NG0204:7852: de nas yang bse zho dang btsan dug la sngags 'di bzlas /
NG0204:7854: ba ya du du rbad ya /
NG0204:7855: chum chum ni ma tsa rbad ya /
NG0204:7856: shag pa du du ya chems chems rbad ya /
NG0204:7859: ru ru ra pa ni dum ma ti rbad ya /
NG0204:7860: zhes 'bum bzlas te lus la reg pa'i gos la
NG0204:7861: bskus na lhog pa dkar pos 'chi bar 'gyur ro
NG0204:7862: // de nas yang bse zho dang btsan dug dang
NG0204:7863: byang ba tsha tshong dang mdze khrag dang mdze pho'i
NG0204:7864: shu ba kun sbyar la mar dang dri ma bsres
NG0204:7865: // / da du+u ma sha khug du sha ma ma bam gol du /
NG0204:7866: du tri ma ma snying phyung */
NG0204:7867: sa ma ya ma ma srog ched /
NG0204:7868: du shag du ya ma ma ti ru ma ti ya /
NG0204:7869: sha sha ma ma rbad su ya ya /
NG0204:7870: nr-i nr-i b+h+yo b+h+yo sod sod /
NG0204:7871: ma ru ya ma ru ya tshal pa rbad yed yed sha thum sha thum rbad /
NG0204:7872: tsa dur ma ma du rbad /
NG0204:7874: sha sha tsa thum ma ya b+h+yo /
NG0204:7876: sha la reg pa'i gos la bskus na mdze dang phol 'bras kyis 'chi bar 'gyur ro //
NG0204:7877: mdze khrag chang dang sbyar nas ltor btang na snying
NG0204:7878: la babs te rus mdze dang mdze nad 'thor bas
NG0204:7880: de nas yang dug rdzas dang rims khrag sna tshogs
NG0204:7881: sbyar nas gong gi sngags rnams drag tu bzlas te
NG0204:7882: / yul khams kyi lha rten nam /
NG0204:7885: brag klu btsan yod pa'i sar gtor na rims nad
NG0204:7886: sna tshogs na bun bzhin gtibs nas 'ong ba dang
NG0204:7888: ser ba drag tu 'bebs par 'gyur ro //
NG0204:7889: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:7890: nad ngan sna tshogs gtang ba'i skabs te le'u re bzhi pa'o ///
NG0204:7891: / de nas yang bcom ldan 'das gshin rje gshed pos 'gal ba cham la dbab pa'i phyir /
NG0204:7892: smyo 'bog ging gi zla gsang gsungs //
NG0204:7893: dbang dang dam tshig ldan pa yis //
NG0204:7894: bla ma mnyes pa'i rim gro bya //
NG0204:7895: lta ba yangs shing spyod lam goms //
NG0204:7896: slob dpon mnyes pa'i thugs gzung nas //
NG0204:7897: man ngag thugs la phur te bsgrub //
NG0204:7898: ri gsum rtse'am brag dkar ram //
NG0204:7899: lha khang dur khrod spe'u dang *//
NG0204:7900: yang na brag phug shar bltas su //
NG0204:7901: rtsa na brag yod rtsi shing skyes //
NG0204:7902: shar du kha bltas zur gsum 'dra //
NG0204:7903: rgyab ri mchad pa seng ge spungs //
NG0204:7904: de ru gnas btsal sa chog bya //
NG0204:7905: sa bdag lha klu zhi ba'i phyir //
NG0204:7906: gser skyems gtang la bden pa bdar //
NG0204:7907: 'di skad brjod la bsgo bar bya //
NG0204:7909: phyogs 'dir sgrol ba'i ging chen po //
NG0204:7910: srog bdag dkar po snying 'byin zhes //
NG0204:7911: rnal 'byor rnams kyi dgra bla che //
NG0204:7913: deng 'dir sa bdag lha klu rnams //
NG0204:7914: gnas gzhan dag tu 'pho bar gyis //
NG0204:7915: sa gzhi 'di yang bkra shis mdzod //
NG0204:7916: ma nyes dpang gzug yus ka gsol //
NG0204:7917: de nas stegs bu brtsig pa yang *//
NG0204:7918: dra phying ras sam dar bting la //
NG0204:7920: ga bur dza ti pha la dang *//
NG0204:7921: rgya spos la sogs dri spos dgram //
NG0204:7922: yol ba bla re 'phan gdugs bres //
NG0204:7923: srog bdag dkar po snying 'byin ni //
NG0204:7924: ras la bris sam lugs sku gcig / shar nas
NG0204:7925: nub tu gzigs pa gzhag / 'bras la sogs pa'i
NG0204:7926: bshos cha la // lha bshos ri rab tshul 'dra bya //
NG0204:7927: de yi phyogs bzhir mar khus byug / dbus su smyug ma tshigs gsum la //
NG0204:7928: bya rgod ldem phod za 'og dang *//
NG0204:7929: bse dang gser dang byi ru dang *//
NG0204:7930: pags blud dkar pos brgyan pa gzug / gzhan yang sha dang nya sha dang *//
NG0204:7931: thud phrum la sogs spyan gzigs kyis //
NG0204:7932: de yi mtha' ma bskor te dgram //
NG0204:7933: spos dang me tog mar me dang *//
NG0204:7934: rnga gling pi wang dung la sogs //
NG0204:7935: sku gzugs de yi mtha' mar gzhag / tsan+dan dkar po'i chu la sogs //
NG0204:7936: dur phor 'khar phor bkang ba gnyis //
NG0204:7937: sku gzugs de yi mtha' mar dgram //
NG0204:7938: nyung dkar nyung nag ske tshe yang *//
NG0204:7939: drag po sngags kyi mtshon du gzhag / gzhan yang sgo nga sna tshogs dang */
NG0204:7942: sgog pa sman dang dri spos rnams //
NG0204:7943: bris sku de yi mtha' mar dgram //
NG0204:7944: gshin rje gshed po'i skur bsgom la //
NG0204:7945: snying po brgya rtsa brgyad du gdon //
NG0204:7946: om a kro te ka ya man+ta ka ha na ma tha b+hany+dza hum phat /
NG0204:7947: om ka la ru pa hum phat /
NG0204:7948: om hrihsh+t+r-ihbi kr-i ta na na hum hum phat phat /
NG0204:7949: bdag la byin brlab lus bsrung bya //
NG0204:7950: de nas dbang du gyur pa dang *//
NG0204:7951: rgyal po btsun pa'i las bya'o //
NG0204:7952: spyan drang phyag 'tshal bzhugs su gsol //
NG0204:7953: phyag chab gsol dang gdan skyems drangs //
NG0204:7954: mchod pa 'bul zhing bstod pa bgyi //
NG0204:7955: 'dzab bzlas dam tshig drag tu bsre //
NG0204:7956: rgyal po'i srog snying 'di skad brjod //
NG0204:7957: om shri many+dzu ya ma ra dza ma ma e ka dza ti nr-i dza dza /
NG0204:7958: tri tsa pa la a shug me swa ha /
NG0204:7959: zhes ni khri 'bum grangs bsnyen bya //
NG0204:7960: rdzas kyis mchod cing rtag tu bzlas //
NG0204:7961: grub nas sngags 'dis rab tu rbad //
NG0204:7962: ha li hu li bam ril nr-i dza li pra ma ni /
NG0204:7965: kro ti ko la sha sha ma tri sha mu tri /
NG0204:7969: che ge mo tsit+ta la dza /
NG0204:7970: de bzhin rgyal po drag tu rbad //
NG0204:7971: gal te las byed ma btub na //
NG0204:7972: rgyal po shi sa 'di yis bstan //
NG0204:7973: ma ra na pra ma ra tsa tsi ta pa
NG0204:7974: le a li sa ma ya am gu sha dza
NG0204:7975: dza / phyag rgya bzhi yis gzugs bcings te //
NG0204:7976: sngags ni brgya rtsa brgyad du brjod //
NG0204:7977: rgyal po rang la dbang med par //
NG0204:7979: de bzhin gsad pa'i las thabs kyang *//
NG0204:7980: smyo 'bog shi ba'i ldan pher du //
NG0204:7981: de nyid rang gi snying khrag dang *//
NG0204:7982: dug sna gsum dang mi khrag dang *//
NG0204:7983: brnag pa'i ming rus bris te gzhug / dur khrod ro ras rnying pa la //
NG0204:7984: gsod pa'i 'khor lo bca' bar gsungs //
NG0204:7985: dang po nyi ma bzhi pa'i sngags //
NG0204:7986: de yi phyi rim rgyal po'i drag sngags bri //
NG0204:7987: yang rim klu yi drag sngags bri //
NG0204:7988: thod pa dril la rgya gram bcing *//
NG0204:7989: nyin bzhi lha yi ging bzhi bskul //
NG0204:7990: skabs su ging chen bco brgyad bskul //
NG0204:7991: nyi ma bzhi pa'i las kyang bya //
NG0204:7992: om ma ha ra dza thun b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NG0204:7995: dgra bo'i snying shag tshal pa dum /
NG0204:7997: rlag dza ru thibs chug dgra bo'i khrag la 'jib /
NG0204:7998: b+h+yi ba b+h+yi ba dun dza /
NG0204:8000: snying ta snying ta la dun /
NG0204:8001: khrag ta khrag la thun b+h+yo thun b+h+yo mug nyung dkar nyung nag ske tshe la //
NG0204:8002: drag tu sngags la brdeg par bya //
NG0204:8003: dkar po gcig gis thugs dam bskang *//
NG0204:8004: rtags kyang 'di bzhin ston par nges //
NG0204:8005: nyi zla 'char dang lder so dang *//
NG0204:8006: 'bag tu rmis na tha mar bshad //
NG0204:8007: bcad po zhang blon dge bshes sam //
NG0204:8008: dmag dpon rmis na 'bring du bshad //
NG0204:8009: rgyal po nyid mthong nyams su @#//
NG0204:8011: de ltar byung na rab tu bshad //
NG0204:8012: bskang bshags bya zhing dngos grub blangs //
NG0204:8013: dam tshig bsre zhing phrin las bcol //
NG0204:8014: de nas 'khor lo thod par bca' //
NG0204:8015: shar du kha bltas chu mig ngor //
NG0204:8016: rgyal rigs sbyor ba byas gyur na //
NG0204:8019: mkhar rmang mnan na gnam lcags 'bab //
NG0204:8020: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:8021: rgyal po phyir ltar sgrub pa smyo 'bog gi skabs te le'u re lnga pa'o ///
NG0204:8022: / de nas yang bcom ldan 'das gshin rje gshed
NG0204:8023: pos rgyal po nang du bsgrubs te smyo 'bog gtong
NG0204:8025: thog mar bla ma mnyes byas shing *//
NG0204:8026: sgrib pa sbyong zhing dam tshig bsrung *//
NG0204:8027: mtshan ldan dgon pa'i gnas nyid du //
NG0204:8028: blta ba rgya bskyed 'jam dpal bsnyen //
NG0204:8029: bla ma mnyes pa'i rim gro bya //
NG0204:8030: dkyil 'khor brtsig dang chag chag gdab //
NG0204:8031: de nas dkyil 'khor bri ba ni //
NG0204:8032: thig bzhi btab la le'u tshe dgu //
NG0204:8033: dbus kyi le'u tshe dkar po la //
NG0204:8034: shar ser lho sngo nub dmar byang ni ljang *//
NG0204:8035: mtshams bzhi smug nag sgo dang bcas //
NG0204:8036: dbus su gru gsum re re bri //
NG0204:8038: rgya shug dkar po'i phur pa dgu //
NG0204:8039: srog bdag dgu ru mnga' gsol la //
NG0204:8040: dar dkar srog snying bris te gdags //
NG0204:8041: 'di skad brjod la dgod par bya'o //
NG0204:8043: dbus phyogs shel ri shel gyi khang pa nas /
NG0204:8044: khams gsum srog la mnga' mdzad pa //
NG0204:8045: srog bdag nag po ral pa can //
NG0204:8046: bstan pa srung phyir gshegs su gsol //
NG0204:8047: bsam pa bsgrub phyir gshegs nas kyang *//
NG0204:8048: pho brang dbus kyi le'u tshe la //
NG0204:8049: dgra bgegs bsnol ba'i gdan stengs su //
NG0204:8050: dgyes shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NG0204:8051: ging ka ra sa ma ya tish+tha lhan //
NG0204:8053: rgyal rigs srog la mnga' mdzad pa //
NG0204:8054: srog bdag rgyal po khu le shod //
NG0204:8055: dkyil 'khor shar gyi le'u tshe la //
NG0204:8056: dgyes shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NG0204:8057: bram ze'i srog la mnga' mdzad pa //
NG0204:8058: rgyal po chen po ag ge yang *//
NG0204:8059: lho phyogs dkyil 'khor le'u tshe la //
NG0204:8060: dgyes shing brtan par par bzhugs su gsol //
NG0204:8061: rjes rigs srog la mnga' mdzad pa'i //
NG0204:8062: rgyal po chen po ug ge yang *//
NG0204:8063: de bzhin nub kyi phyogs su dgod //
NG0204:8064: dmangs rigs srog la mnga' mdzad pa //
NG0204:8065: rgyal po chen po bram ze yang *//
NG0204:8066: de bzhin byang gi phyogs su dgod //
NG0204:8067: bud med srog la mnga' mdzad pa //
NG0204:8068: rgyal po chen po shang ze yang *//
NG0204:8069: dkyil 'khor shar lho'i ling tser dgod //
NG0204:8070: byis pa'i srog la mnga' mdzad @#//
NG0204:8072: rgyal po chen po da khod kyang *//
NG0204:8073: dkyil 'khor lho nub ling tsher dgod //
NG0204:8074: mi nag srog la mnga' mdzad pa //
NG0204:8075: rgyal po chen po ni khod kyang *//
NG0204:8076: nub byang dkyil 'khor le'u tsher dgod //
NG0204:8077: byol song srog la mnga' mdzad pa //
NG0204:8078: rgyal po chen po nyi zla yang *//
NG0204:8079: byang shar dkyil 'khor ling tsher dgod //
NG0204:8080: de nas mchog gi phur pa bzhi //
NG0204:8081: nyin bzhi'i ging bzhir mnga' gsol la //
NG0204:8082: ris mthun dar gyi con pan gdags //
NG0204:8083: phrin las bcol phyir sgo bzhir gdab //
NG0204:8084: dar skud gsum dril mtha' ma bskor //
NG0204:8085: bla rgyan logs rgyan ci mang dgram //
NG0204:8086: dar dkar gur phub za 'og gdan yang bting *//
NG0204:8087: de nas dbus kyi srog bdag la //
NG0204:8088: gsang phye bre gang lha bshos la //
NG0204:8089: ri rab tshul 'dra zhig byas la //
NG0204:8090: dbus su smyug ma tshigs dgu la //
NG0204:8091: mtshal gyi mkhar thabs nya mig bri //
NG0204:8092: rtse la bya rgod rgyal mtshan dang *//
NG0204:8093: dar dkar gdugs gcig steng nas dgab //
NG0204:8094: dngul gyi g.yer kha g.yag rnga phon //
NG0204:8095: lpags bu dkar po'i blud bu gdags //
NG0204:8096: tha ma'i tshigs la ming rus gdags //
NG0204:8097: gzhan yang smyug ma tshigs gsum brgyad //
NG0204:8098: mtshal dang ldong ros sgo sprad la //
NG0204:8099: mkhar thabs bris la rtse kha sprad //
NG0204:8100: lce la dar lce re yang gdags //
NG0204:8101: bar bar ra dkar blud bu dang *//
NG0204:8102: dung dang zangs dang rin po che //
NG0204:8103: byu ru mgron bu+u sa gser gdags //
NG0204:8104: tha ma'i tshigs la ming rus gdags //
NG0204:8105: lcang ma mtho re ba bzhi la //
NG0204:8106: mtshal lam rams kyis g.yung drung bris //
NG0204:8107: thod re ral lpags grog dkar la yang ming rus bri //
NG0204:8108: de bzhin btags la sgo bzhir gzhag / gzhan yang thud dang nya sha dang *//
NG0204:8109: bu ram gtor ma 'bras chan dang *//
NG0204:8110: za 'og dar dang pags dkar dang *//
NG0204:8111: rin chen rtsal la phyogs bzhir gzhag / gcig ni dbus su gzhag par bya //
NG0204:8112: nya phyis dung phor 'khar gzhong du //
NG0204:8113: gser dang chang phud sbyar ba lnga //
NG0204:8114: phyogs bzhi dbus dang lnga ru gzhag / gcig tu mtshe dang nyung nag dang *//
NG0204:8115: chang phud gangs chu chu mig chu //
NG0204:8116: de gsum gcig tu bsres la gzhag / drag sngags rgyun du bzlas pa'i phyir //
NG0204:8117: bdag nyid shar bltas sngon du gzhag / gzhan yang spos dang me tog dang *//
NG0204:8118: mar me dri chab rnga gling dang *//
NG0204:8119: mchod pa'i yo byad phyogs bzhir dgram //
NG0204:8120: ra lug dkar po gang yod pa //
NG0204:8121: ra dang ze ba dmar por byug / ske ru dar dkar khug ma ru //
NG0204:8122: mtshe nyung klu sman sna tshogs dang *//
NG0204:8123: dgra yi ming byang bcug la gdags //
NG0204:8124: nub tu dar 'phan dkar po la //
NG0204:8125: 'phan lce ser po btags pa gcig / rgyal po'i gzugs bris mdungs la gdags //
NG0204:8127: bkal la gzug / gshin rje gshed por mnga' gsol la //
NG0204:8128: sngags bzlas bstod pa mang du bya //
NG0204:8129: ber gyon thod bcing rnga yang brdung *//
NG0204:8130: snyan gsan dbab dang spyan drang dang *//
NG0204:8132: bstod pa dbul zhing smon lam gdab //
NG0204:8133: thugs dam bskang zhing phrin las bcol //
NG0204:8134: srog snying 'di ni rtag tu grangs //
NG0204:8135: om tri stu ti bya 'gyur ra ka la ma ra ma ra ya swa ha /
NG0204:8136: de ni srog bdag rang gi snying po'o //
NG0204:8137: 'di ni 'khor srog bdag gi snying po'o //
NG0204:8138: om khu le ma ha be ram swa ha /
NG0204:8139: om ag ge ru rta swa ha /
NG0204:8140: om ug ge sha ma le swa ha /
NG0204:8141: om drang zi rta ba swa ha /
NG0204:8142: om shang ze shang ka ra swa ha /
NG0204:8143: om da khod bi pi ya ra swa ha /
NG0204:8144: om ni khod ba ra hi te swa ha /
NG0204:8145: om sur+ya tsan+d+ra ma ta khu le swa ha /
NG0204:8146: de rnams srog gi snying po'o //
NG0204:8147: mi tshig g.yal dang spring pa spang *//
NG0204:8148: skya rengs shar nas 'khor rnams bskul //
NG0204:8149: grub pa'i rtags rnams ston par nges //
NG0204:8151: rab la sku ni dngos su ston //
NG0204:8152: 'bring la 'od dang sgra ru ston / tha ma chad //
NG0204:8153: de la dbang bskur dam bsre bya //
NG0204:8154: rbad sngags grangs shing phrin las bcol //
NG0204:8155: a+om ma ha pra ma na rak+sha rak+ta tsa ra
NG0204:8156: mun tra ma ha shi de tso ka tsa la
NG0204:8157: bing bing dgra bo ma ra ya hab hab /
NG0204:8158: de ni rgyal po 'khor dang bcas pa rnams las la rbad pa'o //
NG0204:8159: de nas rta dkar po'i thod pa'i nang brnag pa'i ming rus bcug la /
NG0204:8160: rta thod za 'og dag gis gril //
NG0204:8161: dam sri smyo ru gzhug pa'i phyir /
NG0204:8162: khrag skam mgu gul sbyar de dang *//
NG0204:8163: mtshe nyung go ro tsa na la //
NG0204:8165: om ma ma ma rang ga thun b+h+yo /
NG0204:8166: ma ha ra dza thun b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NG0204:8167: ma ha ba b+ha b+ha ma ha de ba ma ha ru tra b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NG0204:8168: om tro ta ya tro ta ya /
NG0204:8169: tra ta ya tra ta ya /
NG0204:8170: k+shu lha k+shu lha ging ka ra ging ka ra /
NG0204:8171: ging dz+wa la ging dz+wa la yak+sha gr-i ba /
NG0204:8173: d+ha sha gri wa d+ha sha gri wa /
NG0204:8174: pu tra dkar po b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NG0204:8175: de ni srog bdag 'khor gyi smyo 'bog tu bsngags so //
NG0204:8176: de nas brnag pa'i ming rus la //
NG0204:8177: rang rang rtsa ba'i sngags brjod cing *//
NG0204:8178: phur pa rnams kyis rim pas gdab //
NG0204:8179: gtso bo'i phur pa snying la gdab /
NG0204:8180: khu le shod kyi gsang bar gdab //
NG0204:8181: rgyal po ag ge lag pa g.yas //
NG0204:8182: rgyal po ug ge dpung par gdab //
NG0204:8183: rgyal po drang ze'i lag pa g.yon //
NG0204:8184: shang ze'i rkang pa g.yas su gdab //
NG0204:8185: da khod dpung mgo g.yas su gdab //
NG0204:8186: ni khod dpung mgo g.yon la gdab //
NG0204:8187: nyi zlas rkang pa g.yon la gdab //
NG0204:8188: gsad pa nyi ma bzhi pa ste //
NG0204:8189: nyin bzhi lha yi ging bzhi bya //
NG0204:8190: de nas rta yi thod pa ru //
NG0204:8191: ling+ga'i thod shul mthun rdzas stsal //
NG0204:8192: lha khang rnams la btags gyur na //
NG0204:8195: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:8196: smyo 'bog gi zla gsang las rgyal po nang ltar bsgrub pa'i skabs te le'u re drug pa'o ///
NG0204:8197: / de nas yang bcom ldan 'das gshin rje gshed
NG0204:8198: pos rgyal po gsang bar bsgrub pa'i thabs thams cad
NG0204:8199: kyi mchog tu gyur pa 'di gsungs so //
NG0204:8200: rnal 'byor yon tan ldan pa des //
NG0204:8201: bla ma mnyes pa rab byas te //
NG0204:8202: mgo ni rma bya bzhin du dgug / dam tshig chen po srog bzhin bsrung *//
NG0204:8203: gzhan don ma yin rang don du //
NG0204:8204: dur khrod sa phug dgon par 'gro //
NG0204:8205: phyi bshags sdig sbyangs bsod nams bsags //
NG0204:8206: ma nyes dpang gzug glud gtor gtang *//
NG0204:8207: dkyil 'khor brtsig la chag chag gdab //
NG0204:8208: thig gdab dkyil 'khor cho ga bya //
NG0204:8209: dkyil 'khor mthing nag gru gsum bri //
NG0204:8210: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi thod phreng bcas //
NG0204:8211: gru chad sgo bzhi ldan pa la //
NG0204:8212: dur khrod rgyan dang ldan pa la //
NG0204:8214: sgo bzhir gru gsum re re bri //
NG0204:8215: de nas mchog gi phur pa dgu //
NG0204:8216: srog bdag dgu yi sngags bris la //
NG0204:8217: dbus su dkar po snying 'byin dgod //
NG0204:8218: rgyan dang cha lugs gsal bar bskyed //
NG0204:8219: shar phyogs rtsibs la khu le dgod //
NG0204:8220: lho yi rtsibs la ag ge dgod //
NG0204:8221: nub kyi rtsibs la ug ge dgod //
NG0204:8222: byang gi rtsibs la drang ze dgod //
NG0204:8223: shang ze shar la da khod lho //
NG0204:8224: ni khod nub la nyi zla byang *//
NG0204:8225: de ltar sgo bzhir dgod par bya //
NG0204:8226: 'khar gzhong dung phor bse gab tu //
NG0204:8227: snying sna tshogs kyi gtor ma bsham //
NG0204:8228: lug dkar snying srog ma bral ba //
NG0204:8229: srog rtsa'i nang du ming rus gzhug / snying rtse
NG0204:8230: gyen du bstan la gzhag / dar dkar tshil gyis
NG0204:8231: kha bcad la // dbus su srog bdag nyid la
NG0204:8232: gzhag / shar du khrag sna'i gtor ma gzhag /
NG0204:8233: lho ru sha sna'i gtor ma gzhag / nub tu
NG0204:8234: rus pa'i gtor ma gzhag / byang du mkhal ma'i
NG0204:8235: gtor ma gzhag / de nas sgo bzhi'i gtor ma
NG0204:8236: kha bcad la // yang *// shar sgor mchin pa
NG0204:8237: sna tshogs gzhag / lho sgor sha chen 'bru sna
NG0204:8238: gzhag / nub sgor mcher pa sna tshogs gzhag /
NG0204:8239: byang sgor tshil bu sna tshogs gzhag / gtor ma
NG0204:8241: bshos bu mkhyid re btsugs la gzhag / de la smyug rgod re la yang *//
NG0204:8242: phod dkar pags bu dkar po dang *//
NG0204:8243: ming byang re yang btags la gzhag / phyogs ma nor bar gzhag pa yang *//
NG0204:8244: man 'jil steng du gzhag par bya //
NG0204:8245: shar du lug dkar lho ru ra //
NG0204:8246: nub tu bya dkar byang du khyi //
NG0204:8247: bag zan gzugs byas dkar por bsgyur //
NG0204:8248: sems can dngos su yod na rab //
NG0204:8249: med na gang rung gcig gi sker //
NG0204:8253: dam sri'i gzugs dang ming rus gzhug / sha khrag sna tshogs gtor ma la //
NG0204:8254: tshil chen zhal khebs yod pa la //
NG0204:8255: rak+ta'i gsang nan chas pa cig / dkyil 'khor byang
NG0204:8256: shar mtshams su gzhag / ting 'dzin rnam gsum gsal
NG0204:8257: bar bsgom // gzhal yas gdan bcas spyan drang bskyed //
NG0204:8258: bdag nyid gshed por gsal bsgom la //
NG0204:8259: rgyal po 'khor bcas gsal bar bsgom //
NG0204:8260: spyan drang bzhugs mchod tshul bzhin bya //
NG0204:8261: rtag tu snying po 'di yang bzlas //
NG0204:8262: om 'bar sha ma ha ra dza swa ha /
NG0204:8263: om khu le ma ha be ra ma swa ha /
NG0204:8264: om ag ge ru rta swa ha //
NG0204:8265: om ug ge ma le swa ha /
NG0204:8266: om drang ze ba b+ha swa ha /
NG0204:8267: om shang ze shang ka ra ma swa ha /
NG0204:8268: om da khod pi pi pa ra swa ha /
NG0204:8269: om ni khod pa ra hi te swa ha /
NG0204:8270: om sur+ya tsan+d+ra ma ha khu le swa ha /
NG0204:8271: de ni rtsa ba'i drag sngags te //
NG0204:8272: grub rtags sku yang dngos su ston //
NG0204:8273: me dang 'od dang sgra yang ston //
NG0204:8274: sprel dang byi la seng ge 'bag / dge bshes btsad po lta bu dang *//
NG0204:8275: dmag dpon lta bur ston par nges //
NG0204:8276: rgyal po drag tu sngags 'dis rbad //
NG0204:8277: om ma ha da ma rak+sha rak+ta tsa ra mu
NG0204:8278: tra ma ha ni te tso ka tsa la bing
NG0204:8279: bing dgra bo ma ra ya hab hab //
NG0204:8281: lha dang dbye ba drag po'i sngags 'dis dbral //
NG0204:8282: ma ha sa ma ya rak+sha ma ha ra dza thun thun phrol phrol /
NG0204:8283: de nas bsgrub pa thon nas kyang *//
NG0204:8284: gsad pa'i phur pas gdab pa ni //
NG0204:8285: dbus nas phyung la 'di skad do //
NG0204:8287: khro bdag chen po snying 'byin gyis //
NG0204:8288: dpa' bo chen por dbang bskur bas //
NG0204:8289: dgra snying dkar nag mtshams su gdab //
NG0204:8290: btab nas myur du brlag gyur cig / ki li ki la ya tsit+ta mugs //
NG0204:8293: khro bdag chen po khu le shog / gsod pa'i phur par byin brlabs te //
NG0204:8294: phrag khyim g.yas dang g.yon du gdab //
NG0204:8295: btab pas khrag skam myur du gsod //
NG0204:8296: badzra mu ti tsa sha rak+ta rngubs lhan //
NG0204:8298: khro bdag srog bdag ag ge yang *//
NG0204:8299: 'gugs pa'i bdag por mnga' gsol nas //
NG0204:8300: nu ma g.yas dang g.yon du gdab //
NG0204:8301: btab pas mkhris pa k+sha yas sod //
NG0204:8302: tsi li tsi li ma sa ma thibs thibs /
NG0204:8304: khro bdag sgrol ging ug ge yang *//
NG0204:8305: rno ba'i dpal du byin brlabs nas //
NG0204:8306: spyi bo'i gtsug tu btab pas kyang *//
NG0204:8307: klad gzer mgo dang 'dar bus sod //
NG0204:8308: mas bu ta tshal pa tshal pa ka ru hum hum /
NG0204:8310: khro bdag shan pa drang ze yang *//
NG0204:8311: 'debs pa'i dpal du byin brlabs nas //
NG0204:8312: mkhal khung gnyis su gdab par bya //
NG0204:8313: btab pas chu 'gag ske nad sod //
NG0204:8314: bi ma la bi khu ya bi @#//
NG0204:8316: hum khro bdag srog gcod shang ze yang *//
NG0204:8317: zur gsum rtse mor byin brlabs te //
NG0204:8318: mchin pa pho gdung rtsa la gdab //
NG0204:8319: btab pas mchin nad khrag gis sod //
NG0204:8320: ma sa la khu+u ma ta ra la tshang bu re ra dgra bo ma ra ya dza /
NG0204:8322: khro bdag gsod dga' da khod kyang *//
NG0204:8323: thogs med 'debs par dbang bskur nas //
NG0204:8324: sha mtshan rme bu'i dkyil du gdab //
NG0204:8325: btab pas sbos nas grum bus sod //
NG0204:8326: kha la ru tse kha ma la sha phu phat dza /
NG0204:8328: dgra bla'i rgyal po ni khod kyang *//
NG0204:8329: rtse gsum ngar can rab 'byin bskyed //
NG0204:8330: mcher pa'i dbus su btab nas kyang *//
NG0204:8331: mcher nad lkugs nad smyo 'bog thong *//
NG0204:8332: me kha kha ru tsi pag sha ru tra me mu ru mu ru phat dza /
NG0204:8334: gsang ba'i sog bdag nyi zla yang *//
NG0204:8335: phur pa'i lha ru dbang bskur nas //
NG0204:8336: rkang ba'i mthil du gdab par bya //
NG0204:8337: zha grum sgur nad 'theng grum gtong *//
NG0204:8338: 'ba' lu bag te rag sha kha khrag rngubs rngubs //
NG0204:8339: phur sngags btab nas thun sngags brab //
NG0204:8340: om ma ma ma ra ya thun b+h+yo /
NG0204:8341: ma ra ra tsa thun b+h+yo b+h+yo ma ha ba
NG0204:8342: ba ma ha de ba ma ha ru tra b+h+yo
NG0204:8343: b+h+yo / thun gyis brgyab ste brlag par 'gyur //
NG0204:8344: ling+ga gtubs la gtor mar rtsal //
NG0204:8345: ri gsum rtse la yas stags bskyal //
NG0204:8346: rgyal po bsrung ba'i sngags ni /
NG0204:8347: om kha du she sha sha pra la ma ma ru tra /
NG0204:8349: srog bdag 'khor dang bcas las nor sgrub pa'i sngags la /
NG0204:8350: om dzam be le she ba la go mes srum srum trum trum swa ha /
NG0204:8351: rgyal po 'khor dang bcas pas byes su gar 'gro yang dgra bgegs mi 'byung ba ni /
NG0204:8352: om nas ne nas ne ham shi ka ra ka
NG0204:8353: ra ma ra ma ra ru lu ru lu phat
NG0204:8354: phat b+h+yo b+h+yo / rgyal pos gal te bdag gam gzhan la 'tshe bar gyur na /
NG0204:8356: bu ma ha ra dza ba shan zhil zhil shan ting swa ha //
NG0204:8357: ma ha ra dza shan ting swa ha /
NG0204:8358: rgyal po 'khor dang bcas pas rigs brgyud 'phrog pa dang */
NG0204:8360: om ma ha ka la gangs dre mo bdud rnams rngam rngam swa ha /
NG0204:8361: rgyal pos ye 'drog sum brgya drug cu dang thob shor gtong ba'i sngags la /
NG0204:8363: yam be ra srog rtsa la kha sa kha sa me ru me ru swa ha /
NG0204:8364: rgyal pos ser ba 'bebs pa'i sngags la /
NG0204:8365: om pra ta pre sha thor b+h+yo /
NG0204:8368: kha shar tra be shar shar /
NG0204:8370: rgyal po ltas ngan 'bebs pa'i sngags la /
NG0204:8371: om shar ging ram shag rgyug rgyug ram rgyug srog
NG0204:8372: la rgyug sha sha dgra bo'i snying la sha /
NG0204:8373: 'bru til ram khyer sod srog / rgyal pos ya
NG0204:8374: cha stab bsnol gtong ba'i sngags la /
NG0204:8375: om ma ha pra ga shing kha me ru kha
NG0204:8376: la a tsi ma sha dgra bo phrol phrol shig
NG0204:8379: gang la bya yang thogs pa med //
NG0204:8380: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:8381: rgyal po gsang bar bsgrub pa'i smyo 'bog gi skabs te le'u re bdun pa'o ///
NG0204:8382: / de nas bcom ldan 'das gshin rje gshed pos /
NG0204:8383: 'gal ba cham la dbab slad du //
NG0204:8384: gnod sbyin gdug pa'i zla gsang gsungs pa //
NG0204:8385: dad pa gsum ldan rnal 'byor pas //
NG0204:8386: dam tshig rang gi srog bzhin bsrung *//
NG0204:8387: bla ma mnyes pa'i rim gro bya //
NG0204:8388: dur khrod nags tshal dgon par 'gro //
NG0204:8390: bsod nams tshogs kyi yan lag bsag / ma nyes dpang gzug glud gtor gtang *//
NG0204:8391: gnod sbyin 'di nyid bsgrub par bya //
NG0204:8392: lcang lo can gyi pho brang na //
NG0204:8393: las grub rigs kyi zhing khams nas //
NG0204:8394: gnod sbyin bye ba sa ya gnas //
NG0204:8395: de dag nang na dregs pa'i sku //
NG0204:8396: mthu stobs ldan pa'i gang bzang bsgrub //
NG0204:8397: dkyil 'khor dbus kyi khri brtsegs la //
NG0204:8398: steng du gnod sbyin sku gzugs gzhag / tsan+dan rigs las 'bur du brkos //
NG0204:8399: chu zheng gab pa gel gel po //
NG0204:8400: sku mdog sngon po gzi ldan pa //
NG0204:8401: dbu skra lcang lo rin chen brgyan //
NG0204:8402: ut+pal sngon po'i phreng bas mdzes //
NG0204:8403: g.yas na shing tog dmar po bsnams //
NG0204:8404: g.yon na mi lpags rgyal mtshan bsnams //
NG0204:8405: gzas pa'i gzugs byas snying gar gzhug / de yi dbus su dong gru gsum //
NG0204:8406: rtse mo byang du bltas pa la //
NG0204:8407: nang du khrag dang sol bas byug / til gyi phye la dgra yi gzugs //
NG0204:8408: mi khrag bla dwags bris la gzhug / zhabs mas gril la tshon skud bcing *//
NG0204:8409: gru gsum brus pa'i nang du gzhug / mtha' ma
NG0204:8410: rtsang gis bskor te gzhag / gzugs kyi ske nas
NG0204:8411: sngo dmar gdags // sna gcig sku yi zhabs la gdags //
NG0204:8412: sngags pa'i mdun du dam rdzas dgram //
NG0204:8413: la phug rus phye ske tshe la //
NG0204:8414: de bzhin gtor ma byas te gzhag / nyung nag lan tshwa dug tu sbyar //
NG0204:8415: gzugs la brab cing ngan sngags bzlas //
NG0204:8417: de bzhin rims pas las rnams bya //
NG0204:8418: dur khrod ras la 'khor lo ni //
NG0204:8419: dug khrag sbyar bas bri bar bya //
NG0204:8420: rim pa bzhin du drag sngags dgod //
NG0204:8421: spyan drang bzhugs mchod bstod pa bya //
NG0204:8422: phrin las bcol zhing gnad nas bskul //
NG0204:8423: lha dang phral zhing rdzas kyis bdug / drag sngags
NG0204:8424: bzlas shing 'khor lo gzhug / gsad pa las kyi
NG0204:8425: sbyor la 'jug / gnan bsreg 'phang ba gsum la
NG0204:8426: gtad // dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:8427: srog bcod spu gri gnod sbyin gyi zla gsang las /
NG0204:8428: gang ba bzang po phyi ltar bsgrub pa'i skabs te le'u re @#//
NG0204:8430: / de nas yang bcom ldan 'das gshin rje gshed
NG0204:8431: pos gang ba bzang po nang du bsgrub pa 'di
NG0204:8432: gsungs so // dkyil 'khor mthing nag gru gsum la //
NG0204:8433: zla gam gsum gyis bskor ba bri //
NG0204:8434: dmar smug me ri ra bas bskor //
NG0204:8435: dbus su gshed po yab yum ste //
NG0204:8436: mdun du gang ba bzang po dgod //
NG0204:8437: mtshan ldan thod pa dum gsum du //
NG0204:8438: la phug rus pa'i phye ma dang *//
NG0204:8439: snying sna khrag sna sbyar la gzhag / dbus kyi gru gsum mthur du bskor //
NG0204:8440: nang du rabs chad thod pa gzhug / nyung nag nyung dkar lan tshwa dang *//
NG0204:8441: dug dang sme khrag sbyar bas dgang *//
NG0204:8442: dmigs pa'i ming rus ji gzhin byas //
NG0204:8443: thod pa'i nang du gzhug par bya //
NG0204:8444: dur khrod grong khyer bcom nas kyang *//
NG0204:8445: mtshan ma'i ras blangs skyang nul bya //
NG0204:8446: ldong ros chu rtsa ser pos byug / dug khrag sbyar nas 'khor lo bri //
NG0204:8447: de bzhi yi ge dgod byas la //
NG0204:8448: thun gyi thod pa kha yang gcad //
NG0204:8449: de nas rim pas las rnams bya //
NG0204:8452: grub pa'i gnod sbyin chen po spyan 'dren na //
NG0204:8453: bye ba sa ya'i 'khor dang rab chas te //
NG0204:8454: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung phyir gshegs su gsol //
NG0204:8455: e h+ye hi rak+sha ba sna ba si sa ma ya ho ha //
NG0204:8456: gser ltar rab tu brtan pa'i ri ngos la //
NG0204:8457: rma bya rab gnas gser du snang ba ltar //
NG0204:8458: bdag gis khyod bsgrub khyod kyi rang bzhin 'grub //
NG0204:8459: grub pa'i dbang po khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0204:8460: brtan pa bzhugs shig gnod sbyin mchog / rin chen gcal bkram sa gzhi la //
NG0204:8462: khri chen dpangs la brtan par bzhugs //
NG0204:8463: sa ma ya tish+tha lhan s+t+wam /
NG0204:8464: gser dang bcas pa'i skyems phud ma nyams pa //
NG0204:8465: dung chen snod du sbyar nas mchod pa 'bul //
NG0204:8466: dar gyi lhab lhub glu gar rol mo bcas //
NG0204:8467: bsam pa dag pas sbyar nas mchod pa dbul //
NG0204:8468: dril bu sgra snyan spos dang dri //
NG0204:8469: mar me bshos dang gtor ma khrag / mos pas 'bul lo bzhes su gsol //
NG0204:8470: om ra ra so ba ba'u pu tsa kra ma pu tsa ho ha /
NG0204:8471: de nas gsang sngags rab bzlas la /
NG0204:8472: om ba hu ri rta dza /
NG0204:8473: ma g+ha la bag sha dza /
NG0204:8474: ra tra ma ru ru dza /
NG0204:8475: snying la shar shar ru dza /
NG0204:8476: srog la breng breng thum dza /
NG0204:8477: gnod sbyin sku dang 'od dang sgra //
NG0204:8478: sa g.yos thog dang char chen 'ong *//
NG0204:8479: gong gi rdzas kyi rab tu brdeg / thugs dam bskul te phrin las bcol //
NG0204:8480: dus drug sngags 'di gzugs la brdeg / om dza lam ma ha dza lam /
NG0204:8482: sti pu stud de sa li bag sha swa ha //
NG0204:8483: 'di ni sngags kyi rgyal po ste //
NG0204:8484: thams cad grub pa'i sngags zhes brjod //
NG0204:8485: 'khor lo bcas kyi dam rdzas te //
NG0204:8488: (10)@#// bltas chu mig ngogs sbas na /
NG0204:8489: khrag skyugs 'chi bar the tshom med //
NG0204:8490: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:8491: srog gcod spu gri gnod sbyin gyi zla gsang gang
NG0204:8492: ba bzang po nang ltar bsgrub pa'i skabs te le'u
NG0204:8493: re dgu pa'o /// / de nas yang bcom ldan
NG0204:8494: 'das gshin rje gshed pos gang ba bzang po gsang
NG0204:8496: dam tshig dbang sgo thub pa'i bus //
NG0204:8497: bla ma mnyes phyir yid 'thad dbul //
NG0204:8498: mi don ma yin rang don du //
NG0204:8499: bsgrub pa gong bzhin tshul bshams te //
NG0204:8500: de rting man ngag 'di bzhin bya //
NG0204:8501: a ka ru dang du ru ka / lug mig kar+sha pa na le //
NG0204:8502: sngags ni 'di dag rab tu brjod //
NG0204:8503: om dz+wa la ma ha dz+wa la /
NG0204:8504: yag sha bag sha so su sdud de ba lam /
NG0204:8506: 'di ni sngags kyi rgyal po ste //
NG0204:8507: sngon du bsnyen pa sum 'bum bya //
NG0204:8508: lus bsrung sbyor ba 'di bzhin bya //
NG0204:8509: dpung pa dag la btags gyur na //
NG0204:8510: nad rnams thams cad byang bar 'gyur //
NG0204:8511: de nas gsad pa'i sbyor ba ni //
NG0204:8512: kar ni ka dang ba lu dang *//
NG0204:8513: 'u su rdo dreg sha ka ra //
NG0204:8514: ngang pa'i sgro la bskus nas kyang *//
NG0204:8515: gzugs la dus drug mchod byas te //
NG0204:8516: phyag byas bzlas pa byas gyur na //
NG0204:8517: longs spyod dpag med thob par 'gyur /
NG0204:8518: khrag dang nyung rgod rta mchin dang *//
NG0204:8519: ba lang dag la bzlas byin na //
NG0204:8520: rta bong la sogs rmigs zlum rnams //
NG0204:8522: tsit+ta rus pa gyo mogs gsum //
NG0204:8523: sngags 'di bzlas nas byin gyur na //
NG0204:8524: om b+ha hu ri ri dza /
NG0204:8525: ma g+ha la bag sha dza /
NG0204:8526: ra ta ma ru ru dza /
NG0204:8527: snying la shar shar ru dza /
NG0204:8529: glang chen ba lang byin gyur na //
NG0204:8531: bse dang ka ka ru la yang *//
NG0204:8532: sngags de bzlas te byin gyur na //
NG0204:8534: b+hi li ka dang a mar dang *//
NG0204:8535: ru ram bu ram yang sbyar te ril bu bya //
NG0204:8536: zla ba gzas zin dus su bya //
NG0204:8537: ling+ga byas te gtums byas nas //
NG0204:8538: chu mig nang du thod par gnan //
NG0204:8540: bse zho btsan dug sbyar nas kyang *//
NG0204:8541: gsang sngags gong ma bzlas byas nas //
NG0204:8542: sha la reg pa'i ges [\[]gos [\]]la bsku //
NG0204:8543: lhog pa dkar pos 'chi bar nges //
NG0204:8545: yang na zha grum 'gro mi nus //
NG0204:8546: dang por khas blangs bzhin du bya //
NG0204:8547: phag pa spyang ki'i mche ba dang *//
NG0204:8548: wa yi ril ma spyang rtug par //
NG0204:8549: nyi ma gung ngam nam phyed na //
NG0204:8550: sum 'bum bzlas te don po yi //
NG0204:8553: srin rdo gdung chen sha ri ram //
NG0204:8554: de rnams thod pa dum gsum du //
NG0204:8556: sa'i khrag la sbyar la stsal //
NG0204:8557: gong gi sngags bzlas lha rten sba //
NG0204:8559: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:8560: srog gcod spu gri gnod sbyin gyi zla gsang las
NG0204:8561: gang ba bzang po gsang ba ltar bsgrub pa'i skabs
NG0204:8563: / de nas yang bcom ldan 'das gshin rje gshed pos /
NG0204:8564: 'gal ba cham la dbab slad du //
NG0204:8565: gdug pa klu yi zla gsang gsungs //
NG0204:8566: nub phyogs pho brang rgya mtsho'i chu //
NG0204:8567: ngo mtshar chu bo bzhi 'babs pa //
NG0204:8568: rab tu mi srun klu yi gnas //
NG0204:8569: de nyid dregs pa 'dul ba'i phyir //
NG0204:8570: bcom ldan gshin rje gshed po yis //
NG0204:8571: lag na rdo rjer sku sprul te //
NG0204:8572: lag na rdo rje thugs khros te //
NG0204:8573: gser mig 'bar ba'i nga rgyal gyis //
NG0204:8574: gdug pa'i klu rnams bred 'gyur te //
NG0204:8575: rab tu mi srun klu rnams kyis //
NG0204:8577: kye ma'o rdo rje gzugs mdzes pa //
NG0204:8578: rab tu rngams pa'i rdo rje'i so //
NG0204:8579: lcags mchu 'bar ba rab tu brjid //
NG0204:8580: gser mig 'bar ba rab tu bgrad //
NG0204:8581: mgo la yid bzhin nor bus brgyan //
NG0204:8582: shes rab thabs ldan gshog pa brkyang *//
NG0204:8583: thabs ldan sder mo rnam par gdengs //
NG0204:8585: sku stod mchog gi g.yang gzhis brgyan //
NG0204:8586: sku smad sbrul gyi chun pos brgyan //
NG0204:8587: thod pa tshar gsum se ral kha //
NG0204:8588: rtsal 'phags khyad par de bzhin mthong *//
NG0204:8589: bdag cag rnams kyi dam tshig lha //
NG0204:8590: drag po'i cha byad zla las rgyal //
NG0204:8591: drag po chen po bka' bzhin bgyid //
NG0204:8592: ces 'dzer zhing 'thon nas dam tshim smras te sku la 'khril lo //
NG0204:8593: na du tra sa na d+h+ri pa la du+u sa ni gar si ti swa ha /
NG0204:8594: de nas gser mig 'bar ba yis /
NG0204:8595: nga rgyal chen po bstan te /
NG0204:8596: dbang du bsdu phyir dam tshig phyag rgya bstan //
NG0204:8597: dang po gnyis ni nang du bsnol //
NG0204:8598: zla rnams rab tu brkyangs pa ste /
NG0204:8599: khros pa'i nga rgyal 'di brjod do //
NG0204:8600: ta ki dza de byi dzahde hu ya hu ya /
NG0204:8601: hu lu hu lu pu ru te pu ru swa ha /
NG0204:8602: zhes brjod nas che ba rgyun gyi ting 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs so //
NG0204:8603: de nas rigs bzhi'i klu rnams la //
NG0204:8604: rab tu che ba bstan pa'i phyir //
NG0204:8605: nyid kyi gzhal yas khang chen po //
NG0204:8606: rab tu brjod pa 'di nyid du //
NG0204:8607: byol song rigs bzhi dang thabs cig tu 'dug pa'i gnas 'di lta ste /
NG0204:8608: rgya mtsho chen po'i dbus gnas 'bar //
NG0204:8609: ri rab mchod rten gzugs 'dra la //
NG0204:8610: bum pa yid bzhin lcang los brgyan //
NG0204:8611: sbrul gnyis dar 'phyang ltar bus mdzes //
NG0204:8612: rigs bzhi'i rgyan gyis rab tu bklubs //
NG0204:8613: sgo bzhi ka brgyad rab tu ldan //
NG0204:8614: de 'og sum gnyis rab tu mdzes //
NG0204:8615: byol song longs spyod rab tu ldan //
NG0204:8618: gser mig 'bar ba dang thabs cig tu bzhugs pa 'di lta ste /
NG0204:8619: gzi brjid mtha' yas dung skyong dang *//
NG0204:8620: gang po nor ldan la sogs dang *//
NG0204:8621: dga' bo 'jog po ma dros dang *//
NG0204:8622: rigs bzhi'i gtso bo klu brgyad de //
NG0204:8623: sku la 'khril te rab tu gnas //
NG0204:8624: gyad nor med la sogs pa'i rgyan //
NG0204:8625: dar dpyangs ma dang pad+ma'i rgyan //
NG0204:8626: gzi brjid ma dang dung can ma //
NG0204:8627: klu mo rigs bzhi la sogs pa dang thabs cig tu bzhugs so //
NG0204:8628: de nas bcom ldan 'das gshin rje gshed pos gnyen po sgrub pa 'di gsungs so //
NG0204:8629: dgon pa dur khrod mtsho gling ngam //
NG0204:8630: chu mig nags na gnas pa'i bar //
NG0204:8632: dri spos sman gyis chag chag gdab //
NG0204:8633: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud ldan //
NG0204:8634: sgo bzhi rigs dang ldan pa bri //
NG0204:8635: dbus su lag na rdo rje ste //
NG0204:8636: 'khor lo bzhi la bya khyung bzhi //
NG0204:8637: gru chad mchod pa'i bum pa bzhin //
NG0204:8638: sman lnga spo lnga rin chen lnga //
NG0204:8639: 'bru lnga me tog lnga la sogs //
NG0204:8640: bcu gnyis lnga nyid byin gyis brlab //
NG0204:8641: sgo la mchod pa'i gtor ma bzhi //
NG0204:8642: b+ha ma ha sti bcas pa yi //
NG0204:8643: sor mo lnga yi changs pa'i rjes //
NG0204:8644: mkha' lding mchod pa'i rdzas su gzhag / de nas ting 'dzin rim pa ni //
NG0204:8645: dang po stong pa'i byang chub sems //
NG0204:8646: gnyis pa snying rje 'byung ba dang *//
NG0204:8647: gsum pa rgyu yi rnam pa las //
NG0204:8648: bam gyi sa bon las byung ba'i //
NG0204:8649: rgya mtsho chen po'i dbus su ni //
NG0204:8650: lam las ri rab rin chen bskyed //
NG0204:8651: de steng khrom las ga ru da //
NG0204:8652: rdo rje gshog pa'i byin rlabs las //
NG0204:8653: bya khyung rgyal po bzhi byung bas //
NG0204:8654: dkar dang dmar dang ser dang ljang *//
NG0204:8655: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi'i steng du bsgom //
NG0204:8656: shar phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsings stengs su //
NG0204:8657: ye shes mkha' lding stobs po che //
NG0204:8659: dbu gsum rdo rje'i mchu khra la //
NG0204:8660: ring la dmar zhing spyan yang dmar //
NG0204:8661: zhal gdangs ral pa sprugs pa'i tshul //
NG0204:8662: ye shes gshog gdengs sku yang shin tu g.yo //
NG0204:8663: sku dang yan lag rin chen baidur+yar brgyan //
NG0204:8664: phyag drug g.yas kyi dang po 'khor lo phyar //
NG0204:8665: bar pa lcags kyu tha ma thal mo sbyar //
NG0204:8666: g.yon gyi dang pos rin chen zur brgyad bsnams //
NG0204:8667: bar pa zhags pa tha ma thal mo sbyar //
NG0204:8668: nub phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs stengs su //
NG0204:8669: ye shes mkha' lding rgyal po gzi brjid 'od po che //
NG0204:8670: dbu gsum mdog dmar ral pa lcang lor 'khyil //
NG0204:8671: zhal gdangs ye shes gshog pa chen po gdengs //
NG0204:8672: sku dang ye shes yan lag me chen 'bar //
NG0204:8673: phyag drug g.yas kyi dang po rdo rje rtse lnga pa //
NG0204:8674: bar ma lcags kyu tha ma rin po che //
NG0204:8676: dang po rdo rje pad+ma phyar //
NG0204:8677: bar ma zhags pa tha ma dbyug to bsnams //
NG0204:8678: lho phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs stengs su //
NG0204:8679: ye shes mkha' lding rgyal po mi mgo can //
NG0204:8680: dbu gsum mdog ser ral pa gyen du 'khyil //
NG0204:8681: yan lag rin chen sku las me chen 'bar //
NG0204:8682: ye shes gshog pa rgya chen brkyang bskum mdzad //
NG0204:8683: phyag drug g.yas kyi dang po rin chen 'bar //
NG0204:8684: bar ma lcags kyu tha ma dpag bsam shing *//
NG0204:8685: g.yon gyi dang po ye shes ral gri 'phyar //
NG0204:8686: bar ma zhags pa tha ma gshog tshul brkyang *//
NG0204:8687: byang phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs stengs su //
NG0204:8688: ye shes mkha' lding rlung gi shugs //
NG0204:8689: dbu gsum mdog ljang ral pa 'khyil //
NG0204:8690: sgra skad sna tshogs bzhad cing smin ma bskyod //
NG0204:8691: yan lag rin chen brgyan pas sku 'bar ba //
NG0204:8692: phyag drug g.yas kyi dang po ral gri phyar //
NG0204:8693: bar ma lcags kyu tha ma shing thog bi dza pu'u ra //
NG0204:8694: g.yon gyi dang po 'khor lo 'bar ba bsnams //
NG0204:8695: bar ma zhags pa tha ma gshog tshul brkyang *//
NG0204:8696: de rnams rtsa ba'i snying po khrom las bskyed //
NG0204:8697: de bzhin spyan drang bzhugs gsol phyag bya dang *//
NG0204:8698: mchod dang bstod dang bzlas pa tshul bzhin bya //
NG0204:8699: ba lim la sogs byed pa dang *//
NG0204:8700: b+ha ma ha sti bcings pa yis //
NG0204:8701: sor mo lnga yis bcangs pa'i rjes //
NG0204:8702: zan chang dkar gsum 'bru dang sman gyis mchod //
NG0204:8703: om ra dza ma ha ga ru da /
NG0204:8704: hum ba lim pu tsa ba lim ta kha hi /
NG0204:8706: de nas sngags 'di rgyun du bzlas //
NG0204:8707: od kam od kam khyung ka ra khyung ka ra /
NG0204:8709: om badzra maha kro d+ha hum phat /
NG0204:8710: sngags de rtsa ba rgyun du grangs //
NG0204:8711: mkha' lding gso ba'i las byed na /
NG0204:8712: bdag gam gzhan la gdug pas 'jigs //
NG0204:8713: ga ru rgyal po mchod 'dod pas //
NG0204:8714: gnas sam khang pa'i sgo ngos te //
NG0204:8715: snum pa'i sa 'am bag zan la //
NG0204:8716: ga ru da yi gzugs bcas te //
NG0204:8717: ba lim la sogs pu tsa dang *//
NG0204:8718: b+ha ma ha sti bcings pa yi //
NG0204:8719: sor mo lnga yi pu tsa des //
NG0204:8720: ga ru da nyid la ni dbus //
NG0204:8721: snying po lnga po gang yang rung *//
NG0204:8722: gcig gis sna drangs brjod rting la /
NG0204:8723: ga ru da gnyis brjod nas kyang *//
NG0204:8724: de rting pu dza rab tu brjod //
NG0204:8725: thog mar om dang swa has dbul //
NG0204:8726: 'di ltar gzhung bzhin byas nas ni //
NG0204:8727: ka la sha tas zin pa la //
NG0204:8728: grol bar 'gyur ba the tshom med //
NG0204:8729: de nas gnyen po rigs bzhi la //
NG0204:8730: mnyes pa'i bstod pa 'di yang gsungs //
NG0204:8732: rig sngags bdag mo mthu stobs bdag po'i sku //
NG0204:8733: e ma'o phyag gi mthil na rdo rje 'bar 'dra bas //
NG0204:8734: zhal nas gsung skad bton pas khams gsum dbang du sdud //
NG0204:8735: stong gsum drag tu g.yos pas klu chen pho mo 'dul //
NG0204:8738: lcags kyu 'dab gshog chen po brkyang pas ni //
NG0204:8739: gser gyi 'od 'phro rlung sgra drag po yis //
NG0204:8740: rgya mtsho chen po kun tu brdabs pa yis //
NG0204:8741: klu rgyal 'khor dang bcas pa zil gyi gnon //
NG0204:8742: 'jigs byed gser gyi spyan rnon chen pos ni //
NG0204:8743: tshangs pa chen po'i yul sa rtse nas gnon //
NG0204:8744: gal te klu rnams dam las 'das gyur na //
NG0204:8745: rgya mtsho'i snying po rgya mtsho'i lbu ba la //
NG0204:8746: gshog pa chen po rgya mtshor byas nas ni //
